((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14217652611', 'TheReviewersreview', 1, 'Too many ads', 'This app sucks now because you guys putting too many ads!', '5.19.0', 'us', '2026-06-23T11:15:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14209600301', 'Annnahita', 5, '..', 'The best app for studying. Funny, attractive and exciting 🤗', '5.19.0', 'us', '2026-06-21T09:03:46-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14203065946', 'pineappleraccoon', 2, 'App has bugs', 'Love this app, been using it since college (almost 10 years) and like the daily challenges they incorporated however I’ve planted several trees today and none of the daily challenges are being marked as completed as they should…. I’ve had to delete and reinstall the app before to try and fix this problem, but that’s annoying to do all the time. Would be great if these bugs could be fixed', '5.19.0', 'us', '2026-06-19T16:12:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14202848031', 'عبدالله٤/٤٢١', 5, 'شكرًا Forest', 'اصبحت مدمنًا للمذاكرة ومهتمًا بجمع الأشجار', '5.19.0', 'us', '2026-06-19T14:47:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14197316303', 'tori070818', 5, 'Great for people with ADHD', 'I love this app a lot! I have severe ADHD and struggle with time management. I love the events they do and the fact that I can plant a cute little tree every time i set a timer! I love it so much that i got an annual subscription!', '5.19.0', 'us', '2026-06-18T06:19:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14190150318', 'russiankoolaid', 1, 'Support incredibly unhelpful, you’ll lose your data', 'I have used this app for years. After a recent update, I was force logged out and upon logging back in all my data, trees, everything, was gone. Support keeps telling me “logging out does not delete data” and that I must be logging in with the wrong account. I’ve only ever logged in with one email. I never said logging out deletes data, but that is what happened. Years of data and premium unlocked trees lost for no reason. Support cannot locate my data. I am incredibly frustrated and will never recommend this app again.', '5.19.0', 'us', '2026-06-16T09:45:27-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14189697478', 'bigchudboi', 5, 'this is awesome', 'i like how when you set a timer and you look at your phone it tells you to get off your phone and focus on what your doing', '5.19.0', 'us', '2026-06-16T07:30:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14189573586', 'ArtAndEngineering', 5, 'Loved it but wish there was more for long term users UPDATED, thanks 🥰', 'Updates: Thank you team for taking these concerns so seriously! I’m so glad I got to spend coins on cool stuff for the first time in forever! I wish I hadn’t completed this event so early, maybe only 10 days in, but a step in the right direction. Sadly I can’t easily afford plus because it looks like it would add a lot more to do/motivate me, and I hope you continue to support long term users who paid the original flat fee for the app, but I’m pleased by the progress and always impressed by the responsiveness of this team! Original review: Functionality has always been better than competitors, and the bugs that used to drive me crazy have been eliminated over time, so huge props to the developers for actually caring enough to squash them. Has certainly helped me focus, but more in the past since I am very motivated by rewards. As a long time user I’ve amassed well over 10k coins and I have nothing to spend them on. I did a trial of plus since it promised new trees, but was disappointed that they were free with the cost of the subscription. With nothing else to unlock except for the monthly challenges and rare store drops, I’m considering switching to another app. This has served me well but I’m not sure there’s much left for me here. Also, as others have noticed, battery drain has started to become a major issue with recent updates, another reason I’m considering leaving despite loving this app for years. It’s also disappointing that the leaderboards (global) appear to be full of cheaters who somehow achieve 23+ hours of focus time per day, so even that is useless for motivation.', '5.19.0', 'us', '2026-06-16T06:53:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14187200284', 'Shu_90', 5, 'Forest', 'Perfect', '5.19.0', 'us', '2026-06-15T14:44:27-07:00'),
