((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14136607701', 'Person8570', 2, 'Annoying!!!', 'I am super upset. I have been using this app for a bit less than a year, and I loved it! I was kind of disappointed that you couldn’t pause your timers, so I was super happy when that feature was finally added! But now, you have to pay extra money to be able to pause them!!!! Another thing I was happy about, was that it was supposed to be a one time payment, with no ads. It was mostly like that until now… Forest. Has. Ads!!!! My question is, WHY? Why have the ads? Why make you pay to get rid of them when you payed just to get the app?? Why make you pay to pause your timers??? This is the worst. 😡', '5.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-02T13:46:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14131889813', 'Tokiohgal', 1, 'Where are my trees?', 'Yall keep removing the trees I buy with coins every damn update! Fix this bs', '5.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-01T09:46:15-07:00'),
