((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14116259125', '1 Otis', 5, 'Let’s do this!', 'The app really makes it fun to focus on!', '5.17.0', 'us', '2026-05-28T09:34:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14113036427', 'Abbyhy1225', 5, 'Huge help in productivity', 'I don’t know why this works so well, but it really does. I used this app throughout college and now four years post-grad when I need to be productive, and it’s been so helpful for me. I highly recommend this app and the premium features are worth it as well. The only thing I don’t like (this is a relatively new feature) is that you can pause the timer and take a break. I feel it defeats the purpose, and I feel myself “cheating” because I can. I also know I should have self control, but I obviously don’t or I wouldn’t need this app.', '5.17.0', 'us', '2026-05-27T12:49:27-07:00'),
