((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='866450515'), '14093815185', 'A$AP_Erocky', 5, 'Very fun and cute', 'This app is engaging enough that I’m actually sticking with it! I do hope they add some additional features like being able to place you trees in particular spots, maybe in one master plot for the whole year? I like how the longer focus sessions get you cooler trees. If they made it so that the 2hr session was actually taller/bigger that would be cool', '5.16.5', 'us', '2026-05-22T11:02:42-07:00'),
