((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1499198946'), '14258659112', '🩷❤️🏐🩰', 5, 'LOVEEE', 'I have been using this app for over a year now and I love it so much. It helps me plan my day a lot easier than any other way. One thing I do wish was that you could just write things down without worrying about putting a time down. Thats my only complaint tho and I love every other thing about structured!', '4.5.1', 'us', '2026-07-03T09:40:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1499198946'), '14249476825', 'Snap089', 5, 'Love this App!', 'I use it DAILY. My whole life’s structure depends on this app. It’s simple, smooth, visually appealing, yet customizable with fun icons and colors. I’m able to keep up with reoccurring bills, when they are due (that I might forget about), appointments, parties, work schedule, etc. Everything!!! Highly recommend.', '4.5.1', 'us', '2026-07-01T06:24:40-07:00'),
