((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14266266744', 'Laurraine L', 5, 'Love Finch.', 'In this busy world, spending time with my little birb makes me smile, stop and think about my reactions during the day. I find myself repeating positive affirmations, breathing instead of getting angry, moving when I don’t feel like doing anything. It’s cute and helps me pay more attention to self care and self love.', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-05T07:47:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14266263774', '⭐️Books⭐️', 5, 'Awesome app', 'It’s an awesome app I think that you should be able to share reflections with friends and be able to find your past reflections easier. Other than that it’s awesome. I also wish there were some games you could play with your birb . Then I would give it 10/5 stars!', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-05T07:46:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14265932595', 'Raven remling', 5, 'Love this app', 'This is such a great app if you wanna start to do things you haven’t done in a while. This app helps me be able to take care of myself 10/10 definitely recommend.', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-05T06:10:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14265397143', 'haybay1120', 5, 'Helped me', 'This app has helped me so much by staying organized and helped me think and stay on track it helps with people who has been through a lot or has depression or anxiety or people who has hurt themselves i recommend this app completely!', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-05T03:01:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14264856796', 'Kat.Mm', 5, 'LUV SO MUCH!', 'I love this app so so much! It has truly helped me through hard times. It’s helped me build goals and keep them. I couldn’t recommend this more. At first I was scared I’d run out of things to do in the app and would lose motivation and commitment but the monthly events and new locations keep my curiosity and enthusiasm alive for not only helping myself but helping my finch. (her name is Mercury, I love her) One little thing, I wish I had the option to choose how I log my feelings. I want to be able to pick between doing it everytime I log in verse clicking on something separate in the corner of my screen to log it. I often forget it’s there and miss when it used to be there when I opened the app. Other than that I really can only say good things! Thank you so much finch team and guardians 🧡', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T23:22:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14264819618', 'Ocean blackout', 5, 'Finch', 'I love this app! That’s all you need to know.', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T23:07:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14264216824', 'Madi & Peanut', 5, 'From Madi & Peanut', 'I’m happy to say that my birb Peanut and I are doing amazing on our mental health journey! This is an amazing app! I love waking up each morning to gratitude from Peanut and my friends, plus checking off all of my daily tasks while having fun! I’m happy to sponsor 1 membership each month and I definitely recommend the app!', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T18:55:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14264136644', 'Sweet Ladie', 5, 'Finch', 'Such a good way to get into a good habit', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T18:22:46-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14263879766', 'Katsuki_bakugo808', 5, 'Helps so much love it', 'I love this so much it help with my personality and it is so cute the only thing that could get better is a little longer names but other than that perfect', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T16:35:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14263816049', 'iPhone 5s user 2026', 2, 'I’m Done With This App', 'It runs slow on my iPhone 5s which is weird because Geometry Dash a game that looks better in graphics can run really well on my iPhone and this is mainly just a check list app and I just realized I can save my time and storage (because my iPhone is 16GB which is too low but I use it anyway) by using the Apple Notes app or the Apple Reminders app and I hate daily streaks like they do work well for getting the user to come back and do their check list but if you forget then remember when you need to go to sleep you have to stay up longer which isn’t healthy and no matter what you might lose your streak anyway if you go out without the device that has the app on and yes it does give you the chance to continue the current streak if you miss one day and come back but then after the first time of missing one day if you miss it again you need to pay a lot using fake money also I don’t pay for stuff normally with real money so I find it annoying the fact when I go in the shop (non real money one) there’s an ad for the membership saying to claim the free week trial and I also hate when app’s have this invite friends for awards system as it’s a trick to make you tell others to get it and it’s kinda like making your audience the ad of this to their friends and I do love the birds in this app and will miss them for a bit but I think it’s for the better if I stop using this app.', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T16:09:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14263769475', 'Nicknamelsjfi', 5, 'Tysm', 'This helps my self care', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T15:48:42-07:00'),
