((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14263225592', 'Lady Diane SB', 5, 'Accountability', 'Finch allows me to make myself accountable for activities I need to get done. I can add goals so I won’t forget they need to be completed. I get to have a bit of light hearted dress up for a character bird and design a home for it that helps me keep returning to check completed goals off from my list.', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T12:16:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14263164278', 'Ace🪽', 5, 'Amazing app', 'If you really want to get yourself into feeling better and doing things while taking care of a pet then this app is for you. My second time using it and it helps :)', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T11:55:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14263154727', 'yuyigybihgbbjhk', 4, 'I wish you can say over at the end', 'I love it I just don’t wish that you can start over again because if so, that like you can like pick out another color over again like but still keep your goals. I wish there was because I’m actually finished everything and built for. I really want to let go back another color and then have a baby again, but we’re still keeping my progress and stuff just like it’s a baby that I got a new color and stuff like I still wanna be able to keep my clothing and the curse like the rainbow crystals and the micro pet that I have it’s just you know so that like you can keep going over and over and over again I also wish that like you could like go into your future dreams so that you can see what your friend is dreaming about before you go take a nice little rest', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T11:51:51-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14262825038', 'Lilygammer', 5, 'Finch', 'Supper cute unlocked soo many things and how is it only #30 on the chart?!', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T10:04:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14262792225', 'Balib2000', 1, 'Thanks guys', 'The app has helped me get my goals done and they even offered me the finch plus subscription for free cause I couldn’t afford it. Thank you Finch.', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T09:55:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14262511334', '𝓕𝓸𝓻𝓽 𝓜𝓬𝓜𝓾𝓻𝓻𝓪𝔂', 5, 'Do you know why?', 'It helps me', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T08:31:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14262438184', 'BreSellsATL', 1, 'Crashes over and over', 'I’ve had to restart my birb and all my goals over 7 times now. Then the next day get a message that it crashed and resets. Worst experience with an app I’ve ever had.', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T08:10:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14262293012', 'Lily riser', 5, 'I love it', 'I love this app it has helped my daily routine and my mental health a lot💗💗', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T07:29:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14262216943', '☺️🥸😖😭🥺🥵🤯😣🤪😛☹️', 5, 'Finch self care', 'Finch is just… wow it is something that I actually wake up and do my goals. It’s been great and I used to have it on day 104 and I’m starting fresh on day 3 today’s', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T07:08:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14262179248', 'This review is for ideas', 5, 'Amazing amazing amazing', 'For someone who has strees or anxiety, anger problems, like me this app is helping me with those problems. I already have a journal but this helps me with writing more often. I recommend getting this app. Cool features is that my friends and I can share or the stuff so your not alone your with your friends!! 👍✨✨', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T06:58:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1528595748'), '14262096445', 'Ang Conlon', 5, 'Cute and simple', 'Cute way to stay on track and celebrate small wins.', '3.73.185', 'us', '2026-07-04T06:34:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14268517259', '"De"', 4, 'Stumbling', 'I just stumbled across this app. I’ve only invested 1 day so far, but it is guiding me through activities to increase my mental & physical health. I find it very interesting that at least 2 practices suggested are 2 that I have noticed from my past that bear repeating. I’m looking forward to further insights with noticeable improvements.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-05T20:50:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14268388814', '111637384&58393!', 1, 'Scam', 'Charged me $40 and I never signed up. My account says “free account”. Impossible to cancel a membership or contact anyone with all these asinine pop-ups. Run away', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-05T19:59:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14268290984', 'Kshfjsmxhfkal', 1, 'Terrible Experience', 'Total scam. First of all, ridiculously annoying user experience. They make you sit through all sorts of weird animations before you can even interact with app. Secondly, super shady how they make it so hard to cancel. “Delete Account” is not a cancellation - learned that when I was charged $40 a month after I thought I had cancelled. The ‘Contact Us’ link leads to a 404 page. I finally figured out that you can only cancel through their website, and even then I have received no confirmation that my subscription was actually cancelled.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-05T19:19:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14267906576', 'Briggy74', 5, 'Happy Customer', 'I’m only on day three but I’m really enjoying this app. It’s not magic but it really holds me accountable for following through on the things that I want to accomplish. It’s a gentle nudge to be productive and I can say that I accomplished more over the past three days than I have in the last six months. This is gold to me. Highly recommend!', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-05T16:52:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14262966701', 'PPA789', 1, 'Huge Scam!', 'I had the app for a couple days and it did not work for me. Totally fine! Canceled my subscription it MADE me start when I first got the app. No problem. Couple months later I get charged $80! Hadn’t used the app in those months- in fact, it was not even on my phone! Re-logged in, it didn’t remember me, tried canceling again, but there was nothing to cancel. Just got charged another $50 this morning… so I logged in AGAIN. It remembered me this time, thankfully. I tried canceling again, but lo and behold I DID NOT HAVE A SUBSCRIPTION TO CANCEL! So they are just charging me random amounts randomly, it seems. So beware when using and signing up for this app. I don’t know if it’s just me, or if this is something more people are dealing with, but I’m currently trying to figure out how to get them to stop taking my money when I don’t even have the app.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-04T10:49:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14262152932', 'Nurses Know', 2, 'Annoying updates', 'Loved the app for years. However, recent updates with annoying advertisements after every screen change and AI helper bubble that glows in corner interfere with use and enjoyment of app. Gave it 2 stars since I enjoy the app but not the recent changes', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-04T06:50:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14259463631', 'That’s-me', 1, 'Lame', 'I feel tricked into a free trial, then challenges to unsubscribe (many steps and multiple platforms). I don’t even know what this app does.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-03T14:00:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14258950253', 'Erin loves this app', 2, 'don’t download', 'this app is a scam !!!! takes money without your permission', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-03T11:07:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14254078761', 'ABCDUser123', 1, 'Hard to cancel subscription and continued to be charged after I canceled', 'Beware - the subscription to this app is hard to cancel and I continued get charged following my cancellation. Maybe they count on people with ADHD getting distracted while looking for where to cancel the subscription? I don’t know but do yourself a favor and pass on this app. Edit: two months after contacting Fabulous and my bank to cancel the subscription they are still trying to charge my account!', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-02T07:58:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14253543969', 'kcgoudie', 1, 'Scam', 'This app is 100% a scam and the business uses deceptive practices to force you into a subscription that is very hard to cancel, and once you cancel they still charge you. Go look up fabulous on google and look at all the reddit posts.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-02T05:34:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14252499884', 'BirdCat🐱🐤', 1, 'UNCANCELLABLE SUBSCRIPTION', 'This is genuinely such a money scam. The app itself is decent—albeit no different from something much cheaper—but has an intentionally confusing subscription service. As it stands, despite having canceled the charges and repeatedly reporting them, I am getting charged $40 a month and may need to get a new card. I wish I could sue but this app already took all my money.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-01T23:11:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14252084627', 'S. Phelps', 1, 'Fraudulent App', 'I was charged 4 times in one day! 1 charge of $29.99 and three for $39.99. Have no idea about the quality of the app itself because I NEVER USED IT! There are so many claims of fraud, I don’t know how this app still exists! Reply to your stupid response: Not a “misunderstanding “ but a SCAM! My bank refunded these charges because they were fraudulent. These were not “unexpected charges”. Instead of being dismissive of my complaint try explaining 4 charges in one day.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-01T20:27:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14251407958', 'sal_vk', 1, 'Doesn’t help with habit building and they are frauds.', 'I tried the app because it said it helps develop habits based on behavioral science practices that were developed in Duke University. Well that is false. First- the home screen has so many design elements and information that feels overwhelming. Rather than focus on developing the habit, you get more mentally loaded trying to find the said habit to track on the screen which is counterproductive when cultivating new habit(s). Second- as far as I can tell the company is based out of Paris, which begs the question, if this was developed by Duke’s Lab then why headquarter it outside of US. And finally, even if you cancel the within the free trial window, they keep charging you the subscription fee. So not only do you not end up cultivating the new habit you wanted because of how overwhelming the screen feels, you also end up getting frustrated because of their business practices. Please be advised before you start using their services.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-01T16:20:51-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14250974251', 'Ashleykanderson', 1, 'FRAUD/SCAM', 'I was excited to try this app out, even paid the asked for amount to set up an account. But then I was hit with back to back screens disguised as a welcome slideshow with charges each time you clicked through. I wasn’t asked to confirm payment once, just billed. I didn’t even know until my cards fraud department blocked a third charge. Reached out to the company and of course they said it was non refundable. They literally hid upgrades and charges and billed me without asking for payment confirmation over and over. Then I also got hit with an international service charge on each “upgrade” which also wasn’t disclosed. So many people have called them out for scamming online, I wish I had read about it beforehand. So be careful pushing any buttons on this app! Could lead to a $40 charge you aren’t told or alerted about. I never really do reviews but I have my cards fraud department all up in this because this is insane. I would recommend the app to an enemy 👍🏼', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-01T13:40:53-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14249817252', 'Sweetserenity753', 5, 'Awesome sweet gentle reminders for good health', 'Not annoying. Great gentle prods to drink more water. Exactly what I need. Encourages good self care.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-01T07:55:46-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14249135634', 'Haze4Dayz12', 1, 'Scam', 'I was charged 3 times after I canceled before the free trial. I have tried contacting customer service to return my funds, no response.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-01T04:45:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14249070436', 'Hunter1010', 3, 'Lots of Graphics', 'The app is very useful for habit tracking and coaching. However, I get very frustrated trying to check off the items in my routine and having to wait for multiple 10 second graphics that play out every time I press a checkbox. There needs to be a setting that limits the forced interruptions with using the app. Please! I want to be able to check off my list in 5 seconds not several minutes.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-07-01T04:25:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14245729700', 'Januh', 1, 'Ended up paying $30 for a trial and still did not have access to the full app.', 'I signed up thinking it would be $10 to try for a month. They tricked me into paying $30 and apparently adding other apps but they don’t even tell you how to access the other apps to try. I decided to use it just now and it doesn’t even let me access certain things like add a new habit to my routine. It says I need to sign up, but I’ve already lost $30 signing up the first time around. And then I’ve tried going through Settings and looking for a contact to call them and they make it impossible to try to get a hold of them.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-30T09:04:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14245283579', 'arc110', 4, 'Day 2—still working', 'I came back for day 2!', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-30T07:09:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14242154693', 'Nvh9', 1, 'Will not cancel!', 'I told them that I did not order this and I do not want it. Apparently this did not translate into cancellation and they keep on charging me!', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-29T12:22:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14240846218', 'Esteelewis', 1, 'Won’t let me sign in or cancel', 'This appears to be an expensive scam. You download one app and it auto signs you up for a bunch more. Then you can’t sign in and can’t cancel', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-29T06:10:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14237842876', 'Francisco22997', 1, 'Super Sketchy', 'I had a subscription for this app and it has been canceled for a while and they are still charging me. I had to go to my bank and get a new card because of this. This app is terrible and this is super super sketchy.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-28T11:16:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14235088881', 'Kwoinak', 1, 'What a scam', 'This app signs you up for multiple bundles and makes getting rid of them really difficult. The app is hard to navigate forcing you to go through multiple screens before just letting you access your account. Do not sign up for this service.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-27T19:21:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14234486679', 'Leyell', 5, 'Has a different vibe…', 'From other apps I’ve tried before. Gentle but persistent', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-27T15:34:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14233870134', 'Awsomegab', 1, 'Make sure you cancel your membership before deleting your account', 'I hit the button to delete my account. Yet, I was still charged afterwards. I feel like it’s incredibly misleading to not end the paid subscription when you make the change to delete your account. That, or at least make a disclaimer of it. Something along the lines of “Make sure you cancel your subscription before deleting your account” would’ve sufficed. I was able to restore my account and cancel my subscription but it’s incredibly deceptive, and worthy of making a complaint to the FTC (or the appropriate agency) because of how misleading it is not not cancel the subscription when you supposedly cancel your account. Also, this isn’t even worth 40 bucks a month. Maybe 20, if that.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-27T11:47:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14232661836', 'BOOM_BOOM-pow!', 5, 'Very beautiful and peaceful', 'This app is actually very motivating when you use it properly. I’ve made it a habit to check this app in the morning before other social media, and I can say it really does help start the day better on a more healthier and positive note.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-27T05:47:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14232461856', 'cc_cookie1', 1, 'Do NOT download', 'I wanted to try the app just too see if I like it or if it helps before I commit to it, it asked “what amount I think their workers deserve” I just put a dollar so I can get into the app and just try it out little did I know they started a weekly $50 subscription!!! Not only was the app hard to navigate, it also asks soooo many pre questions anyone with ADHD would NOT want to sit though their entire exam type questionnaire. If you still want it, download and use with caution…. ALSOOO it’s so hard to cancel and even after cancelling they will still try to charge your card. AND after canceling and deleting your account and information with them, they STILL will try to charge you… they obviously also store you’r information who knows what else they do with it.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-27T04:43:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14231674243', 'Ctgb', 5, 'Makes habits automatic', 'The checklists, short inspirational coaching pieces, visuals and sound all work together to make new habits part of existing routines, amd over time they really do become automatic. This is one of my favorite apps, and there are always new goals and milestones to celebrate', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-26T23:47:29-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14228639279', 'luciferswaterfall', 3, 'Annoyed with the streak animation', 'I like this app, but lately I’ve been incredibly annoyed having to wait for the streak animation to complete every day, every time I do something. I need an option to turn that off so I can see what’s next on the list without waiting or having to close and reopen the app to make it slightly quicker to go to the next task. This isn’t Duolingo, and feels like they’re trying to copy it. I liked the app better before this was a feature.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-26T06:25:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14224603928', 'mommamia247', 5, 'Recommend by therapist', 'Just started this morning and already feel sense of calm like maybe I can do this!', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-25T06:25:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14224273659', 'arkofcovenant', 1, 'Forced subscription', 'This app signed me up for a subscription without my approval. During the onboarding I couldn’t even follow it because I was so focused on figuring out if I was subscribed and how to cancel it. There’s no way this app is worth $40 a month. Even with crippling adhd I couldn’t vibe code something just as good in a week for free', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-25T04:45:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14222936125', 'IvaPic', 1, 'Scam', 'I paid the one dollar inicial fee to try the subscription for the first time. They charged me and I can’t enter the account. I searched online and many people have the same issue. They have been known to charge people multiple times after cancellation.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-24T19:30:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14222831583', 'Ajpete97', 1, 'Scam', 'Canceled multiple times, and I’m still being charged. I’m about to press charges, because this is ridiculous.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-24T18:51:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14221658632', 'Gemi💖', 5, 'Helpful', 'The app is so helpful and love the graphics and the cute reminders to complete daily habits', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-24T11:40:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14221145502', '111ellie111', 3, 'The app is too busy', 'I really wanted to like this, the graphics are pretty, the idea of the journeys is great, but the app is so busy that it makes it harder to actually keep focused on the habits themselves. My ideal experience would provide the step by step habit building suggestions and then make it easy to actually check off and track the completion rate, not take me into multiple screens or bury the checklist functionality under coaching prompts. There should also be a way to tone down the cheerleading and remove coaching nags. All in all, I find this too overwhelming to use, but maybe this approach works for some people.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-24T09:00:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14220331599', 'AppleUser6037', 1, 'AI Slop', 'Overwhelming navigation to the point that it’s barely usable. Subscribed me to the same plan twice and cancelling was a pain.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-24T05:00:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14220122715', 'Liv loves animals', 3, 'Free trial', 'Scam. They charged me even though I cancelled my free trial. ***Update after contacting them I was issued a refund.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-24T03:47:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14217678622', 'MamaJ2K2', 5, 'Fabulous is fabulous!', 'Just a great way to incrementally incorporate healthy habits. I’ve tried a few habit apps, but this one just seems to work best for me. I’m not a Type-A but wish I was - this app gently moves me in that direction.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-23T11:24:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14217652559', 'Txhthhrjfj', 5, 'Habits', 'Wonderful to keep me on track.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-23T11:15:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14215192055', 'Dancepook', 1, 'Ghost charges', 'You guys keep trying to charge my card twice! One for $29.99 and the other for $39.99. I ended my subscription literally the same day I started the free trial. I told my bank you are a fraud and they have blocked you from trying to charge. I still see you trying because I get a decline notice. STOP CHARGING ME YOU FRAUDS', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-22T19:52:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14213102615', 'The SweetBaboo', 1, 'Confusing & Stressful', 'I’m going to cancel this after an hour. It just wasn’t for me. I think it’s supposed to be guided, but it feels convoluted and unpleasant.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-22T07:40:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14210193310', 'Fit pro 1991', 5, 'Fabulous works', 'I love this app it has helped me to track my emotions and what I’m doing every day.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-21T12:13:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14208952476', 'Adamsonome', 1, 'I feel completely misled by this app.', 'During onboarding, I selected a 1 euro free trial, shortly afterwards I was charged 40 euros for 1:1 coaching that I neither wanted or knowingly agreed to purchase I have already cancelled all subscription and contacted support requesting a refund but this experience has left me with a negative impression What frustrates me the most is the use of hidden subscription, upsells or confusing billing practices that make people for services they don’t want or intended to buy. Transparency should be a priority especially when handling customers payment information I will not recommend this app base on my experience and I will do everything within my power to get a refund for a service I have not used', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-21T05:48:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14206602674', 'Bunny38833', 3, 'Major headache but i got refund', 'I was able to get a refund. Warning: TO SAVE YOUR HEADACHE, DO NOT SIGN UP THROUGH INSTAGRAM!!! I got charged twice on the premium plans! But thankfully customer service actually gave me a refund. Ty', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-20T13:44:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14205938717', 'LOL Skinker', 5, 'Baby steps work!', 'In the last two weeks, I have already been more successful at keeping a routine than I have in the previous 30 years. I recommend this app to get you started.', '20.1.1', 'us', '2026-06-20T09:57:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14205693324', 'hkwoow72&@92', 1, 'It’s so sad that an app meant to help is hurting people', 'I signed up for Fabulous app and then couldn’t afford the 39.99. For some reason the app didn’t have a place for me to cancel. Some kind of error within my account. So the app declined a refund. I said okay there’s nothing I can do but stop charging me moving forward. Now months later, I have another fraudulent charge and I no longer even use the app. How is this helpful? My daughter’s birthday is tomorrow and my bank is saying I can’t have access to my card because they have to send a new one at this point. That will take a week. How is that helpful? How is this contributing to my wellbeing or mental health. This app used to be upstanding but now it’s just fraudulent. What you are doing is disgusting. With all life stressors, people don’t need another one. I suggest no one uses this app.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-20T08:42:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14205388435', 'EF/GA', 5, 'So far, so good', 'New user, enjoying it so far. Easy to navigate.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-20T07:13:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14205068373', '2dopefurreal', 2, 'Well designed but deceptive pay structure', 'Beware this app lures you with a survey. Then it tells you to pay what you want for the survey results but that payment is actually a trial for a subscription. You never get survey results; it just directs you to begin using the app to justify charging you at the end of the trial period.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-20T05:35:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1203637303'), '14203938880', '76Comet', 1, 'Ridiculous, offers of free trial buggy', 'The signup process is completely broken. I clicked through from IG, opened in browser, took the survey, got to the payment page and selected $1 for the trial. Tried to Apple Pay, which said it went through, but declined. Tried 4 times. Got email saying I had a 30 day free trial waiting for me. Clicked through from there, got to payment page again, same issue. Decided to download app directly. Did survey again, got to Another payment page, this time only giving me a one week trial. So now you’ve told me I have 30 days, then two weeks, now 1 week. And want another payment. Impossible to get started! I already spent 30 min on this.', '21.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-19T22:00:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14258521185', 'Bjamin101', 5, 'Simple and powerful', 'Great tool for daily intentions and reflections. Love the customization.', '2026.13', 'us', '2026-07-03T09:01:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14240559223', 'Riah Gruenke', 5, 'Amazing app', 'I’m curious and I love this app the quotes are so inspirational and I love writing so the prompts are so helpful', '2026.12', 'us', '2026-06-29T04:49:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14231365525', 'MDBrown891', 5, 'Expressing yourself', 'I love being able to write out whatever I want without judgement or shame and feeling better writing it out.', '2026.12', 'us', '2026-06-26T21:42:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14229726214', 'Fonseneca', 2, 'The app locks you in', 'Doesn’t let you delete your account', '2026.12', 'us', '2026-06-26T11:38:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14205877894', 'Carlabellag', 5, 'Wish that if was fully free but most features are', 'Beautiful, minimalistic design, with it was free since it has truly helped my mental health so much but I really cant spend on it due to my budget. Byt u can do daily check ins and all. Except appearance features and personalization is not accessible without premium. But regardless I SWEAR BY THIS APP.', '2026.12', 'us', '2026-06-20T09:38:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14183385555', 'ljrc1', 5, 'Love it', 'I just wish the desktop version for windows was decent. It doesn’t do much of anything and doesn’t really sync well', '2026.12', 'us', '2026-06-14T15:08:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14182069994', 'ADHDdiver', 5, 'Best journaling for ADHD', 'This helps me to stay on track with journaling and checking in with myself and how I feel. It makes it an easy task and gives me a win each time I complete an entry. It makes it feel attainable and then helps me feel better.', '2026.12', 'us', '2026-06-14T08:02:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14166058135', 'Amazing doodle', 5, 'Stoic sets the bar high and delivers.', 'I’ve used this app for several years, and it’s truly excellent. It’s a great tool for journaling, intention setting, reflection, and meditation, and I love how it collects so many resources in one place.', '2026.12', 'us', '2026-06-10T06:29:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14163460493', 'AGrainOfSalt...]', 4, 'Great work. Would love to see more details!', 'This review is a list of a few examples that I would love to experience from this app. More pictures. Fun tests. Mood ring. Scream analysis. Put more money on activities and alternative methods of understanding the client non verbally.', '2026.12', 'us', '2026-06-09T12:59:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14153781940', '$$JAC$$', 1, 'All about the $', 'I was under the impression I could use what I felt necessary and each time a new prompt showed up, the end result was signing up for a subscription. If you don’t decline the prompts (even the simple questions you think are designed to help you), I the next page is something else asking for money. I checked this app out for my kid but I will not suggest it for him.', '2026.12', 'us', '2026-06-07T01:37:51-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14148893479', 'Izzy 0921', 5, 'My Lifestyle of many Addictions eventually became mental health issues and helped me stay focused in', 'Staying sober and safe!!!!', '2026.12', 'us', '2026-06-05T18:31:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14135152837', 'Amori', 1, 'Subscription Spam Kills UX', 'As a first-time user who just wanted to learn more about and explore the app, the first five or ten minutes with it was awful and frustrating. I just wanted to see the interface and determine whether or not I might like it. Instead, I got hit with a bunch of popups, subscription paywalls, rating requests, and more *constantly* within the first five minutes — to the point that this “mental health companion” app was actively fighting me while I was trying to figure it out. I get that subscriptions are important. I don’t even mind paying for something I like. But when I’m spammed so much in the first few minutes that I can’t even figure it out, the ask comes across as greedy and unhelpful. Once I cleared the constant popups, I tried to click around and gain a better understanding of how the app functions. Nope: More popups and paywalls. Based on other reviews, some users are having better luck. I still don’t know if this app is for me … but after all the paywall spam, I have no interest in continuing. Devs, please consider implementing a better onboarding flow for users and asking for money *after* someone has a chance to get their bearings.', '2026.11', 'us', '2026-06-02T06:14:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14130300799', 'jellybeandragon', 3, 'Free Version ain’t it', 'I had this many years ago and the free version was still great! It’s frustrating how it now is so basic and not worthwhile unless you have premium.', '2026.11', 'us', '2026-06-01T00:48:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14129200405', 'Nickname333iloveicloud', 4, 'Only one thing holding back from 5⭐️', 'Okay, I’ve had this app for a little over 3 years. And it’s incredible. I remember wanting to be able to write down what I was actually thinking/feeling; However, it has become some so much more than just a hobby or way to organize my thoughts ( though it’s pretty good for those too). I use stoic so much and it’s so freaking good. I feel better every time and I’ve actually seen the app improve over the years. I could go on and on about how it’s amazing and great and how you should download it, but I feel I should also mention what hold this app back. And that would be iCloud. I use the app off premium and it’s still amazing but I can’t put it on more than one devise and I can’t save the entries to my iPads iCloud. And after all these years It would be so depressing to loose all that writing. So yeah. I’m probably going to go and get premium. But if you think that you might want to be able to keep and re-read what you write and not want to pay around 40 bucks a year (there’s also other deals and offers just to be clear and truthful) then this apps probably not for you. And honestly, I don’t know if I would have downloaded it 3 years ago if I had known about this. But again, I want to emphasize that is is like their ONLY issue. Everything else is so perfect and nice and works great whether you want to get all your emotions out, plan out your mornings, or forget about it and come back every 3 months and write a bit ( or a lot Yk). What I’m saying is that it has space for everyone. Unless you want to be able to keep your own writing for free or write across multiple devices……….', '2026.11', 'us', '2026-05-31T17:04:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14108695624', 'Sunshine Sunflower E73V3z', 5, 'Grounded and clear', 'I find stoic to help me feel grounded and calmer than without it. I now know I have a lot of important things to get finished so no more Facebook for a while:).', '2026.11', 'us', '2026-05-26T09:21:45-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14106688807', 'bloopitydoopity', 5, 'Insightful', 'The prompts help reflection while keeping it simple based.', '2026.11', 'us', '2026-05-25T20:11:22-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14105087760', 'EraEjecta', 4, 'Great for Introspection', 'This app is great for self reflection, especially if you’re looking for constructive feedback on it. It’s helping me grow and better control my emotions.', '2026.11', 'us', '2026-05-25T10:06:27-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14100750438', 'Witchanpug', 5, 'Just give this a try .', 'App is down to make you think. About', '2026.11', 'us', '2026-05-24T07:16:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14095267131', 'GMRjr75', 3, 'Good app. Prompts repeat.', 'I like the app. It does encourage me to be more diligent with my journaling. It would be nice if the prompts didn’t repeat so often.', '2026.11', 'us', '2026-05-22T20:25:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14091651922', 'Ruben Gallegos', 5, 'Fml', 'Wonderful piece to add to the machine', '2026.11', 'us', '2026-05-21T21:16:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14084636481', 'Legato Stacatto', 5, 'Truly Insightful', 'I rarely review apps but there are about 5 apps on the App Store that are worth mentioning. This is one of the 5. Stoic is one of the apps where I can confidently assume there were multiple talented developers with varying perspectives and skills involved, which ultimately resulted in high levels of insight. Most of the features inspire ideas, self reflection , and action. All while giving you choices and maintaining intuitive UI for users. I find that amazing and worth a review!', '2026.11', 'us', '2026-05-19T23:32:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14080827323', 'anonymous_e_wg', 5, 'Stoic', 'I wanted something that would clear my mind, This app has done just that, I wish I could say more.', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-18T21:41:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14079195963', 'Nickname333iloveicloud', 5, 'Rly great', 'I downloaded this app a little over 3 years ago and I can’t express how much I love it. The prompts, the options for writing, the quotes. It’s all so easy to understand and navigate and even if it doesn’t sound like writing what happened today down, or journaling about what you wish you could have said, or whatever it is that’s going on in your life will help, speaking from experience IT DOES. And this app is perfect for that. My only complaint is that premium is needed ignorer to have stoic across multiple devices or even save the entries to my iCloud. And honestly, if I had realized this 3 years ago and known how much those entries would mean to me today I would’ve thought twice about using Stoic instead of something else.', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-18T10:33:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14072474444', 'Puma Station', 5, 'Excellent Personal Development Option', 'I am very saturated with ai and related technology. I needed an option to help relieve stress and digitally detox. I found Stoic through one of my AI options. I use it everyday and during my much needed breaks. I highly recommend.', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-16T14:42:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14069375065', 'Chri$tina@2987', 5, 'Great app', 'Motivation', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-15T19:37:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14068316441', 'Sprodigality', 1, 'Did not want to extend trial. Does not give refunds.', 'I wanted to try it out. I never used the app. They charged me $100 and will not give a refund. They say oh it’s not our fault because Apple handles al the billing. We can’t do anything about it. That is BS, unethical and terrible business practice.', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-15T12:36:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14067558200', 'another like you', 5, 'Most needed', 'I need to write . I am hoping this will make me feel better', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-15T08:22:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14058534380', 'elixabth', 1, 'money', 'mental health that everyone is talking about, you ended up charging and making business… not good should be free', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-12T20:44:31-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14045342401', 'The Real Gavin Mahaley', 5, 'Tiny magic', 'There''s a lot to explore in this app and I know that I haven''t even scratched the surface, but there''s some tiny magic in it that keeps me coming back every day.', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-09T07:16:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14044989253', 'philshafer', 5, '#REALMANTALK/mindset', 'Step by step as I use different features I am vey impressed with content and how it brings peace would like to hashtag stoic on my content which I’m currently in development PHIL@60XL/REBUILD', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-09T05:26:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14041253636', 'SlimJones13', 5, 'Such a helpful tool', 'I have been using this app for a couple years now and it is such a great tool. The meditation timer, the prompts, and the customization work so well.', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-08T04:48:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14020976827', 'KingDawgs', 5, 'Simple in design but powerful', 'I need something like stoic. to help me develop a practice of journaling. I am almost to 60 days straight and I have never been able to do that with other apps or manual practices. The mood tracking is huge for me. The only thing I wish I knew how to do was get prompts to address yesterday’s journal, but they have a feature request option so hoping this gets implemented before too long. Highly recommend.', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-05-02T11:07:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14009482134', 'Cyro Paws', 1, 'AI is biased and bad for LGBTQ users', 'The AI is horrible for LGBTQ users. An app all about journaling, where LGBTQ users often need it more, shouldn’t be discriminatory towards them. This is the last thing I want to be seeing in my journal, and it’s horrible for your mental health unless you’re a straight white Christian.', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-29T07:45:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '14007710219', 'SammieKamb120', 4, 'It asked the same questions over and over', 'It asked the same questions over and over', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-28T18:48:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13999019018', 'the nicknames i want are gone', 5, 'Reflection', 'It’s a great way to reflect on your stress, and the question prompts really make you reflect on how you deal with things, and ways to consider different ways to help yourself.', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-26T06:43:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13997744468', 'uhh yeahhh', 5, 'it''s pretty good', 'i like it it''s good for mental health and keeping a steady routine', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-25T21:29:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13993665498', 'Journalingaubrey rauses', 5, 'Mental health', 'Journaling', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-24T17:40:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13989526128', 'jessmess443', 5, 'My CBT savior', 'I am a student with ADD and a mood disorder which I treat with medication but therapy has never been particularly helpful for me. These daily journals and prompts truly help me regulate my moods and thoughts better than any other journaling system I’ve ever used, and I’ve dished out lots in the past for executive style, leather bound detailed planners. This app is a wonderful toolbox for anyone to use, but I particularly recommend this to neurodivergent users. Unless this app drastically changes for the worse, I will be a lifelong user. Thank you so much for this inclusive app that makes my life more manageable. I also love the sleek design style that is non-distracting, and that they support Dyslexia font. Much love <3', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-23T12:12:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13989108597', 'KunFuGreggy', 5, 'The one and only', 'Been using for literal years, not a single complaint, does everything I need it to and more, gives quotes and offers nice prompts for reflection, if this app ever shut down genuinely don’t know what I would do ❤️ been using since 2022', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-23T09:36:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13988771951', 'Jancroque', 5, 'Sin Stoic comenzaría todos mis dias abrumado', 'Uso Stoic desde hace 2 años y ha sido una parte esencial de mi rutina diaria. Cada vez que despierto, por mas abrumado que me siento el dedicar los primeros minutos del dia a meditar o hacer un diario me ayudan a mantenerme centrado. Esta app es genial para aquellas personas que necesitamos un poco de estructura para poder hacer ejercicios de cuidado mental personal. Estoy muy agradecido de tener esta app.', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-23T07:41:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13984635166', 'YagAttack', 5, 'The app was quickly updated!', 'Thank you for promptly updating the app!', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-22T03:39:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13980497941', 'BossBourne', 5, 'Great, well-rounded journaling app', 'Whether you’re looking to journal or need to get in a meditation, Stoic has you covered. It works well and the premium version comes with great features. It’s been an app that has helped me each day in small ways. I would highly recommend it for anyone who is looking for an app to help process the day and stay grounded in the moment.', '2026.9', 'us', '2026-04-20T21:33:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13980274443', '🤔 Lemme Ponderosa', 5, 'peace. joy. stoicism. 🌺', 'glad the launch bug was fixed, and I’m back to beginning my days – and ending my nights – and harmony', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-20T19:41:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13978841811', 'jacksw71', 5, 'Last update FIXED everything', 'Quick response by the developer to resolve an issue in the prior update!', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-20T09:41:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13978505812', 'thelittlebard', 5, 'Love this app', 'Great app! Great support team!', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-20T07:49:29-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13976046019', 'Wolflove1', 5, 'Wonderful App!', 'Best way to help me get through the day. Thank you so much for making a fantastic app!', '2026.10', 'us', '2026-04-19T13:46:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13975688555', 'Big Nimz', 1, 'Unable to open app', 'App crashes every time starting up now', '2026.9', 'us', '2026-04-19T11:35:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13974797466', 'steve2harless', 1, 'App immediately crashes', 'I downloaded this app and upon opening for the first time, it crashed. I tried again, same thing. I tried a few more times and same story. So I decided to give it another opportunity, so I deleted the app and reinstalled. Same story. Frustrating to say the least. I go to the website, and the only way to report a bug is to do it through the app. How am I supposed to report a bug if I cannot open the app?', '2026.9', 'us', '2026-04-19T06:54:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1312926037'), '13974269366', 'NikkiNicole96', 1, 'Worked great until it didn’t', 'I used the app twice a day for more than a year. Then one day it wouldn’t open. No support and nothing online helped to resolve the issue. What a disappointment.', '2026.9', 'us', '2026-04-19T03:46:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14263289461', 'rakishlyrebelbit', 5, 'The only podcast app', 'I’ve been using Overcast since the Apple podcasts app broke and stopped auto-playing the next episode, circa 2016. I’ve never needed another podcast app since. Easy to use, smart customization options, and an app creator who listens. <3', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-07-04T12:39:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14262978436', 'dgp1', 5, 'I appreciate this app', 'To the developer: thanks for caring about and always improving this app. At present, I have no notes.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-07-04T10:52:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14255996332', 'k_cap', 5, 'Great independent app', 'More intuitive than Apple podcasts app and glad it’s an alternative to the stream companies. I gave it 4 out of 5 because I think there’s always room to improve and Overcast will find those ways!', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-07-02T18:28:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14255157777', 'Liz Shayne', 5, 'Still the greatest app in existence', 'I cannot tell you how much I love this app and, even as it shifts, it’s still the app that I judge other apps by - is it as good or as feature-filled or as well designed as overcast? And so few are. It’s the best podcast app ever.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-07-02T13:19:14-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14255089451', 'Murnen', 5, 'Stable release', 'Reliable and stable. There are a few weird behaviors such as completed episodes in-deleting themselves and rewinding a few minutes.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-07-02T12:56:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14254046920', 'J Dag 134', 5, 'All day, every day', 'This app is one of the all time greats. Developer who cares, works hard, and crafts an incredible experience. So happy to pay barely more than $1/month for so many hours worth of listening.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-07-02T07:50:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14253429304', 'boyfromthedwarf9', 1, 'You can tell they don''t beta test', 'ZERO option to just play my manual queue. I want it to autoplay ZERO things outside of what I manually add to the queue. The devs only have "stop after each episode" OR "we''ll play random episodes" bc they don''t understand use cases.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-07-02T04:59:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14246740939', 'rob1sonjr', 5, 'Excellent podcast app!', 'Great podcast app, makes it easy to manage all of your favorite podcasts. I have been using Overcast for years now.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-30T14:10:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14245563512', 'cutain rods', 5, 'Leaving Crazy Town', 'Brilliant', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-30T08:21:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14240361040', 'Dp22222', 2, 'App crashes often', 'Two complaints. The app crashes often, especially if you try to fast forward. The podcasts don’t continue playing sequentially so I have to exit, scroll through 300 episodes, then find the next pod in the series.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-29T03:48:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14239366130', 'WWXXYYZZ1234', 3, 'Great app, current version has bugs', 'The current version, as of 6/28/26, does not properly delete a podcast when it is completed.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-28T20:55:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14233670321', 'Cowboy_X', 5, 'Stop looking, this is the one.', 'It’s an app by a guy — not a corporation — who just wants to make the best possible podcast app, and it shows on every level.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-27T10:42:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14229449927', 'not Rick nor Jeff', 1, 'Buggy', 'After a podcast is done, it “comes back” with a minute or two remaining.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-26T10:11:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14228883395', 'Doubtfulduck', 4, 'The best podcast app, hands down with one minor issue.', 'I’ve been using Overcast for since 2015. Seriously the best podcast app by far. Smart Speed and Voice Boost alone are worth it — they make every other podcast app unusable. It is exactly as the app’s description says: everything you need with nothing you don’t. The only issue I have is a minor one and I don’t think it’s been there forever. But I’ve noticed that when I unfollow and delete podcasts from the home screen, they will sometimes come back when the app refreshes. I assume it’s some issue between syncing the content to iCloud (which I have turned on). It’s not a dealbreaker by any means, but it’s annoying to have to delete a podcast twice, especially when you’re doing a bunch at the same time.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-26T07:31:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14221934210', 'fayfoxxhearts', 4, 'There could be something better', 'I have been using this podcast player for a few months now to regularly listen to my podcasts. It does what it strictly needs to do; it automatically downloads episodes, allows me to access those downloaded files, and keeps track of which episodes I''ve listened to. However, there are just a lot of small things which, though I can accept, make this app not entirely perfect... It is a pain to manually order a playlist and put it in any order other than when the podcast episodes released. The UI also tries to fit all three menus (podcasts, the episodes of a podcast, and the episode you''re listening to) on screen at once on the iPad, meaning they are all a bit squished and none of them get enough space; they should be separate menus, perhaps like Apple Music, where you would look at all your podcasts, click on one and see its episodes, and then see it playing in a tab below, whcih you could click on and expand. I like how it has nearly every podcast, and how they are all free, and how the ads are only banner ads and not audio ads; very respectful. I just have to imagine that this can''t possibly be the actual best podcast player; there has to be some player that does all the things this does and doesn''t have all these minor issues. In general, I would recommend it, but its claim of being the best podcast player is a strong claim and might not be true.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-24T13:12:22-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14217912741', 'kkellymac', 5, 'Natasha has a fake sneeze', 'I’ve tried to stifle a sneeze before and it was just as loud and the pressure in my eyeballs was excruciating!', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-23T12:42:38-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14215529505', 'Oh! That Guy', 3, 'I never give 5 stars', 'This app is pretty awesome. The customizations are the star here. I especially love the skip and rewind customization. I''ve recently come back and lowered it from 4 to 3 stars. You used to be able to hit a download button for any episodes and you''d have it for offline listening. An update has replaced the download button (⬇️) with the Add (+) button which I guess. only adds it to the podcast''s "set aside to listen" list. Downloaded plays faster and doesn''t rely on internet so I don''t understand why shoved the download button into a 3dot sub menu. I absolutely hate that change. Please put it back on the options line up below an episode.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-22T22:23:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14213885978', 'J.J. Maugans', 5, 'Absolutely love!!!', 'The Concept of this being free with Amy Poehler good hang makes me so freaking happy you just don’t even know! Thank you so much!', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-22T11:40:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14213265487', 'Spoon Slayer', 3, 'Was Great', 'Used to be my favorite podcatcher but as of 2026 it’s getting worse. since there is no bug report option, I guess review it is. It’s now nearly impossible to reorganize lists, and they buried that feature under the burger.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-22T08:28:31-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14205847436', 'Glionam', 5, 'As it is -VOA learning English best podcast', 'This podcast very useful you can listen to the news and then you can read it because you can have news transcripts until from previous day Thanks team', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-20T09:29:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14202009718', 'Service Goat', 2, 'Bloated and buggy', 'Used to be a great app, but now changes UI every couple of years for some reason and has become a usability nightmare. Added unneeded features like on device transcription which overheats my phone and drains battery. Constant screw ups with playback now and my audio randomly cuts out or is garbled in my headphones or loses its place and jumps back in time. I stopped my subscription and will find an alternative.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-19T10:00:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14198525529', 'jonm123', 3, 'Good features but the design sucks now', 'This used to be a really nice podcast app. However its design has degraded over the years and by now its usability, discoverability and layout are all terrible. It really needs someone to come in and clean house to apply a consistent and usable design.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-18T12:24:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14188674565', 'scootage81', 3, 'Worse since major update', 'This app got a significant update a year or so ago, I think to switch the underlying code base or platform to the more modern one for iOS. While that change should’ve been largely under the hood, in practice it seems to have introduced several bugs that have caused a significant downgrade in user experience. The two main ways the update has degraded the user experience are download failures and not retaining user changes to the order in custom playlists. The automatic downloads are frequently not fully automatic, as in, a podcast episode released overnight will appear in my playlist but often will not start downloading until I’ve opened the app. Downloads also often fail inexplicably, requiring the user to manually tap to download the episode. There is no particular rhyme or reason to which episodes fail, as it happens seemingly randomly even when I open the app and have multiple episodes from the same podcast downloading at once. It’s a crapshoot whether they all download successfully without a failure. The other very annoying bug is that if I’ve reordered the episodes in a custom playlist, the app will often undo that change, requiring me to again drag the episodes to restore my custom order. I don’t recall either of these bugs appearing before the major update, and as it’s been I think a year or more since then, it’s quite disappointing that these bugs haven’t been fixed.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-16T01:17:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14183926062', 'Crispy Cube', 1, 'Broken and unusable', 'I tried importing an OPML from another app, and nothing happened: it just didn’t import. So I went to try to add the podcasts manually by searching the directory, but the directory wouldn’t load either. I tried uninstalling and reinstalling a few times with no luck. For me, it is entirely unusable. I don’t have time to try to figure this out, going to try a different app.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-14T18:44:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14178496653', 'Zombiecreeper64596', 5, 'The best app ever', 'Yes', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-13T09:38:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14177339029', 'sjames2001', 2, 'No longer deleting finished podcasts', 'This app is increasingly glitchy. I’ve used this for ages, but now it either redownloads a series of episodes I’ve listen to, or it will erase a half finished episode. Increasingly frustrating.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-13T03:36:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14175055932', 'audreyalice09', 1, 'TRASH', 'Literally just skipping around and playing old episodes I already listened to on it, such a massive waste of time.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-12T12:23:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14170737247', 'Sphyg04', 3, 'Was a Great podcasting app', 'Previous review: The only one I use. When I use a different podcast player, I always miss the features and ease of use that this offers. Try it out for a month. You won’t go back to your other apps. I used to use this app exclusively. It was the best one that I could find. But now it won’t download anything properly and leaves me frustrated. So I am searching for something else good riddance.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-11T10:31:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14170342354', 'mbachorek1973', 5, 'Best Pod Player of ALL Players', 'After needlessly suffering the shocking lack of any useful features and attempting to quell the growing frustration over the constant interruptions of the poorly matched mandatory advertisements forced upon users, I finally abandoned Apple’s standard podcast player and have been using Overcast ever since. I absolutely LOVE everything about Overcast. I appreciate the intuitive nature of its interface, along with the simplicity of its useful organizational features. I can arrange my pods using the Playlists feature which allows one to apply a range of colors to categorize the wide-ranging and eclectic subject matter of my favorite shows (Daily Favs, Politics, Constitutional Law, Skeptical/Freethinking, Parenting, Ye Olde Timey Radio, etc). Each playlist can be updated using quick ‘click/apply’ functions (Star, Add/Remove to Playlist, etc), and can then be easily edited using drag-and-drop and/or swipe to prioritize listening. You can customize the way each individual Podcast plays: • set the playback speed (1x to 5x+) • boost voice (helps equalize voice levels of participants speakers); • reduce pauses (to close up unedited gaps in chatting) and; • set the show start and end time to skip over lengthy intros, commercials, and/or closing credits (for example, one of my fav political pods takes more than 5.5 minutes to get from the start of the show…with the intro music, to the show overview [which you can read in the Show Notes] through the first 60 second sponsor commercial, then through detailed introductions of his three guest panelists. So I set the start time at 05:30 which puts me right at the start of the first segment. My FAVORITE FEATURE is Playback Speed which can be adjusted at increments from .5 to 2x, while the pod is playing. Some of my other fav features of Overcast include: 1) applying a “Star” to an episode (allows me to go back through the lengthy episode lists of my favorite podcasts, some going back as far as 2010 with more than 700 episodes - and ‘Star’ specific episodes that I want to listen to but don’t want to presently download); and 2) Skip Ads, simply by hitting the customizable forward button. While there are auto-inserted ads in some podcast shows, there are NO mandatory non skippable ads in any of the pods that I listen to. It’s lovely to not have my shows interrupted by ‘Must Listen’ annoying and irrelevant ads. HIGHLY RECOMMEND!! You’ll love it!', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-11T08:35:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14167372086', 'Dave35753674', 5, 'Transcripts are great', 'The new transcripts are a great addition to Overcast.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-10T13:18:14-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14163845273', 'Ktfals', 3, 'Very annoying', 'I overall like the app but it keeps not playing the next episode in the show and going to another random episode. I’ve cleared the queue and checked the settings and it just keeps doing it. It’s very annoying to keep having to stop what I’m doing to select the correct next episode, especially while driving, and I think I’ll have to find a different app if I can’t figure out the fix.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-09T15:22:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14159564791', 'justanotherappleuserwhocares', 5, 'Just keeps getting better!', 'Overcast has been a mainstay in my listenting for years, and it just keeps getting better. The recent addition of automatic transcripts with smart sectioning and music identifications has completely changed how I listen to podcasts. Before that, the ability to jump back to the previous timestamp after accidentally loosing your place was a huge quality of life improvement. If you like podcasts and care about a good listening experience, I cant recomend Overcast enough.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-08T12:46:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14158987640', 'chhdojebwodjfneo', 1, 'Used to be the best', 'Now completely useless. Dev doesn’t care', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-08T09:39:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14157015520', 'Disgruntled Podcaster', 1, 'Used to Work', 'I''ve used this app for probably 10 years. Now it doesn''t download anything properly, so I''m moving on. Maybe someone other than an AI chatbot will notice, since that''s all anyone gets for support anymore.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-07T21:01:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14156519952', 'Simonandlola1', 1, 'I loved the simplicity of this player', 'The simplicity of this podcast player was the selling point for me. I don’t know why you updated it. I’m out.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-07T17:32:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14152215979', 'nickD0518', 1, 'Nothing ever gets fixed', 'All sorts of inconveniences on this app. I’ve emailed support and done a review. I’ve read other people share concerns on reviews. Nothing ever gets fixed. And I never get a reply back. Easy to use app when it works, but it rarely works.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-06T14:39:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14152194654', 'Casual artist', 5, 'Best Podcast App by far', 'Do yourself a favor and install this now. Delete the Apple podcast app and use this one instead. Your only regret will be that you didn’t make the switch sooner.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-06T14:30:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14150946687', 'Azderson', 5, 'great', 'Transcripts are well implemented. Smarter design than Spotify', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-06T07:40:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14148841777', 'womplyschmoop', 1, 'Busted and never gets updated', 'UX gets worse every year', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-05T18:11:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14148712145', 'Sportsman2131', 5, 'Ryan', 'By far the best podcast app available. So many great settings to really personalize your podcast experience.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-05T17:20:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14141618560', 'JMendes89', 5, 'Was and still is the best out there', 'Overcast has been my app of choice for podcasts for almost 10y now, it always was and remains extremely good for it’s purpose.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-03T21:27:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14141408026', 'Ghduxxbjk', 5, 'A+', 'A+', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-03T19:54:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14139994486', 'WhileyHughes', 5, 'Great app', 'This is my app of choice for Podcast and has been for several years', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-03T10:58:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14136775425', 'N8rboii', 5, 'Best podcast app is correct', 'It simply has all the features I want and none that I don’t. And in the rare instance there is an issue, the developer is great about fixing it.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-02T14:48:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14135847945', 'AsleepT', 1, 'Used to be good', 'Used to be a stand out podcast app. Now it’s solidly in the lower tier. Ads ads ads and rapid battery drain.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-02T09:37:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14135243509', 'Estee_nj', 4, 'Great in lots of ways', 'Great in lots of ways, but there are still features I struggle with (or struggle to find), e.g., managing downloads, and navigating btw shows and episodes.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-02T06:41:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14132892581', 'morphorod', 5, 'Undisputed Champion', 'The best podcast app remains the best with nice niche features that should help you manage a small or massive library. I hear over 100 podcasts and this app handles them like a champ.', '2026.5', 'us', '2026-06-01T15:06:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14128622385', 'toastyburps', 1, 'Glitchy and confusing UI', 'This app takes WAY too much work to dial in settings. It has great potential but it’s useless if the app keeps auto downloading the wrong podcasts or randomly deleting my ONLY podcast from the home page. It’s laggy and frustrating. I want to love it and I will miss the volume leveling but this just sucks. Back to Apple Podcasts I guess. If you just want to listen and go, this isn’t for you.', '2026.4.1', 'us', '2026-05-31T13:22:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='888422857'), '14125726962', 'oodavede', 1, 'Terrible Bluetooth', 'I keep disconnecting the app from my car to use another app and it forces me to use this app again it’s horrible', '2026.4.1', 'us', '2026-05-30T20:05:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14177340293', 'iPadOnTheRun', 5, 'None Better than Pocket Casts', 'The Pocket Casts team really get it! They know what makes a first rate.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-13T03:36:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14175870607', 'Nickname? Fine. Ishmael.', 2, 'Visually it’s just getting worse', 'They added a big blank space at the top of the screen that is totally useless… and made the thing you are most likely to want to interact with (the now playing controls) even smaller than before! It feels like they are vibe coding this without checking the result.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-12T17:29:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14174254572', 'Jasonsdinklefartman', 1, 'TERRIBLE Liquid Glass update', 'Change it back! Why did you make the skip ahead and back buttons 2x small with the Liquid Glass update? I don’t mind adhering to the new design language, but why change how a core feature (the bottom bar) works and where the buttons are? These are the buttons I press MOST OFTEN. Terribly frustrating.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-12T08:19:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14172756848', 'dordr', 2, 'Liquid Glass Update is Nuts', 'The new placement of the profile button is insane, crowding out the Up Next queue that we actually navigate to constantly. Thankfully the other major oddity you can at least turn off — the “minimize on scroll” function. But why suddenly implement this extremely unpopular behavior from Apple’s own apps and make it default? How about just fix the half-dark versions of your app icons after a year of them mostly not functioning as they should? Or repairing the widgets that for over a year now break all artwork displays while in airplane mode?', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-11T23:26:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14172622706', 'wutreviews33', 1, 'Why I will be uninstalling', 'Would rather copy pasta my .opml.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-11T22:23:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14171877850', 'Gameman114', 3, 'Recent Update Ruined Usability', 'Since they added Liquid Glass to this app it’s almost entirely unusable. I use the Electric Blue theme with dark mode and the mini player and tab bar are almost completely invisible now. If this doesn’t change soon then I’m jumping ship after 3 years because this really, really sucks now.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-11T17:10:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14171662221', 'Longsko', 1, 'Liquid Glass update is a miss', 'With this new update it is impossible to use the play controls on the bottom bar they are so tiny. What is the point?', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-11T15:41:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14171193895', 'ecahilm', 4, 'Overall like it, but small play button', 'Have been using the app for years now and does really well for what I am looking for in a podcast app. However, with the last update they made the play button much smaller in the main screen. Why? I use the app during my commute and now I have so many hits and misses trying the get music to play. Make it bigger again please.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-11T12:50:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14170171228', 'patsrs', 5, 'Best App Period', 'Without a doubt one of the best apps in the entire store. Cant recommend enough.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-11T07:45:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14168425716', 'EdHans', 4, 'Not a fan of the glass update', 'With 8.13, we get Liquid Glass, which looks fine, but now the ui for the podcasts, playlists, discovery, etc. icons are hidden behind a player UI, so it’s an extra click on a tiny button to get to them. Why do UI designers add clicks!?! Keep Liquid Glass. It looks fine over all. But get rid of the navigation changes in 8.13.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-10T20:15:47-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14168154372', 'Mandatory_nickname1', 5, 'Using it since 2015', 'I’ve occasionally tried others but nothing beats it. Works perfectly.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-10T18:24:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14166927548', 'Sofa King Cynical', 1, 'Persistent Profile Icon?!', 'Liquid Glass looks good overall. But why is there a now a Profile icon that we cannot remove? It’s just a waste of space. The tiny now playing bar looks bad as well.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-10T10:50:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14165285588', 'wearshades', 2, 'Recent updates miss the mark', 'Some of the recent updates for the app miss the mark for me. The latest version of the minimized audio control bar within the app has shrunk the play/pause/skip buttons so much that it''s difficult to hit the button you want every time. This seems to have been done to create space on that bar to show the episode name and progress indicator, but I''d rather just be able to reliably hit the buttons correctly as on previous versions. Conversely, the playlists now include a giant episode art collage at the top that takes up SOOOOOOO much space at the top for no actual benefit. Give us more space at the top of playlists and bigger buttons on the control bar!', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-10T01:47:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14164369364', 'iOSDevices4David', 5, 'Liquid Glass all the way', 'Like the Liquid Glass refresh! Well done, all!', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-09T18:53:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14164083792', 'k!m', 2, 'Liquid Glass update sucks', 'Pocketcasts is the best player but they really love making updates that nobody asks for and don’t actually improve anything. The most recent one made the play button on the main page unusably small. I hope they fix it soon and I can revise this review.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-09T16:58:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14164011804', 'Juandagreat-', 5, 'The best Podcasts app', 'Been using it for 10 years plus now and will continue to till I keel over.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-09T16:29:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14163745072', 'raydenz0731', 2, 'liquid glass makes it hard to control', 'Now button smaller than thumb, click pause can be backward.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-09T14:43:30-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14163352714', 'LavenderGooms369', 2, 'poor ux', 'On the latest update, if you open “Profile” and scroll down, you are stuck on that screen. There is no button to get you back to your podcasts without force-quitting the app… unless you intuit (perhaps you are a psychic?) that the developers of this app hid your podcasts behind the “Profile” button in the toolbar. How would anyone intuit that opening “Profile” in this state actually doesn’t open your profile; instead it unhides a menu that allows you to continue using the app for its intended purpose.', '8.13', 'us', '2026-06-09T12:22:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14156244308', 'kevjpost', 5, 'superior to the native app', 'apple podcasts was running very slow for me- slow to load, slow to start playing and slow to download. this app works much more smoothly and is blazing fast. works well on my phone and on carplay.', '8.12', 'us', '2026-06-07T15:38:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14150213248', 'pinkrabbitagogo', 1, 'Not worth money', 'The best is if you pause it while another application is open, the app closes. I love spending money on this.', '8.12', 'us', '2026-06-06T03:45:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14149208406', 'Crapple86', 5, 'Definitely worth a listen', 'Extremely well written and well thought out. This is a great sci-fi story with elements of horror.', '8.12', 'us', '2026-06-05T20:36:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14141363335', 'SamHWall', 5, 'Lifetime User', 'I’ve been using Pocket Casts for gosh, a decade now? Anytime I fall to peer pressure and try one of the well known names in streaming apps I always find myself right back here! I appreciate the pride color option and will remain a loyal pocket cast user!', '8.12', 'us', '2026-06-03T19:36:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14141095008', 'I vote for PRIVACY RIGHTS!', 1, 'Nope', 'Privacy concerns. No need to collect personal data. You can’t sell, lose, violate what you don’t collect. Not for me', '8.12', 'us', '2026-06-03T17:48:31-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14139924921', 'Critical Justin', 5, 'Absolutely the best', 'I have been using Pocket Casts for a LONG time at this point and on Android as well. Even though it has changed hands, the app has only gotten better. I have tried many other apps out of curiosity over the years and none are this good.', '8.12', 'us', '2026-06-03T10:36:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14136352848', 'akaGravedust', 1, 'Useless anywhere but iOS', 'Web player DOES NOT function correctly, despite going back and forth with support for months. Pocket Casts ONLY functions through the iOS app, which makes it completely useless when working.', '8.12', 'us', '2026-06-02T12:18:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14134805509', 'JBKnight777', 5, 'Great podcast player', 'Had this for five years and it’s been great!', '8.12', 'us', '2026-06-02T04:21:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14133319042', 'mrjuanhernandez', 1, 'useless now', 'Used to be the best podcast app, however i can no longer listen to Conan on this app. The episodes don’t play, they don’t download, it never works.', '8.12', 'us', '2026-06-01T17:47:47-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14116709482', 'Dvd8718', 5, 'Best podcast app out there', 'Very reliable and intuitive design. Feature rich without the confusion.', '8.12', 'us', '2026-05-28T12:02:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14116487449', 'Jemmake', 1, 'Not updating', 'Missed big episodes from major publishers as it is not updating despite it is data it is??? Fix it!', '8.12', 'us', '2026-05-28T10:47:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14115640622', 'Rian J.', 1, 'Always freezes/Never plays', 'This app’s audio either freezes in the middle of an episode with the episode still going or it won’t even play. Don’t get this stupid app. Find something else.', '8.12', 'us', '2026-05-28T06:29:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14113560373', 'PurpleToonLink', 5, 'gets the job done', 'used it for many years now. idk what the official apple app is like anymore', '8.12', 'us', '2026-05-27T16:12:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14110302790', 'Bill 83572', 4, 'Pixel Buds touch controls stopped working', 'This app has everything I need and I’m very familiar with it after 2+ years on iOS, but a few months ago the touch controls on my Pixel Buds stopped working. I assume it is a Google / Apple issue, but then I noticed everything still works on Spotify and I also recently tried Apple Podcasts which also worked. I’ll need to find an alternative because it’s annoying having to take my phone out of my pocket every time I want to go forward or back. I know this is somewhat of an obscure issue but it’s becoming a deal breaker. All software on both ends is up to date. There were no issues for the first ~22 months of using this app and all of a sudden the issues started. Not sure what happened', '8.12', 'us', '2026-05-26T19:23:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14103456667', 'deluxewombat', 5, 'still my absolute favorite! use every day!', 'however, I did wanna make somebody aware that as of a couple of updates ago the beginning of most podcasts "skip" three or two times. skip, as in, a 1 to 2 to even 3 second stop of playback, which it then resumes right in the anticipated spot. not a terribly big deal. also adding episodes to the Up Next que is now (for me) VERY buggy. I''ve always added approx 7-10 episodes from a smart Playlist and as they are included in the Playlist they are also auto downloaded. now when I do this the app gets Really slow and non responsive. again not a huge problem. hope everyone is well keep up the great work. *iPhone 17 Pro Max iOS 26.5', '8.11', 'us', '2026-05-25T00:39:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14101307589', 'DrMDavis', 4, 'Sometimes glitches', 'When switching between Bluetooth devices the app simply won’t play. Otherwise trying to get used to the playlist features.', '8.11', 'us', '2026-05-24T10:03:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14101223954', 'Schmity48', 1, 'Currently Unusable', 'Overall my favorite podcast app(when it functioned correctly and isn’t glitching)with the app display layout,format, and especially the “up next” or “up last”queue feature. The app doesn’t work anymore. If I press play before a podcast finishes downloading the podcast is broken and unplayable for 24 hours. Every day there are podcasts I can’t listen to because of this. App has been constantly doing this all year, So I’m done with it.', '8.11', 'us', '2026-05-24T09:36:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14083905430', 'Calamaridelight', 5, 'Pocket casts', 'Wonderful with Sterling! Love it', '8.11', 'us', '2026-05-19T17:52:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14072305549', 'maestag42', 3, 'Buggy', 'The play pause play functionality being broken almost made me switch podcast apps. Sticking thru it hoping for a fix because the app is otherwise so good. So this basically means you cannot pause with headphones and start again with headphones. If you pause with headphones you can’t even play it again from home screen or quick widget or anything. You have to open the app again to resume. Pretty much a deal breaker and should be fixed ASAP.', '8.11', 'us', '2026-05-16T13:36:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14068381215', 'Bass clef MR', 3, 'Most functional, one caveat', 'I’ve tried nearly a dozen podcast apps and keep coming back to this one. It has the best queue and UI of any I’ve tried. Only downside is that if your podcast doesn’t contain ads the app seems to insert them for you. Local podcasts with play with no ads on other players but have shoehorned ads on Pocket Casts, usually abruptly inserted in the middle of sentences. Despite that I continue to use the app as my primary podcast app.', '8.11', 'us', '2026-05-15T13:00:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14060363652', 'Reviewing_Rater', 1, 'Too many notifications.', 'Too many notifications coming from a podcast app that has nothing to do with the podcasts i am subscribed to. LEAVE ME ALONE! Deleting now.', '8.11', 'us', '2026-05-13T09:01:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14054662718', 'HD650', 3, 'Play-Pause-Play Doesn’t Work', 'Listening to a podcast and clicking on the AirPods Pro stem once the podcast will pause… cool! However when pressing the stem once again to resume listening the podcast does not resume at all. This has been broken for a while. Please fix.', '8.11', 'us', '2026-05-11T18:55:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14053923661', 'municipalbondage', 1, 'Missing basic functionality', 'Your unarchive all feature is actually completely useless and does nothing and this is why I no longer pay for a premium subscription. Your even more useless AI just gave me directions that I was already following and refused to give me a functional link to a human 😊', '8.11', 'us', '2026-05-11T13:50:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14051436770', 'ScottInAustin', 4, 'Solid', 'I’ve tried and uses a lot of podcast players. This is my favorite. It’s easy to add new podcasts. ONE MISSING FEATURE? “Catch-up”. For this (whatever) podcast, auto-add the next oldest unplayed episode once every X days but only if there are fewer than Y episodes from that podcast in my queue.', '8.10', 'us', '2026-05-10T21:52:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14049423548', 'danjonwig', 4, 'Great tool, needs some tweaks for multi device', 'It’s fabulous of an independent podcast tool. I use many different devices. This does have a feature that is meant to sync them so that progress is maintained across all. I find it. This feature works about 50% of the time. The rest of the time. I find that it simply doesn’t sync and fail silently.', '8.10', 'us', '2026-05-10T08:42:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14043484700', 'JayCee2213', 4, 'Better than most', 'My biggest issue with podcast players is the difficulty moving directly to the next episode while driving. Pocket Casts is the easiest when it comes to this, though it’s still not perfect.', '8.10', 'us', '2026-05-08T18:21:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14041819051', 'Mizirk', 5, 'So much better than Apple’s', 'I thought I’d have to manually re-add each one since Apple doesn’t export. Nope. Pocket Casts can import them all, which would then allow me to export from Pocket Casts to something else, but I wouldn’t need to. The widgets and shortcuts are useful, it doesn’t forget which episode I was on like Apple’s does. And I can find episodes I was listening to a few days ago without searching through the entire show’s episodes. Apple, take note.', '8.10', 'us', '2026-05-08T07:50:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14039336743', 'sam_g', 5, 'The Best Podcast Player.', 'This is by far the best podcast player in my view. In fact it’s one of, if not THE, best app I have used. I listen to a lot of podcasts (apparently given the stats in the app I have listened to over 300 days of podcasts in the last decade) and this app is why.', '8.10', 'us', '2026-05-07T14:13:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14038984296', 'capvfl', 5, 'The essential podcast app', '8 years of excellence and continuous improvement', '8.10', 'us', '2026-05-07T11:54:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14018332676', 'Style by Cozy', 5, 'I cap my business day with David’s insights.', 'Professional, knowledgeable, entertaining, engaging, stimulating, while making me smarter and keeping my panic over our current government at bay. Keep it up!', '8.10', 'us', '2026-05-01T18:08:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='414834813'), '14009905071', 'puqo2020', 5, 'The Best', 'This is by far the best podcast app! Is there a chance of getting more video podcasts like rival apps so we have the option of audio or video?', '8.10', 'us', '2026-04-29T10:09:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '13855342322', 'Tommy Spike', 1, 'Please make page up/down work properly!', 'I like this app but its key bindings on macOS is driving me crazy. Page up/down should scroll the article by a page. Instead, they just beep and you have to use space/shift-space. Also, home/end should go to top/bottom of the article. I will keep my rating at one star until the dev fixes this annoying problem.', '8.0.4', 'us', '2026-03-16T13:04:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '13829970434', 'net23cvr', 5, 'Best RSS Reader for iPad / iPhone', 'Been using Newsify for years - it does exactly what I want it to do. Great software worth subscribing to.', '8.0.4', 'us', '2026-03-09T05:18:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '13731665693', 'SetecAstr0n0my', 5, 'Favorite RSS reader!', 'I’ve used abs paid for this app for years, after trying all the other popular ones. The newspaper layout is amazing. The advanced downloading of full articles for offline reading is amazing. The developer is very responsive. Would recommend.', '8.0.4', 'us', '2026-02-09T12:22:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '13537422427', 'Britt K in Georgia', 5, 'Finally, fixed the performance lag!', 'For some reason, the app got so slow and often with a delayed “loading” screen. This version finally fixes it back to previous quick performance level. THANK YOU!', '8.0.4', 'us', '2025-12-20T21:10:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '13530193027', 'JamesWang1982', 4, 'Image Save Error', 'In the latest version, when I long-pressed the image and try to save OT, it always reports error. And I already gave it full access to my album', '8.0.4', 'us', '2025-12-18T23:51:50-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '13472707519', '[--REDACTED--]', 5, 'Newsify', 'top notch application and developer. been using for years, perhaps a decade already. habe never had a reason to look for anything else.', '8.0.4', 'us', '2025-12-03T20:39:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '13325844645', 'AppReviews1000', 3, 'Goldfish', 'One common problem to a lot of RSS readers is that they do not hide read articles from view. Most will “dim” them like Newsify but not make the article disappear resulting in a lot of clutter on the screen. Otherwise it’s decent.', '8.0.2', 'us', '2025-10-28T09:29:46-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '13233767336', 'nefariousporpoises', 1, 'Seems to be dead?', 'I used newsify for a while and recently returned to it but it seems broken. Won’t sync, I keep getting an error. I tried restarting my phone, as well as deleting and reinstalling but now it won’t let me sign in. I guess i have to find yet another rss reader, yet again.', '8.0.1', 'us', '2025-10-06T19:03:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '13191988579', 'Mysterobvious', 1, 'New article browsing controls are horrendous', 'With the iOS 26 update, the previous, next controls are shrunk significantly, leading me to misclick constantly. Please bring back the standard full screen width controls!', '8.0.1', 'us', '2025-09-27T07:41:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '13082389232', 'Culadernow', 1, 'Not like mobile app', 'Can’t change layout on my Mac Air. Font too small', '7.4.1', 'us', '2025-08-31T06:38:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '12902075702', 'StridentStormyCarrot', 1, 'Ultra-wide and 4K users - no zoom', 'If you use an ultra-wide or 4K monitor, give this one a pass. There’s no way to zoom in. Cmd + + does nothing. The “Zoom” button in the menu just makes the app fill the screen (not like fullscreen, but expanded). This is a very basic accessibility functionality that’s baked into most apps by now - especially if their focus is, you know, READING?', '7.4.1', 'us', '2025-07-17T03:48:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '12405705359', 'pmzdj', 2, 'Why is article browser truncated?', 'Would be a lot more useful if article browser was wasn’t so limited/truncated.', '7.4.1', 'us', '2025-03-10T14:01:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '12323533434', 'Jonges.exe', 5, 'Fantastic but..', 'I very much love this app, the layout is nice and being able to group stuff in the folders is a plus. I have two complaints. The fact I can’t change it the text to comicsans and that pressing a RSS feed link doesn’t bring up the app to add the link. It’s a minor inconvenience but all the same. It will be nice if it was already a feature.', '7.4.1', 'us', '2025-02-17T14:54:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '12180663086', 'EboniLM', 5, 'Almost perfect', 'UPDATE: It looks like email routing issues on my end were the reason the app dev hadn’t received my screenshots. I sent them over and he quickly identified the issue and gave me a workaround. I couldn’t be happier - 5 stars!!! ——— I’ve been a subscriber of Newsify for several years now and have really enjoyed using it. It is literally almost perfect: customizable, easy to use, and affordable. I haven’t had a single issue over the last few years except for the fact that you cannot add a custom URL/source from the iOS app. You have to do it from the desktop interface, which is a pain. I brought this up to the developer and received a pleasant response stating the feature was available. I sent a follow up email with screenshots showing the issue but have not yet received a response in over a month. I’ve since switched to a competitor as I couldn’t keep paying for an app that is missing such a huge feature. If this is fixed, I likely wouldn’t hesitate to return.', '7.4.1', 'us', '2025-01-13T12:20:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '11953133863', 'SriRamaGovinda', 5, 'The Best RSS Reader', 'If you want to keep up with honest news in today’s world the only way I know of is with an RSS news reader. You have complete control over which sources you want to monitor. Enter your trusted web site addresses and you will receive a short summary of every new post. Click on a summary to go deeper. Newsify makes it easy to keep up with dozens of sources. You can avoid fake mainstream news completely. You have complete freedom to find and know the truth without censorship.', '7.4.1', 'us', '2024-11-15T08:06:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '11941946615', '[--REDACTED--]', 5, 'Newsify', 'I’ve been using this product for about a decade now. When I found Newsify, it was only $3. I didn’t mind when the developer switched to a subscription model because I know hosting and coding take time and money. The annual subscription price is fair for what they do. I haven’t even looked for another RSS reader since Newsify does everything I need it to do (just feed my RSS with some good config options). In addition to a great product, the developer always responds to support emails quickly and is very polite. I’ll be using Newsify for the long haul; keep up the great work!', '7.4', 'us', '2024-11-12T07:19:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '11831110102', 'nickname92262', 1, 'Stopped Syncing After iOS 18 upgrade', 'After upgrading to iOS 18 on two phones and two iPads, many of the feeds have gradually stopped working. We’ve reloaded the rss addresses but that doesn’t change anything.', '7.4.1', 'us', '2024-10-13T16:31:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '11755944436', 'Mufid', 1, 'It’s empty after migrating to new iPhone', 'Deleted and reinstalled and nothing works', '7.4.1', 'us', '2024-09-23T07:14:36-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '11725499199', 'tg8035', 2, 'Not even 7 days into free trial', 'and the app and web unread counts are out of sync by more than 100 article count Have tried to fully resync multiple times, restart, login and out and nothing For that matter, why is this developer not allowing iCloud sync option but instead only using their own web server sync which is clearly not working, not being fixed, improved or maintained. Not too mention only allows unreads for 30 days. So no, I will not continue with this rss app reader service once trial ends. Such a shame, this rss reader app service probably has the best newspaper view mode of all rss reader apps. It appears that that’s all this app service has going for it 😒', '7.4', 'us', '2024-09-14T21:29:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '11562948850', 'حسابدار', 4, 'Translation', 'We need to translate the feed with Google translator.', '7.3.5', 'us', '2024-08-02T03:05:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '11455558083', 'tbernh', 5, 'Interesting Facts About the Night Sky', 'Provides educational comments about the night sky. Presented in a manner where the read is not too long but still informative.', '7.3.5', 'us', '2024-07-04T06:58:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '11259214347', 'betweenthesedays', 5, 'The RSS app I’ve been looking for', 'Ever since Google Reader went away, I’ve been using a “good-ish” alternative. That got a bit buggy and laggy and irritating so I decided that after all of these years someone has to have created something for people like me. Turns out it’s this one! The sign of a good design is if the tool fades into the background and just works. Less focus on the tool, more focus on the news. LOVE IT!!', '7.3.4', 'us', '2024-05-12T05:18:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '11012006356', 'laughingpenguins', 1, 'Needs OPML import and export', 'Data portability is important. RSS is a feature of the open web, and moving between services should be made easier. I''m actually trying to move to Newsify, but the lack of OPML support is making it more difficult. Update: Requiring an account (which lessens privacy) to import OPML is not good enough. You need to add support within the native apps and not require an account before I will increase the rating.', '7.3', 'us', '2024-03-05T11:44:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10976543108', 'zanp998', 5, 'Very nice', 'I have used several since the demise of Google reader. fantastic', '7.3.4', 'us', '2024-02-24T17:57:51-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10963224593', 'Toopushy2', 1, 'The most aggressive ads I have ever seen', 'Ads are fine but ads that pop up nearly every paragraph and are difficult to dismiss are too much. I get that you want me to pay money but this is excessive.', '7.3.4', 'us', '2024-02-21T04:15:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10864721343', 'galtenberg', 5, 'Needs to stop popup videos', 'Popup videos are starting to ruin the experience. The Verge, Reuters, other news sites are abusing this more and more. The app needs to not permit this. It also seems we''ve lost a setting to stop viewing Safari pages in Reading Mode. It''s stuck on for me on certain sites (and my main Safari settings have no "Automatically use Reader on").', '7.3.3', 'us', '2024-01-25T20:27:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10825959590', 'Buddha88', 5, 'Not Useable on Mac - super SLOW', 'Newsify is a 5-star app on iPad and iPhone. However, the Mac app is super slow. I see the spinning beach ball of death several times while trying to read a single article. It can take several clicks and up to a minute just for a menu to appear. In suspect there is no data or code running locally on the Mac, and the app makes individual calls to the Newsify server for every single function - even bringing up a menu, scrolling even a little bit down an article, etc. I would not recommend on Mac. The developer needs to re-write it to address these issues.', '7.3', 'us', '2024-01-15T11:57:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10810444242', 'Rick-G.', 5, 'Best news reader', 'I''ve tried several diffferent readers through the years. I like the look and flow of this one better than any that I''ve tried. Very slick!', '7.3', 'us', '2024-01-11T09:38:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10795439999', 'Fudged ‘Mo', 1, 'TOO SLOW', 'SLOOOWWW', '7.3.3', 'us', '2024-01-07T08:40:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10747259227', 'fxJedi', 2, 'iCloud Sync is Broken', 'Fails every time I reset iOS/iPadOS. Have to re-add all subscriptions.', '7.3.3', 'us', '2023-12-26T07:42:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10738747918', 'harleydavid96', 1, 'End of Life', 'This app is.', '7.3.3', 'us', '2023-12-24T03:17:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10646119617', 'Richinaz126', 1, 'Constant crashing', 'The last update broke the app. I''ve been using this for years without any issues but every time I use it now it will crash within a minute or two. Unusable. I have downloaded another reader. I''ve deleted it and reinstalled twice and cycled power on my iPad. No improvement. Seems to be an app issue.', '7.3.3', 'us', '2023-12-01T08:58:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10547064979', '/''y+*4', 1, 'Not updating on articles', 'Last update on Breitbart news articles was 2 days ago. This is certainly not the first time articles are not being updated on many of the news outlets I have. Very frustrating.', '7.3.2', 'us', '2023-11-03T16:08:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10542938400', 'Abkang', 5, 'Fantastic', 'Fantastic RSS reader. Saves me a lot of time.', '7.3.2', 'us', '2023-11-02T12:10:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10542461611', 'Becky8675', 4, 'I used to love it', 'None of my rss feeds seem to be showing any recent content even though I know there are new articles. I’ve been using Newsify for years but it basically doesn’t work anymore Updated: reached out to the developer and there is an issue with the feed', '7.3.2', 'us', '2023-11-02T09:13:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10427912315', 'SDTravel', 2, 'Development has stalled', 'Newsify *was* a good RSS reader. I like the full text download. However, the developers have basically put this app on maintenance with zero new features in years. It’s now missing essential features like Shortcuts support to add a RSS feed, directly adding a YouTube channel and decoding the RSS feed URL. The developers stated these features are not even on the roadmap. Extremely disappointed. Time for a new reader. Use another reader that supports modern usage. Newsify is NOT that app.', '7.3.2', 'us', '2023-10-01T11:22:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10413262977', ':(39571', 1, 'Slow and Severe Delay in Refresh Rate', 'Need Push Update in Real Time!', '7.3.1', 'us', '2023-09-27T10:25:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10392660871', 'Rhune G', 5, 'Great app', 'Great app that syncs between my iphone, ipad and Mac. Would be great to have an ad blocker in it. But really, best way to keep track of my RSS feeds. Great job by the developer.', '7.3', 'us', '2023-09-21T13:06:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10387897243', 'Joe B-2023', 4, 'Enjoy the newsfeed but…', 'I enjoy the newsfeed but the photos on many articles have no direct relevance to the article - and it is somewhat misleading or confusing', '7.3', 'us', '2023-09-20T05:31:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10382936449', 'Docabilly', 4, 'Use this everyday', '...on my iPad and iPhone. Occasionally on my mac. I love the ability to download full text and read when I am offline.', '7.3', 'us', '2023-09-18T17:59:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10369740853', 'devonhub', 5, 'Newsify rocks!!', 'Newsify continues to be one of my indispensable daily apps on both my iPhone and Mac. Newsify allows you to create your own personal newspaper with the content you want to stay current on from sites you choose. It''s an incredibly powerful information source with a very effective and intuitive user interface.', '7.3', 'us', '2023-09-14T23:37:15-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '10001915298', 'lightnin32', 5, 'CNN is not Working', 'The CNN feed stopped working over a month ago. Please update the link for this. Thank you', '7.2', 'us', '2023-06-05T07:06:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '9980949327', 'BDRhodes', 5, 'Rare form: elegant design AND highly customizable', 'An RSS reader is something that I want to be in unique and particular control over. If I accidentally read something, I want to be able to easily market as unread. That kind of thing. This app gives me that kind of control, and so much more, over how I keep up on what I like to read. Right down to font choice and offline caching. And I got it while it was free! :-) Couldn''t be happier.', '7.2', 'us', '2023-05-30T07:29:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '9966100666', 'pjthekilla', 4, 'Best RSS Feed app on the app store', 'Would give 5 stars but subscriptions can not be fit into a folder. It only allows one subscription.', '7.2', 'us', '2023-05-25T22:33:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '9801425832', 'bitterseeed', 1, 'Doesn''t work very well on MacOS', 'You click on a function, it gives you options and when you try to click on the option it just disappears before you can click on it. Don''t put an app on the MacOS store if it''s just meant to be on iOS and used with touch. Bad form.', '7.2', 'us', '2023-04-08T14:52:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '9787034042', 'BlazingBrother', 1, 'Does not work', 'Will not refresh.', '7.2', 'us', '2023-04-04T12:42:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '9761887722', 'Jesse_K', 5, 'The best RSS reader on the app store', 'I''ve tried many different RSS readers since Google killed their RSS product and Feedly filled in the RSS gap. I use Feedly for overall RSS sync, but I''ve never loved their native app. I use Newsify every day, but I still keep an eye out for new/updated RSS apps in case something better comes along, but we''re now at least a half a decade in with Newsify, and it''s still my favorite available. Feedly sync, lots of ways to customize, support for folders, shortcuts/gestures, different view options — those are a few of the things that are done very well with Newsify. Just the best.', '7.2', 'us', '2023-03-28T11:48:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '9739288939', 'Tommy Spike', 1, 'Please fix image loading bug', 'After all images in an article are loaded, the view is reset to the top position. This is very annoying, especially when I am on a slow connection. This has been a long standing bug. Please fix it. I’ll change my review to 5 stars.', '7.2', 'us', '2023-03-22T02:23:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='510153374'), '9584253687', 'SDTravel', 1, 'Decent RSS reader but low innovation', 'Good RSS reader, but developer rarely adds any new features. Version history for 2 years is very sparce in terms of new features. Pain points for Newsify: 1. Lack of Youtube RSS feed support 2. macOS app feels like an iPad port with zero support, for example, of resizing the columns 3. macOS app can''t display a full tree view of all RSS feeds/folders. 4. One of the most expensive RSS readers, and as previously mentioned, zero new innovation for the money. Very poor value. 5. Unresponsive developer. Seems like he''s mostly abandoned this app and just collecting the subscription income. IMHO, look for a more robust app and a developer that actually innovates and responds to customer requests. Newsify is NOT that app.', '7.2', 'us', '2023-02-04T18:25:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '14124789894', 'seattle boy', 5, 'Revolutionized how I consume media', 'I finally feel like I have a grasp on everything I read and a single place to read it all. Highly highly recommend', '8.4.1', 'us', '2026-05-30T13:51:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '14098640023', 'Jcb20142016', 5, 'Wow!', 'So I came from rss.app and Feedly cause I want to keep up with the playoffs.. I understand reader isn’t fast pace but it’s what I’m looking for .. use Flipboard and whatever is out there to find an article dump it in my library.. get feeds dump then then read them on my own time.. I been doing read later for now .. don’t get me started on chatting with highlights. I LOVE IT SO MUCH!! Using it on laptop and phone ! Thank you devs!!', '8.4.1', 'us', '2026-05-23T17:11:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13994632951', '_eascoast', 1, 'Just downloaded but my trial is expired?', 'This app must be connected to to original in terms of subscription. I’ve never used this one before but I’ve used the Readwise app; just downloaded this, signed up and it told me to subscribe to continue as my trial is expired. I can’t move past that page to even see what the app entails. Thats a real bummer, really wanted to try it as I get back into reading.', '8.3.2', 'us', '2026-04-25T01:08:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13981590978', 'pendolino', 3, 'Great app, disastrous quality control', 'The amount of bugs this app has is amongst the highest I''ve ever seen on any app, whether high quality or otherwise . It''s too bad, because this thing is really, really, really good when it works. For at least a year or two now, my inbox on my iPhone just does not want to work properly. It takes forever to load, and I''ve cleared the cache and done everything in the instructions and troubleshooting, but nothing seems to happen. I really do hope the developers get their act together.', '8.2.2', 'us', '2026-04-21T06:05:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13933456719', 'GeKaram', 4, 'Great, but no Widget support?', 'I’m enjoying the app and the service. But it would be great to see a widget for the news feeder.', '7.39.1', 'us', '2026-04-07T13:47:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13882001707', 'ksmith80209', 3, 'Unreliable', 'I love the idea of this app. I love the feature set. What I do t love is that a substantial portion of the articles I save get improperly saved. For example, I saved an article and the top and bottom sections (about 80% of the article) weren’t saved. I tried the same thing in GoodLinks — none. The article was as expected. Not sure what’s going on here but great features can’t make up for unreliable parsing.', '7.39.1', 'us', '2026-03-24T06:49:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13856226145', 'dkobro', 5, 'Favorite reading app, have tried them all', 'been using for around a year, just so well done. Forward everything here, just put on my fiancee with the app too. She loves it', '7.39.1', 'us', '2026-03-16T19:10:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13853391895', 'ssredwood', 5, 'Great app!', 'Battery and performance issues have been fixed :)', '7.39.1', 'us', '2026-03-16T00:16:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13830635603', 'Alan Alf', 5, 'The BEST media organization app', 'If you decide to use this app, prepare to expand your ideas of what is possible with a reader app. Wildly powerful and takes some time to get comfortable with, but for serious readers it’s 100% worth it. I wish there were TTS playlists but that’s not going to prevent me from happily giving 5 stars ✨', '7.39.1', 'us', '2026-03-09T09:15:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13800191876', 'Intrepid Insomniac', 5, 'The best all-in-one reader around', 'This app has changed the way I consume almost all online, and some offline content. While it’s not perfect (yet), it is very actively developed and supported. New features are coming all the time and when things break, they’re at least quickly acknowledged and usually resolved reasonably fast as well. It’s the best app I’ve seen in this category and I’ve tried plenty!', '7.38.2', 'us', '2026-02-28T14:59:31-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13679067631', 'Apexpredator67', 5, 'Great tts app', 'Please add a sleep timer The app is great so far', '7.34.2', 'us', '2026-01-26T12:44:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13671324261', 'Dermerat23', 1, 'TTS broken again', 'No QA testing before each update? Now when using TTS and you tap the button to jump back, it jumps ahead instead. Acceptable for a free or cheap service, not acceptable at this price.', '7.34.2', 'us', '2026-01-24T11:29:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13650252416', 'kalistowe', 5, 'Elegant Interface - and a true 2nd Brain', 'I save everything in it - research, epubs, pdfs, feeds from twitter lists, and websites, blogs. The text to speech feature is excellent for anything from articles to books.', '7.33.1', 'us', '2026-01-18T19:58:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13471728037', 'Aaron Hime', 5, 'reader app made by readers!', 'read & highlight anything, including YouTube and podcast transcripts. I can feel the love put into this app.', '7.30.2', 'us', '2025-12-03T13:49:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13398567426', 'AppRemarker', 1, 'No RSS compact view', 'Unlike every other rss app or similar apps such as email clients that all offer compact view vs default or vs expanded etc, Reader still has 0 options to customize the RSS screen. Can’t hide the image, can’t hide the excerpt etc so it’s a terrible rss experience and seems more aimed for the view one would want for curated saved articles not all ones rss feeds. Every years more small random updates but this never gets addressed. So frustrating.', '7.26.3', 'us', '2025-11-14T15:38:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13368379923', 'luckyseven888', 3, '发热严重', '我连续续费两年了，只要打开没多久手机就会发烫，所以我基本用网页看，中间 iOS 更新了很多个版本，每次我都期待更新后不发热，但是至今开发者没有解决这个问题，希望开发人员重视这个问题，及早解决。', '7.25.1', 'us', '2025-11-07T08:10:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13298626216', 'Swaggington', 4, 'I like it, but not seeing much progress', 'Been a paid subscriber for two years. I like a lot of things about the app: dark mode, flipping from one email to the next immediately from the end of an email I just finished, being able to save links inside of emails to read them later, custom email addresses to forward newsletters directly to the Reader. It solves the use case of “I want to have all my reading and highlights in one place” With that said, I’ve seen very little product progress over the last two years. The AI text to speech is still primitive. If you get a lot of emails, it’s still possible to be overwhelmed by the amount of content and feel like the app isn’t helping you get a grip on the information flow. There are a lot of missed opportunities to use AI for data analysis and better summaries. The “feed” view has a lot of unnecessary elements like the “Email” tag, an overflow menu that hides way too many important options, an AI summary that is too small and not informative enough, and a “reading time” indicator that is not accurate. Also line lengths are too long when reading on iPad. It feels like this is an app that started with a strong code idea, but lost its focus.', '', 'us', '2025-10-22T01:50:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13295723671', 'Bfeg', 5, 'Absolutely Life Altering', 'This reader has saved me so much time and also allowed mind to rest easier. All of my feeds and articles in one spot. I don’t get sidetracked as often with the focused UI. It’s a beautiful experience. I’m just kicking myself for not finding it sooner. I can’t wait for highlights view to be integrated!', '7.25.1', 'us', '2025-10-21T08:20:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13284413243', 'DrBionic', 5, 'Excellent App', 'This is the app for those that read a lot and remember what they read.', '7.25.1', 'us', '2025-10-18T16:40:45-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13282528727', 'Donne-SonnetX', 5, 'My most used iOS app', 'I love the text-to-speech feature, making any media listenable while allowing for reading without losing one''s place. The app receives consistent updates and provides excellent support. The highlight feature is transformative.', '7.25.1', 'us', '2025-10-18T07:08:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13280014654', 'benkuhn', 5, 'Bug', 'Current version has a bug where most downward swipes on the article view are interpreted as sideways swipes, making the app nearly unusable.', '7.25.1', 'us', '2025-10-17T16:40:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13237768576', 'AaronMS', 5, 'Love this App', 'Love this app for read to later. I’m on my second year of a paid subscription and it’s an obvious decision when it comes time to renew. It pairs with Readwise to save Kindle highlights. The only feature that I feel like I need that today it don’t have is aggregating articles to create a Kindle Digest like Matter does (that app is inferior).', '7.23.3', 'us', '2025-10-07T17:24:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13139420310', 'nishkaonapps', 5, 'Didn’t know how much I needed this', 'I try to minimize my use of apps/heavy tooling but this is downright incredible. It’s intuitive and exactly what I needed.', '7.19', 'us', '2025-09-14T23:53:14-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13117173271', 'Kerryth', 1, 'Last update introduced crashes.', 'Been us the Readeise reader app to have it read to me the details of a very large PDF and after the recent up the app crashes after about 5 minutes. This happens on both iPad and iPhone. I hope the developer fixes soon. All what good until then update yesterday.', '7.18', 'us', '2025-09-09T06:22:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13114569421', 'Dr. Ammar A. Shawkat', 5, 'Turned my books into audiobooks', 'I really like this app, I can read every kind of document I want, including YouTube where I can highlight text. Also, the text to speech feature I use to listen to my epub books before I go to sleep. Amazing.', '7.18', 'us', '2025-09-08T12:31:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13087612448', 'da-wdc', 3, 'Disingenuous update re Apple Pencil', 'Yes, you can finally use an Apple Pencil to highlight. But it’s nothing like you’d expect. You can’t highlight PDFs unless you’re in “text” view. Ok, annoying, but maybe not the end of the world. Until you switch back to pdf view. Then you can’t see your highlights anymore. Forget about something basic like handwriting notes. Not available. I realize this is a reader app not a pdf app. But if you want to claim your app supports Apple Pencil then support it. I really want to like this app more but there are just SO many seemingly needless friction points. I’ve signed up for one more year in the naive belief that when they say more support for iPad is on the way that it really is. We shall see', '7.17', 'us', '2025-09-01T13:21:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '13037331520', 'Nick ajajsjbebfkfltot', 1, 'Buggy and poor UX for reading', 'Got this because I already use readwise highlights and wanted to sync e-books and reading states across devices to my android e-reader. I don’t enjoy reading with it. I would cancel if it weren’t part of the highlights subscription which I value more. - Buggy: highlighting a word doesn’t always bring up the menu to allow highlighting. Often it mis-registers a page turn. Lots and lots of effort just to get a word definition or add a highlight. Then, - No offline/real dictionary: makes it completely unusable for difficult reads on planes and commutes so on… requires like 3 taps and 3-5 seconds of loading to get a watered-down chat-GPT definition as a highlight as opposed to a comprehensive dictionary definition. Infuriating with spotty connection, impossible with no connection. - Strange gesture controls for ebooks: No swiping left or right to change the page so all those years of muscle memory of reading real books and using a e-reader or any other reading app are really haunting me. Don’t understand why this seems not to be adjustable in the settings when other gesture controls are. Edit: further frustrations: - Can’t bookmark a page/location (I suppose you could do this with a Note or highlight but that makes no sense). Sometimes I want to return to a previous chapter or some other place in a book for reference but then I lose my current place. - No long-term saved/automatic location/progress markers. There’s a small dismissible notification which allows you to return to where you were if you jump around but once it’s gone, it’s gone. I live in fear of accidentally clicking this thing on a thousand page book I’m reading and losing where I was (it’s happened a couple times). I believe the Kindle app has this figured out, with multiple-device location. - More of a feature request: No document prioritization feature. Sometimes I just drop a bunch of things in to read later with some idea of which ones I’d like to read first. But you can’t reorder the documents in the home feed, nor can you add some sort of color or flag to mark which ones are higher priority or more important.', '7.16', 'us', '2025-08-19T17:40:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12968330575', 'Elmo Mierz', 1, 'Missing functionality', 'I got this to be a good place to read all my favorite publications in one app. Unfortunately, it has been my experience that I’m unable to read any of these publications, such as the Economist, New Yorker, or History Today, in the Reader App. Whenever I try to import them, I only get the first paragraph, presumably because when Reader goes to grab the article, it does not have my credentials to access the articles behind paywalls. If I can get support to help me find a way to use Reader for my needs, I’d be happy to change this review. But until then, this app is disappointing and useless for me.', '7.15', 'us', '2025-08-02T13:08:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12870134850', 'Pryn625', 3, 'Very helpful to collect and curate digital content', 'This app works well for collecting and managing the digital content I consume. —- 07/08/25: iPhone share to Reader issues resolved. Further enhancements I would like are [1] account merge, or [2] an export in a format that can be imported (as is) to another account. [3] Separate Tag and Notes buttons. In general, I’m most interested in having the ability to review what I have read/watched/listened to over periods of time (such as in the month or over the year); the ability to associate notes with that content for future reference; and the ability to curate a collection for different purposes - such as in identifying resources for a presentation. —- 02/07/25: iPhone share to Reader issues persist. I was using this app to collect mostly podcasts and youtube but several months ago the “share” feature stopped creating entries in my account. Did not matter what app I used (safari, pocket-cast, youtube, etc). If I want to create an entry now, I have to copy the link and paste it into reader. I have been hoping the issue would get resolved but so far no luck.', '7.14', 'us', '2025-07-08T23:56:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12697037722', 'a dude 42', 5, 'Packed with amazing features(but for the love of god change the app icon)', 'I love this app. It basically combined my separate RSS and “read later” apps into a single amazing reading hub, and I am only scratching the surface of its functionality. But good god the app icon is ugly — please change it so more people can find out what an amazing piece of software this is!', '7.5', 'us', '2025-05-25T09:01:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12682956285', 'roweniee', 5, 'just what i needed', 'awesome replacement to read-it-later apps like pocket. the ability to add rss feeds is awesomeeee. worth it if you read a lot and actually want to review your notes/highlights.', '7.5', 'us', '2025-05-21T18:30:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12644481269', 'Listocrat', 5, 'Keep up the good work', 'Can’t get enough of it they seem to be adding something new every couple of weeks….', '7.4', 'us', '2025-05-11T06:53:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12604524864', 'Chabbi21', 3, 'Great when it works', 'This app is fantastic except when it glitches, which is unfortunately a pretty regular occurrence. I have to delete and reinstall several times a year, and every time I do, it’s a massive pain to sign in because my account is not connected to Apple or Amazon. I would love to see this app making signing in via email easier.', '7.3', 'us', '2025-04-30T15:39:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12576067189', 'Parkrangerryan', 5, 'Didn’t know how much I needed this app until I used it', 'Title says it all. I am I school and it completely changed how I research. I was tired of social media apps trying to pull me away from my work. I started deleting them, but couldn’t fully disconnect. The feed in this app completely replaces any social media app i had before, all ad free. This app is truly a game changer. Highly recommend.', '7.2', 'us', '2025-04-23T02:36:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12427542059', 'Aliir74', 2, 'Good idea with lots of bugs without any fixes', 'The main idea is good but the app has several bugs which you encounter on a daily basis. And there isnt any way to report them easily in the app. Thats not fine with a paid app. I might cancel my subscription in the near future.', '7.1', 'us', '2025-03-16T07:00:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12353562379', 'rfanimation', 5, 'Absolutely love this app', 'I just wanted to write and say how much I truly love this app. The ability to tag, search, and review those nuggets of value I find in reading has made my reading so much more valuable and useful. And the new ‘Chat with your Highlights’ feature is about the best use of AI in my life. The opportunity to ask a question about something and have the AI summarize and organize content from my own sources (and only my own trusted sources) is incredible useful. In combination with Reader, this is absolutely among the best apps I have ever owned.', '6.18', 'us', '2025-02-25T06:47:15-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12349702454', 'jrschumacher', 3, 'Subscription', 'Can’t justify $12/m', '6.18', 'us', '2025-02-24T06:34:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12349299359', 'Thomas D. Hobbs', 5, 'The Best Read It Later App', 'Reader allows me to consolidate my reading resources into one app. Digital books, journal articles, websites, RSS feeds, and e-mail newsletters all go into Reader and keep me from bouncing around from app to app. And best of all, my highlights and notes automatically sync to the Readwise app for later reference. Readwise and Reader are the foundation of my second brain.', '6.18', 'us', '2025-02-24T04:32:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12303432914', 'Emin A A', 5, 'Good', 'Triple tap airpods to highlight during TTS is amazing!', '6.18', 'us', '2025-02-12T12:31:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12234693828', 'Joanbln', 1, 'Analytics/streaks?', 'As an avid reader, I optimistically switched over from my previous reader. However, I deeply miss being able to see my reading progress, streaks, goals, etc for the year at a glance', '6.16', 'us', '2025-01-26T13:48:15-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12214533814', 'Starman6969', 1, 'Extremely slow to refresh', 'App is extremely slow at initial open. It get better once everything is loaded but that takes forever', '6.16', 'us', '2025-01-21T20:48:22-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12204875616', 'Thebestestestwedgielover', 1, 'One huge issue', 'This Reader at fist glance seemed perfect but it seems to be completely missing a reading statistics page. Every reader has some type of stats page. How was this overlooked? Readers just aren’t useful to me without a way to track my reading progress', '6.16', 'us', '2025-01-19T11:34:14-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12156743079', 'JasonSpeaking', 5, 'The research tool I’ve been looking for!', 'I have used every major and minor reader type tool, and this one is the best, working with my research flow rather than forcing me to work with it. The highlighting feature along with ReadWise is outstanding providing a unique way of highlighting text even in a web browser to be saved.', '6.14', 'us', '2025-01-07T11:11:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12076512065', 'Dave143739', 1, 'Zero statistics', 'The app is beautiful and revolutionary but it has no reading statistics which is the only feature that I wanted. Just a simple line plot showing pages read per day so I can see some type of trend to improve myself. The developers mentioned this was low on their priority list which was very sad since statistics is what set their original Readwise app apart from the competition and is why I became a Readwise user in the first place. It seems Readwise has lost the vision. If statistics are ever added to Reader, I’ll update this review to make sure it has accurate information.', '6.14', 'us', '2024-12-17T23:25:27-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12067271133', 'Kdappreviews', 5, 'Great start - needs to stop adding features just “because”', 'I want to give this app 5 stars, but they continue to put superfluous / unneeded features into the reading view. The reading view should have NO distractions. Not a bar at the bottom of the screen with the document title. Not an annoying popup asking if I want to “return to 76% position. Stop putting things in the reader view please!', '6.14', 'us', '2024-12-15T10:24:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12042272457', 'steveo74', 5, 'What I’ve been waiting for', 'Since all the old RSS readers died and every site has been adding paywalls it’s been harder and harder to be efficient with my reading. Enter Readwise Reader. It lets me funnel nearly all the content I want to read - emails, articles, even PDFs - into one experience. I churn through everything on my iPad in the morning and save content for work to access from the desktop app. They have a great Discord community too and are super responsive to feedback. Love this team!', '6.12', 'us', '2024-12-08T19:46:22-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '12039944491', 'bAd DeTeCtIvE', 3, 'Crashes', 'Since latest update when listening to an ebook the app crashes and quits, forcing me to reopen the app, reopen the book and restarting the book.', '6.12', 'us', '2024-12-08T05:44:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '11989188959', 'Frond like Me', 3, 'Inexplicably not the web-app on iPad OS', 'I love Readwise on my phone, my Palma, and my web browser. It’s the best reading app & it’s expensive enough that I almost trust it’ll stick around (unlike Omnivore…). For unknown reasons, though: the iPad OS app is the web browser’s inferior in every way. The lack of a sidebar is nuts and it’s basically a high-res version of the phone app. What’s up with that?', '6.9.6', 'us', '2024-11-24T21:53:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1567599761'), '11960445577', 'Macfan4life12', 5, 'Wow, it has everything', 'A place to read, listen (text to speech), and organize your notes. All very well executed with a great UX. I wish I found this years ago.', '6.9.6', 'us', '2024-11-17T05:52:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '14063292766', 'mmcwatters', 5, 'Essential', 'I’m a longtime read-later app user, from Feedly to Reeder to Instapaper and beyond. I’ve been using matter since it launched a few years ago, and it’s surpassed them all. I love its ability to redirect newletters so my mailbox stays clean. It allows me to save, favorite, and highlight my favorite articles and newsletters. Its AI “readers” are the most natural and “listenable” I’ve experienced. It provides a beautiful reading experience. And that’s just the tip of the iceberg.', '4.1.9', 'us', '2026-05-14T05:16:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '14033353980', 'Toasted Angle', 5, 'Simple, powerful, reading queue', 'Matter comes to fill the gap after Pocket closed down, and I love its simplicity and useful features. Finding things to read in the discover or related articles section is nice. You can also add newsletters or rss feeds. Adding things to read later is simple as using the share sheet anywhere on iOS or via browser extensions for other devices. With premium you get a natural sounding voice reader, article summaries, highlights, search and no limits on the archive. I like sending links from google news or social sites to fill the download queue for stuff to read later.', '4.1.9', 'us', '2026-05-05T22:24:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '14003977221', 'Frosting6968', 4, 'Pretty good, missing a few things', 'A widget for unread articles would be a game changer, or the option to buy once. I just can’t justify paying monthly.', '4.1.9', 'us', '2026-04-27T16:17:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13950038921', 'tjj1', 2, 'Can use with only one device', 'I tried to get it in mt phone. But my email confirmation never arrives. I wrote the company - check spam/junk, which I of course had done. No other help available I gave up and deleted it. After several emails back and forth, they never did anything with the information I gave them April Update I thought I’d give them another chance. Still no email confirmation received', '4.1.6', 'us', '2026-04-12T06:10:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13902594191', 'iPad_For_REAL_Work', 3, 'Great concept, mediocre execution', 'I love the concept of the app, but it falls far short of being your go-to reading app. It’s very difficult to get PDFs or text emails into the app. Sometimes the emails are in your queue quickly, and sometimes they don’t show up at all. The browser extension sometimes pulls in the article, and sometimes it only creates a browser link, which is no better than a bookmark. You can supposedly add content via the iOS share menu, but it’s very limited in what can really be shared to it. I’m a paying “pro” user, but there is no response to support questions. They don’t seem to be updating the app.', '4.1.5', 'us', '2026-03-30T00:46:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13840560222', 'Brman99', 5, 'Best way to convert content to audio', 'Great product that allows me to save news articles from multiple sources, and provide text to voice playback from a saved queue. Saving works great with paywalled articles, but the caveat is that if you are on ios, the paywalled article must be brought up in Safari to allow the full article to have text to voice playback. For desktop systems, the Chrome extension works with paywalled articles.', '4.1.3', 'us', '2026-03-12T08:21:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13838702538', '554228', 5, 'Better than Readwise', 'For my use case (listening to articles), this is so much better than readwise reader. Rarely it gets messed up on the TTS.', '4.1.3', 'us', '2026-03-11T18:19:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13803302027', 'papasmurfrock1', 5, 'Best read later app', 'I’ve tried several different apps but Matter is the prettiest and best interface. I just always go back to Matter.', '4.1.1', 'us', '2026-03-01T10:57:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13777899650', 'Bnjoroge777', 5, 'love it', 'makes it realy easy and intuitive to have all my newsletters in one spot. reduces clutter and actually makes me wanna read them', '4.0.9', 'us', '2026-02-22T11:05:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13757848352', 'bwandyn', 4, 'Does the job', 'Solid and customizable reader, appreciate the Discover tab and being able to follow writers/publications. Support for any and all RSS feeds so I don’t have to rely on newsletter workarounds would be appreciated.', '4.0.9', 'us', '2026-02-16T20:37:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13704980556', 'JakeUsernameIsTaken', 3, 'Good App, Bad Support', 'I like what this app has to offer, but I don’t have anything nice to say about the support. I’ve opened multiple tickets with the support team via the Slack channel available via the app and I’ve heard nothing in weeks.', '3.8.8', 'us', '2026-02-02T07:22:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13700934258', 'seelliimm', 5, 'Beautiful and useful app', 'I enjoy it so much.', '4.0.7', 'us', '2026-02-01T05:59:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13691152711', 'ProtoZiggurat', 5, '"Double-tap is back"', 'Devs responded in a timely manner to a complaint I had, so I felt listened to and encouraged by their continuous work to improve the app. Much appreciated!', '4.0.7', 'us', '2026-01-29T17:34:31-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13687637829', 'jhlewis26', 4, 'Love the content but…', 'Hello, I love the articles recommended to me but often you continue to recommend articles that I have already read.', '4.0.7', 'us', '2026-01-28T19:23:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13652196408', 'HP requires nicknames', 5, 'Best reading app for iPhones', 'Matter has everything a reader could want. You can select any article and file it to read later. The app also gives you useful reading suggestions based on your previous usage.', '4.0.6', 'us', '2026-01-19T08:46:51-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13621374621', 'WhyANickname???', 5, 'Helping me feel sane', 'I have been using Matter as part of decluttering my life and replacing doom scrolling with more focused reading. Matter works great for this. I would love to subscribe to support them, but $80/year is a bit steep, and I don’t want to pay for AI “features”; I’ll never understand how AI would help me to read. This seems antithetical to reading.', '4.0.5', 'us', '2026-01-11T06:58:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13515101083', 'Sig Sal', 1, 'Beware Predatory Subscription Tactics', 'App is okay, however, upon opening it, I was confronted with a subscription offer that promised a trial. Unfortunately, I did not receive a trial, and $14.99 was deducted from my account. Within 5 minutes, I attempted to request a refund from Apple, I was informed that it was not eligible. I cannot endorse any application that conducts business in this manner. I advise you to avoid it, as there are numerous reputable RSS readers available.', '4.0.5', 'us', '2025-12-14T19:42:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13386730855', 'Joshua Seraphim', 1, 'Tried matter, but the app is a waste of time.', 'It downloads most webpages fine, but the way it formats them is sometimes obnoxious and counterintuitive. I looked past it because they claim in multiple places the app can download PDFs and easily convert them for reading with all the features they advertise. I tried 4 PDFs and only one worked. I tried going premium (used the free trial) and same problem. I emailed their feedback email asking for help and got nothing. I emailed their support email, got nothing. I emailed their CEO, who emails you when you sign up saying to reach out to him with concerns. Did I get a response? Nope. It’s been a week. Don’t waste your time.', '4.0.3', 'us', '2025-11-11T16:29:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13343441514', 'Tomasge', 3, 'Let down by unresponsive Customer Support (update)', 'They finally responded. It seems you need to write a bad review for the to pay attention which is a shame. New version is nice, and Matter is probably still the best app to organize your reading, but some key features have gone for no good reason (they confirmed it). A good example is the ability for bulk delete both in your inbox and archive. It seems they assumed people don’t mind accumulating documents, but for many it’s key to keep their archives organized. Hope it comes back. Original review: The app is good, but despite being a paying and loyal customer and their claims of being user oriented, they never answer when you contact them. Good luck if you need support.', '4.0.2', 'us', '2025-11-01T11:29:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13236898573', 'AaronMS', 1, 'Used to Love…', 'I used this app to aggregate articles into a single file to send to my Kindle. Other apps allow single article send and it is very messy. I was enjoying the app; then the update happened. I lost the ability to do the only thing I used the app for. I contacted the company several times but never received a reply. I have Readwise, which is incredibly responsive. Rating a 1 because I couldn’t get help and paid in advance for a year.', '4.0.2', 'us', '2025-10-07T12:07:39-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13212243023', 'aidanchau', 5, 'I love this app', 'I love this app I use it every day', '4.0.1', 'us', '2025-10-01T22:28:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '13089277812', 'EWimm', 5, 'Great and even better than Pocket', 'A really thoughtful and featured reader, and even better than what it replaced for me (the discontinued app Pocket).', '3.8.8', 'us', '2025-09-02T01:20:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12923619112', 'Eparz', 5, 'My Pocket Replacer', 'When I heard that Pocket was being sunset, I scrambled to find a solution and I think that this will do just fine. I want to be able to add articles that I don’t have time to read in the moment, so that I can refer to them later, tag the article so that I can group the topics I want to read, and easily save from other sites. Matter ticks all of those boxes, but it also adds features I didn’t know I needed, like the ability to convert those articles to text and listen to them. For an information hog like myself, this has been invaluable because I can listen to the articles I’ve saved in the car or on a walk or while doing the dishes. At first, I was a little bummed out to have to pay for it, but considering I’ve lost all of my saved articles now three times in 30 years of digital existence because of companies going out of business, I’d rather support a company financially and keep it going!', '3.8.6', 'us', '2025-07-22T11:26:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12848098764', 'davidsadler', 5, 'Matter rocks!', 'Longtime Pocket user having evaluated everything I can get my hands on as a replacement! Matter feels like the winner for me. It is a very thought full app which is precisely what I want! Thought full content and more-so an engaging well thought out interaction that feels smart. No wasted moves, space or fluff, while addressing what I want to track beyond the norm. It’s tight - I dig it!', '3.8.6', 'us', '2025-07-03T09:14:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12696235181', 'Mrcos', 3, 'Good experience but…', 'Overall it does a good work but search needs work urgently', '3.8.4', 'us', '2025-05-25T05:04:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12658653512', 'sdcabf', 2, 'sometimes it works', 'maybe it will save an article, but don''t rely on it to do so', '3.8.3', 'us', '2025-05-15T05:58:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12641769005', 'YelpingYak', 3, 'Women authors', 'Pretty good app. The content is very much lacking. I’m a big proponent of female authors and for whatever reason content from female authors is completely lacking. I’ve “followed” and “favorited” female authors but the content is so narrow that I consistently am not provided with any articles from them. Most of the days out of the week there’s just no options. I’ve falling back to simply finding my own content for which there’s no reason for me to pay for this service anymore.', '3.8.3', 'us', '2025-05-10T12:42:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12635133150', 'Shawn c', 4, 'Pretty solid with a few frustrations', 'I’m a few months in now, and this app has become part of my daily routine. There are a few things that could be improved to make it perfect: (1) RSS limitations: with a standard like RSS, I don’t understand why so many legitimate feeds are not recognized (2) sometimes I’m afraid to open an article because I don’t want to be flooded with “since you read…” the next day (3) the reading minutes meter seems to not go away unless you uninstall and reinstall—I just don’t want to see this at all. I’m hoping more updates are coming—haven’t seen any updates in a while.', '3.8.3', 'us', '2025-05-08T18:25:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12600279586', 'Wanderingella', 1, 'Used to be great', 'I used to use this app all the time. Now, despite paying for a subscription, the app doesn’t recognize I’ve paid. This feels like fraud.', '3.8.3', 'us', '2025-04-29T11:56:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12598584748', 'idontwritereviewsever', 4, 'Great read later app with a UI that’s actually nice', 'Been using Matter for a couple months now, switched over from Pocket and I’m loving it! The feed is clean and the keyboard shortcuts for highlighting and notes are super convenient. I’ve especially enjoyed the ability to listen to my articles and cleanly save video and text in one queue. I’d really like the newsletters feature to work better for me. I got it all hooked up with email forwarding, and I can see them come in on the desktop version, but I do most of my reading on my phone, where I cannot find the Inbox. Hoping that this can be added to a menu in the future.', '3.8.3', 'us', '2025-04-29T02:05:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12548091869', 'Quark Gluon Plasma', 1, 'Not a good fit for my workflow or my life', 'I am not a particular fan of read-it-later apps for general reading. I do have a need for apps that assist with researching or keeping up with topics of varying scope. I want to easily extract information with an eye to acting on it. This app is not notably better than its competitors, Pocket and Instapaper, which were much earlier to market, and a bit less modern. All of them are frustrating to me. All they do is act as an extra inbox, and they do not make me more productive. They all alter and filter the contents of web pages, and often cut essential information like the authors of articles. Then there are other, more widely applicable issues: First, the price: $60/year, and it’s going up in 2024. I think it’s very expensive for what you get. Then the interface, which I find unpleasant. Each entry takes up a lot of room both horizontally and vertically. It seems thick, somehow. Finally, there’s the curation, which is unimpressive.', '3.8.3', 'us', '2025-04-15T17:51:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12453818801', 'Louis-f Celine', 1, 'I’ve lost all my data after update', 'Will never use it again. My reading list disappeared after update.', '3.8.2', 'us', '2025-03-23T02:09:50-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12416070572', 'Tommy_Rowe', 5, 'A better way to read.', 'I can’t speak more highly of Matter; for 2+ years now I have been using it to actually read, listen, and reflect, rather than other apps/systems which just help you build a queue but never help you tackle it. Hop on board!', '3.8.1', 'us', '2025-03-13T09:26:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12408934844', 'wfisher', 5, 'Worth its weight in gold', 'Truly amazing as a reading app. I use it for all my newsletters, long-form articles, you name it.', '3.8', 'us', '2025-03-11T11:11:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12389550318', 'D3200', 3, 'Nice start but repeats over time', 'Gave up another subscription newsletter organizer that I liked better, because of the curated content Matter offers. Quite enjoyed the material to start with but several months in most of the content is on repeat. There are days without a single article I haven’t seen before (other than my newsletter inbox). At this price point and based on what is being advertised, I would have expected more.', '3.7.8', 'us', '2025-03-06T11:06:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12351182735', 'SeriousSusan11', 3, 'Transcription used to work', 'This app is dead. Developers are no longer updating the app as frequently. The transcription service no longer works. When you email them, they just tell you that they would look into it. Go find another app', '3.7.8', 'us', '2025-02-24T15:04:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12327032720', 'objectiveandfair', 5, 'Hsjfff', 'Fdsd', '3.7.8', 'us', '2025-02-18T12:51:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12278699933', 'chrisleader87', 5, 'The best', 'My only request is for an Android app so I can read on my BOOX Palma 🙏', '3.7.8', 'us', '2025-02-06T10:05:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12214091233', 'ChopFromBalm', 1, 'Description is a lie', '“Matter offers a free service and a paid service.” No, only a paid service.', '3.7.8', 'us', '2025-01-21T18:28:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12181514623', 'Somebeachsomewhere', 1, 'False', 'The 7 day trial doesn’t let you do anything but watch the preloaded video, so you can’t truly see what the app really does. So don’t even offer the trial. Disappointed.', '3.7.8', 'us', '2025-01-13T17:34:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '12119878505', 'Oldies4Doc', 3, 'Same old stuff', 'Been using this for several months and am getting the same assortment of articles . Mostly directed to business people. I am a retired educator with many interests but none of them are business. Digging through my history and queue I can find something worthwhile. It would be great to have these upfront and daily instead of stuff for the corporate bros.', '3.7.8', 'us', '2024-12-29T06:45:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '11941562407', 'Jugurtha656', 5, 'I’m so much smarter thanks to matter', 'This app has lured me away from twitter and I am so thankful for it', '3.7.7', 'us', '2024-11-12T05:18:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '11921389084', 'ssrrstuart', 2, 'Disappointed', 'I’m a long-time Pocket user, but that product has really fallen off (GUI, reliability, voices, etc) so I’m looking for a new tool that’s similar to what Pocket used to be. I tried Matter, but wasn’t super impressed. The GUI is good, but no better than Instapaper (free). The summarization sounded promising, but didn’t work very well. The idea of managing my RSS feeds sounded great, but Matter couldn’t process half of the feeds I tried to set up. The product has potential but seems half-baked on the advanced functionality that I would actually pay for. So I guess I’ll use Instapaper for now.', '3.7.7', 'us', '2024-11-06T20:32:46-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '11905549088', 'skch.', 1, 'Garbage', 'Cheap developers, bad design, trying to milk the crowd using subscriptions. Waste of time.', '3.7.6', 'us', '2024-11-02T17:43:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '11904755733', 'Q ✨', 3, 'There is no free plan', 'After the 7-day free trial the options are: $79.99/year $14.99/month It’s a pretty ok app, but I don’t like the lack of transparency or documentation.', '3.7.6', 'us', '2024-11-02T12:38:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '11870898143', 'roscomcmillan', 1, 'No free option, $80 read it later app', 'Really annoyed by these psychological and statistically optimal onboarding procedures that ask you a million questions and make you create an account before they reveal that there is only a limited 7 day trial before you’re paying. I’m so over wasting my time with these apps that are so confident in themselves that they think there’s no way you’re not going to want to pay $80 a year because you can save what mark manson writes on any random day. I should have known when they didn’t have a pricing tab on their site. Also because it had apples “app of the day”, since they’re getting a share of every subscription, they’re gonna award it to pricey apps. They’re all out of touch, I’ll stick to my free castle player, omnivore, and news explorer apps which do the same thing.', '3.7.5', 'us', '2024-10-24T14:35:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '11813701151', 'Hfkdoenntkfoxjdk', 5, 'Possible Violation of iPhone accessibility feature', 'The app appears to disable iPhones spoken content accessibility feature, seemingly to incentivize you to purchase a subscription to use Matter’s text to speech. This seems to violate some disability rights. Other than that, phenomenal app and game changer', '3.7.5', 'us', '2024-10-09T00:13:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '11725341579', 'Artbuydesign', 4, 'Beautiful reading app, just the cost...', 'I did the trial of this app and liked how it asked your interests and then provided you with articles that you would have never known about to read ontop of whatever you have forwarded into the app. I also like that it challenges you to read daily or at least listen...yes, listen! My only issue is the cost. For those of us who aren''t in the workforce any longer and living on a budgef, but still want to keep up our mental sharpness by reading, it would be nice if there was another price option.', '3.7.2', 'us', '2024-09-14T20:17:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1501592184'), '11706911848', '1TSjustM3', 1, 'Patriarchy Reader', 'I guess it’s a good app but all the Read Something Wonderful suggestions and every writer in the Top Picks recommendations were men. Why?', '3.7.2', 'us', '2024-09-09T12:49:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14266426060', 'David ryan K', 5, 'Love it', 'Best budgeting platform, super easy to use and see all my metrics', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-05T08:32:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14264745073', 'zjiang91', 5, 'The most pleasant app I have been used after mint shut down', 'Compared to other apps, it does everything I want. A lot of other apps I used has tiny issues, e.g. Fidelity full view or credit carma. They had issues importing one or two of my accounts such as Morgan Stanley Stock Plan or HSBC. But Monarch does all of them right. Feels so good to see all things again.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-04T22:35:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14263464338', 'Master of Clickability', 5, 'Look no further', 'I used to like Mint. Everything else I’ve tried since never satisfied me. There was always things missing or clunky. Until Monarch. It’s literally perfect. I’ve never had a moment where I thought “man it does not do that?” Nope. It does it all and does it in an easy to use and intuitive user interface. Well done. Non reason to look at any other option.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-04T13:44:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14263153905', 'andros1984', 5, 'Mint but better', 'Just like the mint I used to love', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-04T11:51:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14262738699', 'JimWeberg', 5, 'Best financial consolidation app you will find', 'I was lost after mint closed down until I found Monarch. They are the first and last app I check every single day. If you were serious about your money, you cannot do any better than Monarch for personal wealth management.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-04T09:38:51-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14257972793', 'Adamwkij', 2, 'Meh', 'Nice app. Just know that every time you open the app, you’ll suffer through a “dashboard” which is really just their marketing ads on trying to sell you services. Is quite annoying. Might want to find another app before you spend time setting up this one.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-03T06:33:27-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14257950053', 'Angel1910’', 5, 'Best app', 'I really like this app for my personal finance, they everthing just one place', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-03T06:27:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14254125578', 'sleadslead', 5, 'Worth Paying For', 'I’ve tried a bunch of personal finance services, and Monarch is by far the best. I use it every day and am happy to pay the subscription.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-02T08:11:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14252291113', 'Unholyephraim', 5, 'Amazing', 'Great app that keeps track of everything. I like the layout and how granular I can be with my budget. Best budgeting app out there and great for tracking all things financial.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-01T21:47:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14251006833', 'Maryannville', 5, 'Overall great app', 'I like how two people can upload their own accounts so each person can have ownership, and host the whole picture can also be seen. I like how you can see all transactions that come in. The accounts stay connected for the most part. I’ve been using it for about 8 months now and I like it so far. I do wish there was a way to order the accounts by balance rather than the order they happen to be listed, like I did when I used Copilot Money. It’s is easy to update the manual balances.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-01T13:52:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14249612038', 'Gypsyzzzzzzz', 1, 'Missing a key feature', 'Unfortunately I have to update my review. I cancelled my Monarch subscription months ago when they stopped supporting access to my bank. I cancelled again when they sent me a reminder in May. They charged me anyway. I have contacted customer service but received no response. I’m left either no choice but to dispute the charge and replace my card as they clearly intend to keep stealing money. Very sad.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-07-01T07:01:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14248357162', 'Beau Chevassus', 1, 'Locks you out until you’re forced to update', 'Been a paid user for +2 years. Low signal? Old iOS? You’re out of luck. They will have a giant screen come up that completely locks you out of using the app and the services YOU PAY FOR until you drop everything and go update their app. You’d better hope you’re not on an older iPhone that doesn’t have the latest iOS because they’ll 100% lock you of the app until you update. That’s something so bad, I almost expect Mint to do that.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-06-30T23:58:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14247727858', 'wpattison', 5, 'Great release notes!', 'I just wanted to thank you for providing detailed release notes when there are updates to the app!', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-06-30T19:58:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14247721244', 'user34799752267', 4, 'Love this app, one thing is broken', 'App is amazing and has done wonders for me. Only thing is I wish I could see my rollover reflected in future budgets in the mobile app. For example this month is June and I have $20 left in a rollover category. I want to look at July’s budget and see my budgeted amount plus the rollover from June, but I only ever see the July budget until the month begins, then it updates and displays appropriately.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-06-30T19:55:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14247644847', 'Amazing! Wow! Yep!', 5, 'Obsessed', 'Obsessed with Monarch - well worth the money.', '2.0.104', 'us', '2026-06-30T19:28:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14245637042', 'Dr.agus', 1, 'Es de pago', 'No puedes obtener prueba sin otorgar información de pago', '2.0.103', 'us', '2026-06-30T08:40:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14244987698', 'Greg Isaacs', 5, 'Best personal finance app', 'Love this app. Been using it ever since Mint was wound down. Its affordable and at the same time more robust than Mint ever was. Highly recommend.', '2.0.103', 'us', '2026-06-30T05:52:27-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14243937747', 'Winchermunster', 1, 'Doesn’t stay connected', 'The simply cannot stay connected to accounts. It’s really frustrating.', '2.0.103', 'us', '2026-06-29T23:39:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14243356015', 'heyjaywilson', 3, 'Paywall felt like it’s made to trick me', 'There are 2 options on the paywall. 1 to start trial and another to continue in app. I thought the start trial was going to open the Apple subscription flow which was very misleading when it didn’t. I don’t like to use non-apple subscriptions in apps as they are harder to manage. It was not clear that “continue in app” would open the apple subscription flow. I thought it was going to do something else like a demo or something not anything dealing with a trial. I felt a bit duped by this, and it makes me not want to even try Monarch.', '2.0.103', 'us', '2026-06-29T19:46:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14242929975', 'PatelBA1999', 5, 'One of my favorite apps', 'Love this app and the web version. Referred so many people.', '2.0.103', 'us', '2026-06-29T17:08:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14242926954', 'PennUltimate', 5, 'Best Money Tracking Product', 'This service has been life changing for me. I tried several apps and was even afraid of auto sync etc, but this has actually allowed me to be even more obsessive with my personal finance and is funly customizable. I love it. Thank you for this!', '2.0.103', 'us', '2026-06-29T17:07:41-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14242591915', 'ElainaN1', 5, 'Complex but fun!', 'Not super intuitive but it’s ok, there’s a lot of resources to learn how to get the most out of the app', '2.0.103', 'us', '2026-06-29T14:55:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14241663348', 'Jhazz', 5, 'Great app for tracking finances!', 'Wonderful to see everything in one place.', '2.0.103', 'us', '2026-06-29T09:50:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14238040987', 'Clemnoodle', 5, 'So easy and user friendly', 'Transformed my tax experience, worth every penny. Best thing out there', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-28T12:21:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14237523430', 'efhlfukhefrnekr', 2, 'Not any better than free apps', 'A lot of the functionality you would think it doesn’t have or doesn’t work smoothly. Poor syncing, can’t sync with some common account types, duplicates accounts, duplicates transactions, lots of manual overrides needed, can only do some things on web. Better of just sticking with Empower Personal Capital since it’s free and has the basically the same bugs.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-28T09:37:22-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14232333032', 'untaken_nickname_hope', 5, 'Love', 'Love', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-27T03:58:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14230133603', 'Kel54', 5, 'Best tool yet', 'I have tried a few of the other one and none did as good as my excel budget. But this one may just take over. It shows a ton of details and has a dashboard high level overview. I love it', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-26T13:58:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14228730604', 'Benno Jo', 5, 'Easy Money Management', 'It’s a well built app that allows me see my assets and expenses across many different accounts.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-26T06:50:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14226338537', 'meatsauce30', 1, 'Inaccurate Info', 'Incorrectly showed holdings and returns (showed losses on strong increase days). Support was very slow to respond and not helpful at all. Cancelled after 6 months for a refund. Look elsewhere and save the headache.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-25T15:47:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14219073371', 'mac_hine82', 5, 'Life changing', 'Don’t know how I survived without it. Game changing, I bought it for both my kids and aunt too.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-23T20:17:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14213823851', 'Unnamed user1', 3, 'Good for spending tracking not for account aggregation', 'Pretty intuitive for tracking credit card spending across categories and budgeting. Tried using it as an account aggregator to have investment and retirement accounts included and it turned into manual updates every few days. The app can’t distinguish transactions between interest or dividends paid and reinvested. I have to fix it every month, which involves reclassifying latest transaction then all previous ones that get messed up. Same with contributions to retirement accounts. Again credit card data is fine, it’s when you add other accounts that becomes constant manual entry/update hassle.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-22T11:19:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14212935922', 'Transaminase', 5, 'Needed Support', 'My wife and I have been struggling to get a consistent budget for the household. Monarch has made the budgeting process fun, interactive, and collaborative. I rate this app 10/10!', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-22T06:50:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14212632852', 'Helpful Budget Tool', 5, 'Great App!', 'So helpful with a budget and helps you save a ton of time too!', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-22T05:16:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14211432161', 'Gustavo2016', 1, 'Unable to keep accounts synced', 'I really want to give five stars but can''t because they cannot keep accounts synced. When you contact help they ask you to resign in which works 1/4 of the time and the others support responds back with canned messages like are you sure you own the account?? Mean while their sync status page will show issues with the major providers. You can do better.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-21T20:28:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14202308824', 'Sparkletron1', 5, 'Goals', 'The Goals portion of this app is what makes Monarch worthy of a five star review for me.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-19T11:36:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14201644926', 'thisnamesux', 3, '2 Stars for the iPad App / 4.5 stars for the platform', 'I absolutely love the platform and experience very issues with syncing but I absolutely hate the iPad app’s unnecessarily reduced capabilities and minimal investment in improving it. Over a year ago I requested that the reporting feature from the web version be brought to the iPad, which at that time was the only major feature missing from the iPad, and this month got notified that it has been delivered to “mobile”. After redownloading the iPad app, which I deleted for lack of feature parity, I discovered that “mobile” appears to only mean “phones” and not tablets. Super let down, especially given that now in addition to reports there are a bunch of business features that are not available on iPad/tablets. Not trying to throw shade, but if Monarch isn’t going to maintain feature parity between devices then they shouldn’t offer apps for them.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-19T08:11:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14197533750', 'pdrry6', 4, 'Best on the market… but', 'Recent upgrade got rid of yearly data prior to 2025? This is what EveryDollar started to do before it went downhill…', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-18T07:22:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14197486178', 'Motsumi', 1, 'Bad data, confusing interface', 'Accounts require at least weekly sign in. Connection to data is regularly lost. And when I reauthenticate, I’m told my credentials are good but there are no compatible accounts. Impossible to use under these conditions. If my data comes through, then I have a cluttered, confusing interface to fight through before anything useful can be realized. What a mess. Don’t waste your money.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-18T07:08:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14196253238', 'SF Jeff', 3, 'Meh-narch', 'This app is ok, for budgeting but that’s about it. It’s pretty much the reincarnation of mint.com: full of double entered transactions and things that you need to recategorize multiple times before it sticks. Fine for budgeting, but not great for projections which is important to me. God, I wish Intuit hadn’t stopped making quicken.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-17T23:17:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14191407186', 'i.knight7000', 2, 'Glorified spreadsheets', 'Initially I held this app in much higher regard because of the syncing features and insights. However, after a couple of weeks, all my institutions except for Fidelity have blocked access. You can try to sync manually but it’s a painful process that requires you to repeat the same steps multiple times. All for the app to disconnect from the institutions in another week or so. Without the automated syncing, it’s not worth the hassle.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-16T16:56:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14189618919', 'Wag13579', 5, '100% Everytime', 'Customer service is just like it used to be. They put their customers first and value them. You won’t regret it', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-16T07:07:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14186853226', 'mybigobsession', 5, 'Love it', 'So helpful and easy to use.', '2.0.100', 'us', '2026-06-15T12:42:50-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14186140769', 'k311y.c00k', 5, 'The best option out there', 'It has had some browning pains, but is by far the best personal finance tracking solution out there. Highly recommend.', '2.0.99', 'us', '2026-06-15T09:01:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14185778083', 'Kseggs', 5, 'Right for an old Mint user', 'I was a faithful Mint user for at least 10 years before they shut it down. I searched to find something new. Quicken Simplifi didn’t have the intuitive metrics I wanted, but Monarch does.', '2.0.99', 'us', '2026-06-15T07:15:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14184388190', 'WheresDavid@', 5, 'Feature Request', 'Add an option to export or print out the budget', '2.0.99', 'us', '2026-06-14T22:03:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14182769279', 'LightFighter29', 5, 'Best Budgeting App', 'I use budgeting software for over a decade, and this is definitely the easiest budgeting software I’ve ever used, and this helped me to switch up to more of a cash management system', '2.0.99', 'us', '2026-06-14T11:34:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14182021094', 'app falls short', 4, 'Great addition', 'With the exception of refreshing accounts mainly due to my Etrade accounts . I had to learn how to refresh them manually wich ar first was a little difficult. But over all this is a great App for keeping your Finances in check. Love it.', '2.0.99', 'us', '2026-06-14T07:48:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14178575452', 'TRINITY-626', 5, 'Monarch Made Taxes & Biz Ops So Much Easier!', 'If you’re looking for a budgeting app that is the complete package, this is it - it has an elegant design (+1–orange is my fave too), a UX that is easy to navigate and customize, for both quick glance features and in-depth info with charts, filters, tags, colors, etc. My personal fave features are the Recurring section where it lists all your monthly recurring income and expenses and shows you a calendar with dots on the days and notifies you in a few days in advance so you’re always prepared. The other is the Create Rule feature that allows you to take a transaction and customize it to automatically have attributes you assign for all future transactions. Say you have a business expense for supplies every few months that you want to tag (label) as business-related and/or as a tax write-off - any time you make this purchase in the future it will now have those tags. You can also edit the merchant name to better match what it reflects and much more. Lastly I recently had to fill out 6 months of profit & loss forms for legal purposes and I used the new AI they’ve implemented to automatically gather the items I specified, itemize them, and give me totals so I could simply plug-in the numbers (after double checking them for accuracy, of course 😉). I know there’s a number of good financial budgeting apps out there right now, but I’m glad I decided to try Monarch and it’s been so helpful with taxes and other legal uses that I’ve decided to keep subscribing at $14.99/month. At times, I wish it were a little cheaper, but when you consider the real-life implications of financial organization (or lack thereof) and how the practicality of an app like this changes the game for those things, the value you get in return is worth a lot more than $14.99 a month. Highly recommended app if you’re serious about your financial life.', '2.0.99', 'us', '2026-06-13T10:03:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1459319842'), '14177810240', 'MitchM16', 5, 'The Only Budgeting App That Has Stuck', 'I tried multiple budgeting apps and this is the only one that I’ve stuck with. It’s super easy to connect your accounts and track all your purchases. Without hyperbole, I’ve never felt better about my personal finances and it’s in large part due to this app.', '2.0.99', 'us', '2026-06-13T06:16:22-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14267780233', 'Danojr12', 2, 'Budget', 'It’s low key hard to navigate and the budget is hard to figure out and set up', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-05T16:03:14-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14267754106', 'dwmetzler', 2, 'Missing Critical Feature', 'The mobile app is super nice. But, without an Apple or Windows app it brings less value. BOTTOM Line: get an app out that does not require me to pickup my phone to use it.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-05T15:52:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14267461163', 'RN-Omie', 2, 'Not customizable', 'Does not let you export specific transactions to csv files. Makes transferring info to excel sheets difficult', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-05T14:00:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14267191973', 'NerdBot', 1, 'App is trash', 'This app is trash it does nothing like advertised it doesn’t lower your bills it just puts you in contact with scam companies offering garbage services that then sell your contact information starting a never ending harassment cycle. It also doesn’t help having a budget. That’s always two weeks behind on updating everything.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-05T12:28:22-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14266575427', 'hersh50', 2, 'They want to help you cancel subscriptions by signing you up for a new subscription.', 'I was hopeful and now I am very disappointed. They want to help you cancel subscriptions by signing you up for a new subscription. There were no surprises in the list of subscriptions that Rocket Money had, and subscriptions that I expected to see were missing. Waste of time for me so far.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-05T09:15:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14263903957', 'Bunkie345', 1, 'Ugh', 'It’s impossible to log into this program. Nothing works.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-04T16:46:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14262318235', 'syd2032', 4, 'So far so good', 'Just downloaded less than a week ago, so far I feel like I already have a better grasp on my spending habits!!', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-04T07:37:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14259650330', 'ghnyggdrstbhntvrbr h', 1, 'Not worth signing up', 'I signed up to get them to cancel a subscription I couldn’t find to cancel because that is what they say they do when you link your accounts. Well they couldn’t find the subscription and told me to cancel it myself. So yeah I will start with canceling this subscription.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T15:10:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14259614077', 'HisShepherd92', 5, 'Great Budget support', 'Get it and use it , be diligent and discipline, my life is better!', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T14:56:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14259289457', 'Roniesue', 2, 'Not really worth it', 'Not really getting the savings suggested when I signed up. Also, can be very quirky adding vendors you’d like them to negotiate with.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T12:58:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14258134478', 'AvJillJustTrying2222', 1, 'Not Helpful for managing subscriptions', 'Not at all helpful really for anything. It will cost you much more than you save. Cancelling a subscription is a joke. Much simpler to just do it yourself. The app is confusing and hard to use. Now I gotta figure out how to cancel it!', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T07:17:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14258114094', 'Hvactl03', 3, 'Annoying', 'The app is functional and ok to use, but my god the ads are so insanely annoying. There’s no such thing as an average person needing to budget that would be clueless about 23 subscriptions costing them $500 a month and who’s idea was it to get people in a podcast setting to talk about this app as well? Worst marketing I’ve ever seen', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T07:12:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14257805890', 'Shikaashay', 1, 'Save', 'I have been trying to save money, but it won’t link to my account. It’s linked to my account, but it won’t pull every time. I try to put something into the savings. It won’t let me it keeps showing a negative.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T05:45:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14256805997', 'Liz9449', 5, 'Liz T.', 'Rocket Money saved me hundreds. Removed unnecessary subscriptions.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T23:38:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14256102484', 'Mo G of LR', 5, 'Saves Me Money.', 'Saves me money!', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T19:06:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14256063693', 'haayhoney', 3, 'I love the app! But-', 'I really do love the app and the service it offers. However, im frequently getting notifications of "refunds" that were purchases that I have made and I have to report the issue. Hopefully with the update I just did maybe that issue may be fixed but it throws me and the numbers in the app off and makes the experience frustrating.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T18:52:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14255687148', 'loooooooômghhuytbh', 3, 'Goals', 'Not sure why it keeps turning my goals off, and I have to login to resume deposits in my goals', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T16:32:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14255050849', 'Lonaoz', 5, 'Has help me budget and save!', 'For a young guy out of college to now 4 years later I needed some help grasping my financials and being able to save for the future and present. Rocket Money has help me do that and create the proper basics to have down when sending, budgeting, and saving!', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T12:43:51-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14254378838', 'Tsunami73g', 1, 'Scam', 'They charged me for the service twice and the customer support isn’t responding to my messages. This is fraudulent app', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T09:19:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14254215242', 'Becketno', 1, 'Unhappy thus far', 'Rocket Money is only showing one subscription. I know I have several more just by looking at my iPhone and probably some that I don’t even remember', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T08:34:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14253499029', 'Martov', 1, 'Not as advertised', 'Does not let you cancel most subscriptions in the app.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T05:20:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14252864583', 'Ron Bauza', 5, 'Rocket Money', 'We have found Rocket Money to be a wonderful way to track income expenses. Categorizing everything. Simple easy to use. We highly recommend Rocket Money.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T01:40:15-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14250705903', 'Nanofloe', 5, 'Works like they said it would', 'Makes cancelling subscription really easy and another app that helps you track spending', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-01T12:11:50-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14250556381', 'jojobear97', 4, 'Rocket money', 'This app is actually pretty helpful seeing how much you actually spend.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-01T11:24:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14250195175', 'miclay', 1, 'This does not work', 'The items that were to be canceled have not been cancelled. Why am I paying for this?', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-01T09:38:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14250099805', 'prisifox', 1, 'Not helping to control false payments.', 'I have tried over the last couple of months for you all to help with charges from which I had no apps on and you all couldn’t intercept for reasons that don’t seem right. I no longer want to be a member of this app.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-01T09:11:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14249819630', 'Trekwoman21', 5, 'Really good app', 'I get a text message informing me about my spending so if there’s anything I can cancel I can do it in the app', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-07-01T07:56:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14248004932', 'lukaaa1234', 1, 'Subscribe', 'I didn’t even understand how I make a subscribe…..', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T21:39:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14247505598', 'Anonymous95￼', 1, 'Don’t download', 'Please don’t download rocket money they will sell your information or use it. I had an account with a cellular company and they tried buying things and adding more services to my account. Thankfully they knew my voice and it wasn’t mine. I actually had a conversation with the person who acted like me. He hung up after he was caught. They told me it was rocket money doing this', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T18:40:31-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14247064536', 'Ella Faiths mama', 1, 'Unknowingly being charged', 'I had cancelled this subscription thru my apple subscriptions… they continued charging thru the app & I had no idea. Super disappointed.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T16:05:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14246978812', 'Six6pack64', 1, 'Cancel my subscription', 'Cancel my order', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T15:34:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14246515238', 'em;))))))', 1, 'False advertising', 'Doesn’t do a single one of it claims. It found one subscription from my bank statements, and you have to manually enter everything. You can’t cancel subscriptions from the app, and when you delete the app after having it for a week they still charge you for months. Cool thought, horrific execution.', '14.1.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T12:53:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14245834221', 'Fernanda.zzz', 1, 'Subscription', 'You have to go into settings to completely cancel your subscription even if you delve the app they will keep charging you be ware!!!!', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T09:32:15-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14245801614', 'yamanjosh', 1, 'Wont link my bank', 'Terrible. Tried 6 months ago to link my bank then deleted the app, got it back today and went thru the whole process just for it to not let me link my bank account again. Terrible.', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T09:23:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14244918370', 'Ab-rod', 5, 'Check this out', 'Best app for managing my money and easy way to save money. I am not got with keeping track with my spending habits but Rocket Money had helped so much. Love this app 😎', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T05:33:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14244640171', 'Xx1butterxx1', 2, 'Start up process', 'Why do I have to add a home phone number when I don’t have one. Also required me to add work number and I’m not employed at this time. 😢', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T04:07:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14243383091', 'Taylorking3111', 5, 'Details', 'Very detailed', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T19:56:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14243131292', 'KreggSan', 1, 'App not functioning.', 'I’ve input a lot of personal information on this app for the app all of a sudden to give me an access denial.', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T18:24:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14242792272', 'Frankieliz', 5, 'Spending', 'Wow! This lets me know every penny and it’s shocking, but I appreciate knowing so I can control my spending better.', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T16:14:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14242624771', 'TakiGRE', 5, 'The best', 'Usually these apps when you connect your cards and such you always have to re-sync them and add a password and all the time Rocket Money doesn’t have that problem. Also, it’s really easy to use. I’d recommend it for everyone who wants to track their money.', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T15:08:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14241901983', 'Concern2026', 1, 'Awful experience, consumer beware.', 'I had smart savings goals and when I went to withdraw on one it stated that all the money was gone. Went from 1600 to 68. Good luck trying to talk to anyone but an AI that argues with you and gives you no answers. Your money is not safe here. I’ll put it in an interest earning savings that has actual people to help if something happens. Consumers beware because they will steal your money.', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T11:01:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14241563931', 'Joecool937', 1, 'Another price hike', 'For an app that is for saving money the rate increase again isn’t fair. What services as improved to make the rate hike better to understand.', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T09:22:47-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14240925685', 'oaky!', 1, 'Not helpful unless you are already cooked', 'If you pay cash for things or dont have many subscriptions or services it really isn’t helpful. The app is getting nearly EVERY category of spending wrong and is god awful at attempting to adapt to whatever is going on with my finances. The budget is terrible, genuinely not many options if I want to use it and allow it to track my budget instead of doing it myself I am going to have to go correct tens or hundreds of items of spending that are not categorized properly by default. Maybe it would be helpful if you were super in debt and had subscriptions and credit cards and stuff. I simply don’t use those, I was trying to use it to budget to help me save to move out while renting temporarily.', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T06:32:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14240883896', 'JesseO515', 1, 'Just a another bill to add to your other bills.', 'Don’t see any savings, can’t cancel for me the only thing I wanted it to cancel for me.', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T06:20:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14240681889', 'Hello Kitty Kashy', 5, 'Helpful', 'I see things that I was not able to see before. I am more aware of my spending now. Thanks.', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T05:24:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14239384218', '!?):$!,!/‘nx', 1, 'Scammed me out of my money', 'I downloaded this app without buying a premium subscription and they charged me for it, so i recommend to really take care of your money because they s', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-28T21:02:46-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14238631400', 'Blah2340', 1, 'I can’t Update My Account', 'because I don’t have access to my phone number on file there needs to be and update where I can access my email instead of my phone number', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-28T16:02:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14238035627', 'JayDTNguyen', 5, 'Rocket Money', 'Easy to Understand', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-28T12:19:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1130616675'), '14237253100', 'Warrior of prayer!', 5, 'Focused', 'Focused on the importance of financial health and literacy. It helps me with reminders and planning.', '13.18.0', 'us', '2026-06-28T08:19:14-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '14218399910', 'Caitland988', 1, 'This app is only free to download', 'Once downloading the app there is no way around a paywall. Where they want you to sign up for a free trial of their premium services. I just wanted the free plan. Thanks for nothing.', '5.19.3', 'us', '2026-06-23T15:43:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '14147825282', 'Mr.C_yoho', 2, 'So many bugs', 'This app is way more worse than two years ago. A lot of issues including not able to set my default not counting credit card payment, reset all my previous split transactions', '5.19.3', 'us', '2026-06-05T11:46:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '14095388968', 'BeamerDude', 1, 'Trial Subscription Cannot Be Cancelled', 'Beware!! This app does not show up as having a subscription in the AppStore settings, so the free trial cannot be cancelled!!! This is horrible!', '5.19.3', 'us', '2026-05-22T21:17:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '14093812952', '8h0st', 1, 'Unfortunately', 'I would give a better review if the app would allow me to access it, instead all I get is “suspicious ip address”', '5.19.3', 'us', '2026-05-22T11:01:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '14091495400', 'CRANTON23', 5, 'Perfecto', 'Gmgood app', '5.19.3', 'us', '2026-05-21T20:01:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '14089493270', 'twomoms42', 1, 'Waste or time & money', 'Paid for annual subscription and seemed to be great for a few months. FINALLY, got everything lined up after many hours now my bank is not updating data. This is the second time. I contacted support and they apologized and just said their tech was working on it. After 6 weeks decided to delete the account and start over-lost all my work. Now it happened again. Money and time lost…not good in this economy when I am trying to budget.', '5.19.3', 'us', '2026-05-21T07:29:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '14080587033', 'CS3205', 1, 'Don’t Bother', 'I never write reviews but I feel like I should warn people since the company won’t. Unless you are willing to pay for a subscription or check your account every day, they will reset everything. After every 24 hours all your data will be gone with no way to get it back. No warning either. Seems a little ridiculous for an app promoting good money habits to make people addicted to looking at balances.', '5.19.3', 'us', '2026-05-18T19:45:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '14079304462', 'iguy_4', 5, 'Finally Workong', 'Finally seems like the connection issues are fixed. Hopefully it stays that way. I much prefer this app over any other I have tried.', '5.19.3', 'us', '2026-05-18T11:10:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '14073054739', 'DaisyG..', 5, 'Heaven sent', 'Pocket guard is literally heaven sent, haven’t been able to steward my finances well until I got this app. Makes beginner budgeting and expense tracking and goal setting so easy! I download/tested like 5 other of the “best apps” and PocketGuard was clearly the best, easiest set up, clear dashboard, and visually smooth , very good insights even helped us catch fraud on credit card to quickly put a stop to it. The best app ever', '5.19.3', 'us', '2026-05-16T18:44:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '14038016434', 'UWbadgers16', 3, 'Slow and clunky', 'This app used to be quite snappy. Somewhere in the last couple of months, likely when the Pace feature was introduced, that all changed. UI interactions are slow, the app freezes for seconds at a time, and there’s been no improvement despite opening tickets with support.', '5.19.2', 'us', '2026-05-07T06:25:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13960939705', 'Good288:?75?&8', 5, 'Fantastic', 'Awesome app, best one I’ve ever used for money management. Question to developers: when you click into Net Income from the dashboard page, you are shown your income vs spending breakdown for each month, which is great. When you select a month, and click into Spending, you are then shown a list of your transactions for that month. Any chance we can get this broken down by budget/category first? Then the level below that can be transactions?', '5.19.2', 'us', '2026-04-15T09:08:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13954435903', 'SanLouisKid99', 5, 'Evolving Nicely', 'It’s received a lot of very nice improvements over the years. The improvements have added up to make an excellent app.', '5.19.2', 'us', '2026-04-13T11:16:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13953465743', 'Katkakakakakat', 1, 'wow', 'The fact that this app can’t successfully sync with American Express renders it completely useless for us. I’m disappointed that they don’t disclose this bug ahead of time because it compromises ease of use, which is literally the whole point of the app. I spent more than 30 bucks on a broken product. I wish I could get my money back.', '5.19.2', 'us', '2026-04-13T05:44:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13951629723', 'Loveour2dogs', 2, 'Great concept- terrible customer service', 'Had high hopes for this app as I like the easy adaption but I was unable to log in on my laptop to my account as it would only clock and I was also unable to get my joint accounts with my husband as primary integrated into the app. Emailed several times for customer service assistance with screenshots but went days without a response and no help. I feel like a simple call would have rectified this but going back and forth by email for weeks isn’t helpful. Will be canceling the app and requesting a refund from Visa due to lack of customer support.', '5.19.2', 'us', '2026-04-12T15:19:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13943532490', 'Zzzeeerrrttt', 5, 'Simply the best', 'I was a Mint user for years until… well you know the story. ;0). I reviewed almost every alternative and PocketGuard is hands down the best.', '5.19.2', 'us', '2026-04-10T10:15:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13940761395', 'Jake222567568', 5, 'Changed the game', 'Love this app so much. I was a completely novice to this kind of thing. It can take a beat to get familiar with everything but I tried a bunch of apps and this was the most intuitive. Now I can’t imagine life without it', '5.19.1', 'us', '2026-04-09T15:09:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13903905374', 'Pereidenko', 2, 'Security Concerns', 'Within a week of opening my account, I received a security alert ping from one of my credit cards due to potential fraudulent activity. Additionally, they use Billshark to offer bill negotiation services, but that 3rd party service is very challenging to cancel. Finally, the app doesn’t offer a great layout for all of your finances if you split bills with other members of household , and makes it difficult to track transfers between accounts. Would not recommend.', '5.19.1', 'us', '2026-03-30T09:07:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13891857310', 'Rod Pur', 4, 'Overall great experience', 'I’ve been using pocketguard around 6 months now. While there have been some sync issues on occasion they have always worked themselves out. Recently, I’ve had an issue where I have lost a couple transactions on the same day. Aggravating, but not a show stopper. I do love some of the new features though. Only thing that worries me is that once new features are added, that’s when i see little bugs start showing up. Overall, Pocketguard is a nice tool to monitor your spending with. It would get 5 stars if it weren’t for the little quirks that occasionally arise.', '5.19.1', 'us', '2026-03-27T01:53:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13889494719', 'Chandieeee', 1, 'App doesn’t work', 'Not sure if it’s a bug? But hopefully this review will pop up to the developers and they can fix it. I can’t get past the start my membership screen because it redirects me to my browser to a blank page that won’t load. Will probably have to go with another app if they don’t fix this soon.', '5.19.1', 'us', '2026-03-26T09:20:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13872106779', 'Sofifi1234', 5, 'Best on Appstore IMHO', 'In my humble opinion this is the best free Budgeting App on the Appstore, as I have tried basically all of the other popular free budgeting apps available. I specifically appreciate the bank account sync feature which not only syncs with my bank but also syncs my Checking, Savings, and Credit Accounts (it is a day behind in terms of sync updating but that is not an issue for me). I also appreciate the separate management of bills/utilities/subscriptions, income, transfers between accounts, and other transactions. The transaction sorting and tagging are very easy to use and actually help with tracking transaction and money flow. The Insights page which provides a pie chart of spending based on your chosen budget categories as well as a line chart that tracks spending over the course of the month are extremely useful when comparing spending month-to-month and across categories. The one thing I would suggest as others have mentioned in their reviews is being able to edit budgets/transactions from previous and future months. But with that being said I do very much like having the dashboard, budget, and insight views being geared toward only showing one month’s information, being the month you are currently in. I highly recommend this app.', '5.19.1', 'us', '2026-03-21T09:35:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13857674253', 'trulyn kendrick', 1, 'DON’T START TRIAL', 'I got charged $68 at the end of my trial but cancelled my trial the day of getting it due to me not liking the overall app in general. Thankfully my bank flagged and declined it but very scammy app. DONT RECOMMEND', '5.19', 'us', '2026-03-17T06:41:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13843529322', 'Colton1246337', 1, 'Awful', 'Doesn’t sync up right. Amounts of bills will randomly change. Doesn’t categorize spending accurately. Will have bills show up as other spending. Constantly having to edit income, spending, and budgets. Overall worst app and complete waste of money. Will not buy again', '5.19', 'us', '2026-03-13T05:53:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13759715516', 'streechy', 1, 'Easy fix but they’re not interested', 'Tried the free trial. Couldn’t see any pending transactions. Checked-my bank DOES share them with PocketGuard. Reached out to PG support and they took a long time to answer. Then they wanted screenshots of my banking app with the missing transactions. They refused to help without it. But kept sending me emails asking how they could help optimize my experience. Cancelled the trial.', '5.18.4', 'us', '2026-02-17T09:32:30-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13705633818', '6ta1', 4, 'Good budget app', 'I like the app in general, it is not yet at the level of clarity and user friendliness as what Mint used to be. I do love the option of 1 lifetime payment rather than monthly fee.', '5.18.3', 'us', '2026-02-02T10:54:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13691441174', 'TexasLTC', 5, 'Great App!', 'This app does everything I currently need! Helps me keep track and isn’t a headache to use. Thanks!!', '5.18.3', 'us', '2026-01-29T19:32:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13690162168', 'SlayBells', 5, 'INCREDIBLE!!!', 'EDIT: PLEASE ADD A NOTES SECTION.. I would like to describe amount of $ for Electrolyte powder but if I hashtag it, it might include the price of protein bars and pickles since it’s all groceries… I would love a way to add a price to the hashtag, or quickly see notes searchable without adding 100’s of extra hashtags.. I LOVE THIS APP! spent about 4 hours a year ago and set up some categories but never fully grasped it and didn’t continue using it. But, as a part of my New Year’s Resolutions… I am taking a photo of every receipt in TurboScan, putting it in a folder named receipts, naming it with the day like 2026.1.15 ‘Store’ ‘$ amount’ … and then 3 days later when transactions finally show up in Pocketguard, I can easily reference my recipt photos and add it to transactions… it gets even better! I am able to read my CostCo receipt and split it into 5+ categories.. I made one for Kitchen, Meat, Equipment, (because Groceries is too vague, shopping is too vague, but I did use Groceries and Clothing as well) THAT WAY, I can quickly switch between the picture of the Receipt and my calculator and add up all my meat, X by .0975 for tax, then add the original amount back! BAM! now I have the exact amount I spent on the Meat category for this transaction.. do this same step with 4 categories and the 5th category is the last amount left so no calculating… Now my Budgets are correctly tracked down to the Pickle, Ziploc, or Storage Bin! A CAUTION AND WORD TO DEVELOPER! I wish there was a ‘ARE YOU SURE’ button after hitting the ‘Change for ALL Transactions’ Maybe there is? I don’t always feel safe Changing the Generic Default ‘Shopping’ category to… well… ‘Nicotine or Gum’ because I have a lot of categories and I would HATE for all my Amazon ‘Shopping’ Purchases to then auto change to the ‘Gum’ category!!! seems like a tiny oversight that could cause almost irreversible damage if we spend years categorizing… one small click without looking could destroy hours worth of tagging. WHICH brings me to the next idea… Is there an UNDO BUTTON? if so I haven’t found it. it would be amazing if we accidentally edited like 350 transactions, and then were easily able to click UNDO. Please let me know if this is possible. Some tips for people, here are my categories. Instead of just Auto and Transport, I added one for GAS. Instead of just Groceries, I added SNACKS, MEAT, GUM, COOKING, KITCHEN. That way spices and oil goes into Cooking, Ziplocs and Appliances goes into Kitchen, Pickles, Mayo, Mustard goes into Groceries, Ribs, Shrimp, Eggs, Tuna, Meatballs goes into Meat (I’m doing Keto/Carnivore, and Carbs like Cookies, Chips, Ice Cream goes into Snacks. That way I can really know how much I’m spending on junk food. BOWLING, VIDEOGAMES, MOVIES, EQUIPMENT, TOOLS, BATHROOM, CASH SAVINGS, ACCESSORIES, RECURRING BILLS, SUBSCRIPTIONS, SUPPLEMENTS, GIFTS, (CASH AND ATM, TRANSFER - so I can easily see how much got added from the budget sections) So doing this basically makes the default Pocketguard app 3X more detailed. It’s a joy to see. I’m going to spend the next 3 months dialing it in and change budgets amounts accordingly. I will try to use the ‘Roll Over’ feature for like… Yearly Subscriptions, and try to save that over time, Because like the Carly app is $100 a year and always catches me off guard!! So! in that case, I also got a leather A6 Money binder that has clear zipper pockets that fit dollar bills… I will cut some vinyl and label them the Budget category name… and try to save as much as I can. Anything I don’t spend, like clothes, in 3 months I’d have $30 bucks saved, I could add that to my Cash Savings… If my Cash Savings gets over $1000, I could then move it to the Investments categories! It’s always harder to spend $ when you have physical cash… you feel more guilty actually letting go of it. SO MY TIPS TO ANYONE! 1. Get the TurboScan app $10 lifetime 2. make a folder for _Receipts 3. everytime you buy something, scan the receipt and name it ‘YYYY.MM.DD - STORE - $$.$$’ 4. Add more detailed categories 5. make a bunch of rules for stores to auto tag and categorize to help future transactions 6. 3 days later, find your Pocketguard transactions, reference your receipts, split the transactions like I explained, categorize and hashtag it, add receipt photo 7. Watch your budgets start to fill up precisely broken down to the itemized receipt 8. Have confidence knowing after a few months, you’ll know exactly what to budget for and how to plan ahead 9. Keep adding to your manually made CASH SAVINGS budget, so you always have an emergency fund 10. After 6 months, start investing everything extra that you didn’t spend!!! BOOM! BAM! THWACK! that’s how you use this app! so in total, I spent 4 hours a year ago, and 8 hours this week setting it up… Now my system works extremely well, and planning every Sunday to spend 30 min - 1 hour categorizing.. so if you feel hopeless, don’t give up! It’s like I ‘Game-ified’ Budgeting with POCKETGUARD!! Just spend about 10-15 hours laying your foundation with Rules for frequent stores to auto add hashtags and categorize, and add more detailed budgets for stuff you spend $ on! -A :)', '5.18.3', 'us', '2026-01-29T11:08:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13682495084', 'I did this for the levels', 5, 'Easy to use, cost effective, efficient', 'This is perfect for someone who wants a simple, straightforward spend tracker and budget app. Highly recommend.', '5.18.3', 'us', '2026-01-27T11:05:38-07:00'),
