((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='949414211'), '13471168306', 'Blaze of Glory123', 1, 'Absolute garbage', 'Before signing up, I was told I could just manually enter my income and expenses without having to link my bank account. When I first signed up to create a profile, it was trying to force me into linking a bank account with no other option. I thought maybe I messed up somewhere in the signing up process, so I tried to backtrack all the way to the beginning, and it wouldn’t let me. So then I deleted the profile and tried to start again, then it said that my IP address was suspicious, which makes no sense, and it wouldn’t let me create a new profile. So to hell with it!', '5.18', 'us', '2025-12-03T10:24:13-07:00'),
