((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14254011603', 'ImARainbowUnicorn', 1, 'Inaccurate and Hard to Read', 'When the verdict of my slumber is shown, it is basically impossible to comprehend its findings. In other words, the graphs you provide make no sense and the sensor for sleep is very off. Turning on this app via my watch caused my watch to die mid-day and I still found the results useless. The actually set-up of the app is similar to Hulu as it is not user friendly. I would recommend the app SleepWatch over this app and if you’re reading this, I urge you to make that change. I would not recommend this app to anyone because it doesn’t work and was a waste of money. I will stick with my $38 a year subscription to SleepWatch.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-07-02T07:41:04-07:00'),
