((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14244788236', 'stirza', 4, 'Helpful sleep app', 'I have been using this app for a few years and find that it provides useful information. Some recommendations for changes- Should you sync with time zone changes? (Sleep wake consistency trend) Your trends in are over 30 days. I think it would be helpful to see trends over longer periods. At least perhaps one year? Thank you!', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-30T04:54:37-07:00'),
