((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14229125702', 'Woshiairy', 2, 'Not accurate at all', 'It’s not tracking the sleep accurately. It counts as sleep time even after I get up and walk around for 20 mins. Or when I charge the watch before bedtime. The deep sleep time totally wrong too. The integrated apple health app gives much better results, and it’s free.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-26T08:37:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14228851836', '393Hemi', 5, 'Very helpful Knowledge', 'I use it to track all aspects of my sleep and added heart tracking; With the knowledge received I can adjust my life habits to make better sleep all around but mostly my Fero Dlerp hours that help my brain. Wearing my watch at night is a non issue for me.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-26T07:23:22-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14220185857', 'B Briggs', 5, 'Wonderful app', 'I have really benefited from using this app. I check it first thing when I get up every morning. It gives thorough and great information about all of my sleep the night before. It also gives me valuable heart information. I am still trying to learn about all its features to get the most use out of it. It’s one time small charge fee is great for me as a senior citizen who likes to follow sleep and general health. I recommend this app for anyone using an Apple Watch like me.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-24T04:10:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14220078966', 'Oh_LaLa', 5, 'Saved my sleep', 'This app helped me to see the dips in my oxygen levels at night. Had a sleep study which confirmed that my oxygen was definitely decreasing sometimes to upper 70%. No sleep apnea thank goodness. I was prescribed nighttime oxygen and I feel like a new person. Thank you developers you saved my brain!!!!', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-24T03:31:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14214418115', 'calico traveler', 5, 'Love this app!!', 'Tried several before this app. No need to look further!!', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-22T14:45:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14212996001', 'GrannyFrannie', 5, 'Love it!', 'Best sleep app I’ve tried. It’s the most accurate and reliable. I’ve been using for several years now and tried others that promised better results but didn’t. You can’t go wrong with this one.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-22T07:08:53-07:00'),
