((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14212440385', 'Salvisa Kenny B', 5, 'Very helpful insights', 'I’ve used this app for several years now and it has helped me improve my sleep hygiene. Much like food logging, the insights I gain from this app have given me the awareness I need to make better decisions during the day and before bedtime to ensure I am maximizing the effectiveness of my sleep time.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-22T04:08:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14212248727', 'S.hirschy', 5, 'Still trying to figure out how to customize it after many years', 'It shows I’m sleeping when I’m not. I love seeing how well I’m prepared for the day based on my sleep. I think next I will activate the snore indicator. This app is great and I love that it is a one time only paid app.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-22T02:52:13-07:00');
