((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14211673492', 'Claudine0321', 5, 'Love this', 'I absolutely love this AutoSleep app. I just started to use it again bc my sleep was horrible and wanted to know what I was doing not right. This helps me to get to bed on time and to understand sometimes why I am still so tired even after I slept for 8 hours Thanks', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-21T22:20:53-07:00'),
