((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14208829839', 'BBTC40', 5, 'Perfect Sleep App', 'Love this sleep tracker app. It gives me all of the information I need to track my recovery and sleep in an easy to understand format. I highly recommend it.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-21T05:06:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14205881805', 'CMc III', 5, 'Best Sleep Tracker', 'I’ve used a couple of sleep trackers, but AutoSleep is by far the best. So glad my children introduced me to this.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-20T09:39:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14205849761', 'R8bert F!nn3yfr0ck', 5, 'My go to 3rd party app for sleep tracking', 'Before apple had their own sleep tracking, this was the best app on the market. Even now I use both because this provides a deeper insight into my sleep patterns and helps me understand my sleep/wake cycles.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-20T09:29:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14205321574', 'fzouki', 5, 'Huge help', 'First of all I love that there''s no stupid subscription. Thank you developers both for that and for an awesome app. If you know you are not sleeping well but are having trouble pinpointing the problem, this app gives you so much information that you can start to figure out what to work on. There is SO MUCH information and my sleep has improved both in quantity and quality- which means my quality life has also improved.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-20T06:54:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14203753054', 'Botu57', 5, 'Love this app!', 'I have been using it for about two years now. At a minimum I understand more about my sleep habits. The biggest benefit - I have made a more conscious effort to sleep, wake on a more imposed time schedule.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-19T20:41:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14203672272', 'Jan610', 5, 'Excellent app', 'This is the most accurate app I have found. Highly recommend !!!', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-19T20:09:47-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14203616846', 'airhound', 1, 'Doesn’t know how to tell time .', 'Went to bed the other night midnight thirty and woke up eight hours later . The app said I woke up after 11 hours sleep . It does stupid things like saying I went to sleep at noon and woke up a 6 pm . The hours it counts are wrong . The time I go to bed are wrong . Buy a Fitbit .', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-19T19:48:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14203082265', 'p, jc', 5, 'Excellent', 'Great app. Lots of helpful information.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-19T16:19:15-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14202319021', 'sjscott5280', 4, 'It works', 'It works without asking for money from you daily. Like every app does ruthlessly if you want to use them.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-19T11:39:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14200993182', 'Sleep / health', 5, 'Auto sleep', 'I love this app . It has helped my health in all ways .. Not a better one out there . I can even tell when I’m coming down with something before it happens . Amazing', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-19T04:56:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14199704690', 'Car0lineB', 2, 'Confused by the Love', 'I am so confused by all of the positive reviews for this app. My main complaint is totally on me, which is why I’m giving it 2 stars not 1: it’s so overly complicated, micromanagy, and maximalist. I want something simple and clean. I don’t need the chaos of 12 rings telling me about my sleep. It is horrible at tracking my sleep. I slept 2 hours last night? And 11 the night before? I sleep about 7.5 hours every night and am only in bed for about 5 minutes on either side. I’m sure there are tweaks I could make to help this but why should I need to? The sleep debt thing is not backed by science and there is no world in which I would need to get 15 hours of sleep tomorrow night to make up for a bad night’s sleep. That’s not how anything works! If I could fix the tracking issue and get a simpler UI, I’d be all in but I guess I’ll just stick with the Health app. App deleted :(', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-18T19:50:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14197825063', 'Teachermom123', 5, 'Awesome App!', 'This app is awesome! It helps me see when I’ve had sufficient (or insufficient) sleep. I charge my Apple Watch first thing in the morning so I can wear it all day and night to track activity and sleep. Love this app! Highly recommend!', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-18T08:45:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14193933853', 'Catechizer', 5, 'Way more insightful and accurate than Apple app', 'well been using this app now for a while and it is very good it helped me adjust my adjustable bed so that I got the right angle to greatly reduce my sleep apnea which was hitting into the dangerous area. I am really enjoying this app well worth the price the Apple version is OK but this thing is way more accurate', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-17T08:52:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14193064321', 'Vicster8', 5, 'Great Sleep App', 'This app gives you a great look into your daily sleep and your sleep habits overall. It breaks your sleep down into so many useful categories.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-17T04:30:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14191919886', 'Infidoll', 5, 'I love this app developer’s apps', 'I’ve been using this and HeartWatch, another app by this developer for years. I love them both and check them every day! ❤️', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-16T20:13:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14189396254', 'S_F_1', 5, 'My favorite!!', 'This is my favorite sleep app! It’s easy to understand and gives great information about my sleep!!', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-16T05:58:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14189386865', 'leehoeffel', 5, 'Top of the heap!', 'If you want a true look at your sack time, including your deep sleep, this app has it all!', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-16T05:55:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14182875480', 'Twispies', 5, 'Great app', 'I like the graphics easy to follow and no data collected.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-14T12:08:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14182193325', 'RobiGlobi', 4, 'Love this App to Monitor my Health', 'I have been using this App for years now and I couldn’t Imagine going through the week without it. I love the insight into my sleep.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-14T08:38:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14178930964', 'troendy2521', 5, 'Favorite sleep tracker', 'Finally found a sleep tracking app that provides the data I need in a way I can understand. Helps me evaluate & make changes to my sleep hygiene.', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-13T11:58:29-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14177698419', 'F Forns', 5, 'Great sleep tracking app', 'Neat A good record keeping tool if you are interested in keeping record of your sleep patterns, for information and means of Improving your weak points..improving', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-13T05:41:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14177553588', 'Dave''s ITunes Acct.', 5, 'Awesome App', 'I highly recommend this app 😀', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-13T04:53:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1164801111'), '14177227484', 'K1INGSOLOMON', 5, 'MUST DOWNLOAD AND USE!', 'This changed the way I see how the human body sleeps. If you want to really see how good or bad your sleep prep and cycles are this is the app for you. If you want to have better behavior, this is the app for you. I’ve noticed I’ve gotten amazing sleep by purposely making sure I actually utilize the app. Once you see your numbers your excuses of being tired either will be valid or False. Good luck', '6.16', 'us', '2026-06-13T02:52:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14251284796', 'the-coderok', 1, 'Non-skippable screens asking to start free trial', 'What’s up with the screens asking to start free trial that can’t be closed? (Have to keep the app). I already got used to regular reminders to subscribe, but these screens that have no close button is some dark UX pattern stuff. I guess it is time to look for simple and not bloated alternative', '7.9.1', 'us', '2026-07-01T15:33:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14251259156', 'ColoradoAussie', 1, 'You can’t change serving size', 'When logging meals, the app assumes a single serving size and doesn’t allow you to change it. Instead it forces you to calculate and update the macros yourself (protein, calories, etc.). It doesn’t allow you to change the serving size or portion size. Also very difficult to get a refund. They require that you go through Apple to request a refund.', '7.9.1', 'us', '2026-07-01T15:23:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14240962175', 'Nanjack50', 5, 'Love', 'So very helpful when I use it to track my fasting goals.', '7.9.1', 'us', '2026-06-29T06:42:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14239585238', 'ScrabbleHound2', 1, 'Major bug!', 'I have listed my weight as 315 pounds, with a goal of 250… eventually. However it appears to be calculating my program as though I were 142 pounds. I’m not sure how to LOSE weight at 142 to get me to 250 as a LOSS, so I am concerned that it is going to give me a program for a weight GAIN, and not a loss at all. Definitely a very bad bug here! Especially since it wants me to hit 199 g of protein per day which is unreasonably high!', '7.9.1', 'us', '2026-06-28T22:29:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14237170768', 'Rosisimo', 4, 'Overall good app', 'First week using it. Has good tools and tips. I dislike that no matter how good your meals try to be, they always have a tone of not good enough. Only way you get a good job on a meal is if it’s only protein.', '7.9.1', 'us', '2026-06-28T07:55:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14222180788', 'mass confusion', 1, 'Too many pay walls', 'I came back to this app after a few years and the only thing accessible on the free version now is the timer. And the pop ups to try a subscription every time I open the app are making me delete this for good.', '7.9.1', 'us', '2026-06-24T14:41:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14221097455', 'MariDarling', 3, 'I’ve used zero on and off for 6 years', 'Overpriced; too many upsells; too many features.', '7.9.1', 'us', '2026-06-24T08:46:04-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14220522224', 'Giansel', 1, 'Greedy and shady behavior', 'I’ve had this app for three years. It was always free. Now to even open the app they want you to pay now. I can’t even get to my profile or see my past stats. The minute you open the app you have to pay to unlock. Smh this is so greedy and shows this will be their downfall.', '7.9.0', 'us', '2026-06-24T06:00:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14213245048', 'Evergreen Monster', 3, 'Cool App, Hard to Cancel Zero Plus', 'I like the app but having to sign up for Zero Plus just to get into the app was a bit shady. Also can’t seem to get Zero Plus to cancel so they will probably end up with my money.', '7.9.0', 'us', '2026-06-22T08:22:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14209166543', 'Mary BB23', 1, 'Faulty App and Fraudulent Charges', 'I wanted to try this app for the free 7 day trial and the app said it would notify me before charging me for the subscription. After a few days, I decided I didn’t want to subscribe, but no matter how many times I tried to get to my subscription in the app, the app locked up and refused to let me cancel. Then, without notifying me, they charged me for the full year. Will be reporting to BBB.', '7.9.0', 'us', '2026-06-21T06:55:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14205756320', 'dmarie1996', 1, 'No good', 'Won’t let me do anything without a purchase? Thought the app was supposed to be free from what I’ve heard', '7.9.0', 'us', '2026-06-20T09:01:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14193582397', 'DTorresTX89', 1, 'Paywall', 'After being a loyal user for awhile now I am now being forced to PAY?? This was an integral part of my diet and life. I’m so upset they are forcing us to pay. I WILL not be doing that. There are zero benefits to paying for it except for my past data. Unfortunately I will be finding a new way to track which is so unfortunate.', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-17T07:10:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14192119578', 'Nikko23@0', 1, 'Only good for tracking water and fast', 'Easier to log food on MyFitnessPal', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-16T21:39:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14191233720', 'CincyBearcat66', 1, 'Buyer beware', 'Cancelling is a nightmare', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-16T15:48:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14184071803', 'Bxx Kane', 1, 'Used to be good, now spams you with ads you can''t x out of', 'Title', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-14T19:42:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14181391621', 'jamie_Farlend', 2, 'Haven’t eaten in a month: why is it encouraging that?', 'I slipped up and didn’t manage the app for a few weeks. Checked back in and the app was encouraging me because I have entered the “fat burning” stage. I wish the algorithm in this app acknowledged that there is a limit to how long you can safely fast. Otherwise if you are susceptible it can promote disordered eating.', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-14T04:24:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14179957491', 'AlicefromWonderland2', 1, 'Zero:Fasting and Food Tracker', 'Don’t like it, because it keeps showing the free trial, and it says that I’ve got my Parents approval. I’m 48 years old, and I don’t need their permission.', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-13T18:23:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14172905628', 'Joyti_k', 1, 'Forced free trail sign up', 'Once I got set up with the app I could not move forward without signing up for a free trial and providing a credit card. Hoping this was a glitch? Otherwise that is horrible shady user experience.', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-12T00:36:14-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14171675796', 'GuySmiley’sGirl', 1, 'not free', 'I only downloaded this because it was listed as the best of the free tracking apps. It’s not free at all, there’s no free version whatsoever. That’s false advertising and is illegal.', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-11T15:46:51-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14169745432', 'Aritcfgyt', 1, 'This app doesn’t work', 'There’s no way to properly enter a meal. For the app to determine calories or macros. The enter a meal field just has you typing or take a pic. And guess what all this is a lot of data for them to sell. Without actually doing any work for you. Skip this app.', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-11T05:38:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14169717080', 'bitbrains', 4, 'Very useful and fun to use', 'Nice UI and very useful. Only complaint is the notifications in the app are all off but the app keeps spamming me with notifications. Had to disable it in system settings.', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-11T05:29:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14169561722', 'Chascona$', 2, 'Not worth it', 'There assessment of my macros is inaccurate most of the time. Make suggestions on my meals which they have no business commenting on.', '7.8.0', 'us', '2026-06-11T04:37:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14152322483', 'JanythD', 5, 'I love this app', 'I have had to much success using this app so far. The flames when peak fat burn is happening are exceptionally great motivation to KEEP GOING. I trying have been enjoying tracking my meals and water intake. Planning to purchase the subscription once my month trial runs out. Love it!', '7.7.1', 'us', '2026-06-06T15:22:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14143363452', 'User-6-26', 2, 'New user with difficulty', 'I find it not totally easy to enter data. For example I entered data for two days and it was not logged. The help function is not very easy to find. Editing an incorrect fast maybe possible, but not obvious. I assume the last meal and first meal would log the start and end of my fast. I paid. There appears that one can’t edit or even display my info on a PC. I am probably too old school. I don’t use my smart phone and devices as my only device nor do I trust them for privacy. I am maybe too critical. But, right now I can’t give a higher rating. The nutrition files are excellent. Software not so much.', '7.7.1', 'us', '2026-06-04T08:34:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14140820092', 'foosball_p', 3, 'Sloooow app launch', 'This used to be my favorite fasting app but lately it’s become unusable because the app takes so damn long to open up an I see the splash screen forever before it actually shows app data.', '7.7.1', 'us', '2026-06-03T15:56:34-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14130011615', 'Alirexxxa', 1, 'Not worth it.', 'Terrible app. Gimmick. Not even a free trial is worth having this app.', '7.7.0', 'us', '2026-05-31T22:39:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14109726263', 'Roadrunz', 3, 'Easy to Use, Aggressive Salesmanship', 'I was nearly 2.5 days into my first fast, and during that time the app was a joy to use. However, the application wouldn’t let me do anything other than sign up for a free trial for their paid subscription (the mag screen couldn’t be dismissed). I don’t want or need the subscriber features, and couldn’t do anything else in the app, so I uninstalled it.', '7.7.0', 'us', '2026-05-26T15:28:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14102739676', 'Grazsoo', 1, 'Complete Garbage', 'Couldn’t even make it past the 3rd screen to try and sign it without it crashing every time. Junk.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-24T19:03:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14090351319', 'Badappyyyy', 1, 'Forced upgrade suspicious!', 'I have a paid for annual subscription, being forced to upgrade is suspicious and makes believe there is nefarious intentions by the developers. Highly don’t recommend!', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-21T12:13:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14090316917', 'Big papa pump 👍', 5, 'Fitness', 'Been very helpful and keeping track of whatever you need to fast', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-21T12:01:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14089601005', 'Imhere81', 2, 'Won’t be renewing', 'Just started IF and this app was recommended. In contrast to advertised “free” version you can only get into the app if you subscribe. So, ok I did. The level of customization is minimal. One of the biggest deficits is that you cannot go back to the previous day to log a missed meal. (If supposedly this data is used to calculate your fat burning wouldn’t you want it accurate?) The recommended fix was to “set a timer” to remind you to log. WW and other apps allow for this so it can’t be that hard to add in developers! Will be cancelling at end of this subscription if not improved. If it only going to inform me of fast time I can do that on the timer function on my phone. 😳', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-21T08:02:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14085890058', 'Katieeeee93', 1, 'Forces you to get subscriptions', 'Just wanted to track fasting, would not let me close out of free trial where it charges in a few days. Misleading so say there’s a free option when you can’t opt out and try basic.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-20T07:41:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14083516401', 'food logging not good', 3, 'logging food', 'not very happy with the way it’s set up i want to be able to add the AMOUNT of food im logging . like 1/2 cup of cheese, 1 hard boiled egg etc. will not be paying for full subscription due to this.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-19T15:08:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14080783109', '11Mer11', 3, 'Great! Could use more connectivity and widgets', 'I wish that I could connect to my Garmin Connect app. Also more widgets would be awesome like a quick meal log, water log, fasting timer combo or just small individual ones that could be added however you want. Overall, I love the ease of tracking and adjusting data. I also love the calorie/protein count. Great app, I just want a bit more.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-18T21:19:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14079836302', 'TheFlyPaperPodcast', 2, 'Data Miner', 'No reason to collect my data. Bad App.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-18T14:28:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14079391618', 'bugz0r', 1, 'Hard paywall', 'Have to pay to use', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-18T11:41:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14078472461', 'aChaoticBi', 3, 'Subscription', 'I used to have this app and I loved it, it was super easy to use and free, but now that I’ve redownloaded it I see that I have to subscribe and pay for it. I hate when apps do that without letting the people downloading know, like at that point just make them pay before downloading the app.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-18T06:42:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14067325176', 'Aramatha', 1, 'Feels like a database trap', 'Can’t look at any functionality without a major input of personal data.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-15T07:13:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14056603956', 'Willnotusethis app', 1, 'Not free', 'The app is not free but you do get 3 days free and then they charge you for a full year.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-12T08:23:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14046125057', 'Phaysa2', 5, 'I love Zero APP!', 'I’ve been using this app for years. I’ve enjoyed it. It’s been great so I signed up for Zero Plus! It has helped me get healthier and I have lost 21 lbs since the first of the year! Fasting is a healthy way to heal your body and to lose weight!', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-09T11:19:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14044912231', 'Phil marching', 3, 'Good, but could easily be better', 'The app needs a library the user can save their favorite commonly eaten items to for ease of entry', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-09T05:00:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14043696056', 'Lucas217p', 1, 'Deleting Fasts over 24 hours', 'I would appreciate it if you could look at this app. There have been several instances where it has deleted fasts for no apparent reason other than the fact that they went over 24 hours. I was using this to help me track my progress, but obviously that’s not going to happen as I cannot remember the specific times. I just know it was showing me at 23 consecutive fast. Before a 24 hour fast then reduce that to just two consecutive fasts.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-08T19:50:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14041193417', 'Jrg369', 1, 'Terrible', 'I want to use the free features but it won’t let me unless I sign up for a free trial. Not trust worthy. Scam.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-08T04:27:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14031772106', 'Kaceyyyyuuhhyyy', 1, 'Cost', 'I had the old version of this app for years and went to update my phone and redownloaded it only to find out I now have to pay for it. I don’t want all the fancy stuff they charge for now and it sucks you can’t even use it anymore with out a subscription', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-05T11:11:46-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14021855387', 'Super Iviana', 3, 'Great app for logging fasting, but', 'I’ve had this app for about three years now for keeping track of my fast but now I can’t do anything unless I choose the free trail for a week or I get the yearly and it won’t let me by pass it so I’m assuming that means I can no longer use Zero because I’m fine not choosing any pay options but I can no longer log my fast.', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-05-02T16:56:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14011086593', '8Sunny8', 1, 'Idiotic', 'Congratulations on building a bare bones app, which provides zero information, motivation or guidance during a fasting state. What are you asking $$ for? So I can tell you the start and end day of my fast? Lol, what a joke', '7.5.1', 'us', '2026-04-29T18:06:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14010762117', 'Sophia Boxton', 1, 'Not worth it', 'It’s a paid app', '7.6.0', 'us', '2026-04-29T15:45:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14006569940', 'Love24!!!!!!', 1, 'Widget does not work', 'Widget continues to count your fasting timer even after you end the fast. Haven’t fixed for months. App now completely useless.', '7.5.1', 'us', '2026-04-28T10:52:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1168348542'), '14004103958', 'AnonymousIRL', 1, 'Was Free, Now Expensive', 'I used to love this app. I had stopped using it for a while to start 2026 as the year has been pretty crazy. Finally was in a spot where I am ready to get back into fasting and opened the app to find out you HAVE to pay to use it now. Disgusting. Any app that claims to care about health and then charges $70 to use it is lying about caring about your health. Only cares about your money. I noticed they added that AI calorie counter thing where it guesses the calories based off a picture, and I bet that’s why it s so expensive now, because AI is expensive. News flash, NOBODY WANTS THAT BS!!!', '7.5.1', 'us', '2026-04-27T17:14:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14268037515', 'ghggggghhuigffhhhgf', 1, 'Bad color change and they won’t change it back/allow us to change custom colors', 'I get some apps change themes overtime, functionally it’s the same in terms of inputting data, but it is too hard to read now. Flat out they made it difficult to read and follow along with what you are reading. They seem pretty responsive on Reddit/social media and they aren’t changing it in the near future. I really don’t like this new change and I never leave app reviews, I hate it that much I am going to leave a 1-star until they fix it.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-05T17:42:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14266056492', 'ReadingExpress', 5, 'Brilliant nearly flawless app', 'As a software professional, I look at apps with a practiced eye. This app is designed by people who pay attention to details of usability that is rare in the apps I’ve used. Their level of attention to features and functions deserves an A+. There’s a little bit of a learning curve in a few areas that are beyond my pay grade, but I’m mostly interested in the major nutritional categories. I think this app is as close to perfection as one can find in a food and nutrition logger and it gets better all the time.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-05T06:47:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14262123012', 'Midlander2018', 3, 'Good Potential', 'Quirky app. Not able to login sometimes on an iphone. On an Ipad it will rotate to portrait on it’s own. Adding daily items will not also work (very frustrating). No feature to photograph a meal and let it decipher (I would rarely use this but when dining out it’s very useful. No ability to easily track hours not eating (IF) this should be easily added.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-04T06:41:47-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14262041263', 'Brokenmedicalsystem￼', 4, 'Helps with controlling minerals and nutrients.', 'This is helpful in making sure you are eating healthy. The database is full of foods so it makes it easier to log.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-04T06:17:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14260074546', 'Jacqueline0304', 2, 'Too many ads and pop ups', 'I used to love this app but the ads and pop ups are out of control', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T17:56:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14259639804', 'Mrguitarguy', 1, 'New colors are terrible', 'How are we supposed to read these? Just give us the option to change it back or choose a theme.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T15:06:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14259395353', 'Rentrobis', 2, 'Lacking attention to detail', 'I love the overall concept but the level of polish is just not sufficient to me. The app is full of little bugs and confusing details and slow-to-load essential screens.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T13:35:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14258927096', 'QuikSilver24', 1, 'Can’t create a new food anymore on web version', 'I’ve been logging foods in Cronometer for almost 16 months, and a recent update introduced a frustrating issue on the web version. Previously, if I searched for a food that didn’t exist, I could immediately choose “Create New Food.” Now, the search always returns partial matches, even when the exact food doesn’t exist, so the option to create a new food never appears unless I type random gibberish. The developer suggested creating foods through Foods → Custom Foods → Create Food, but that doesn’t solve the problem. Before creating a new custom food, I first want to search my Favorites to see whether I’ve already created it. After almost 16 months of logging, I can’t always remember every custom food I’ve made, and this way it helps prevent duplicate entries. The previous search behavior was much more efficient. Why try and fix something that isn’t broken? I hope the web version is updated to restore it. When this issue is fixed, I’d be happy to update my rating.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T11:00:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14258755458', 'StubT', 3, 'New colors suck', 'I''ve been using this app on and off for many many years. I get that the color change is because maybe people felt ''judged'' because the fat metric was in red. But the new colors are all too pastel and similar. It makes it very difficult to see at a glance what you have eaten or burned that day. You should at least give us a choice of color palate. Bring back the old colors!!', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T10:08:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14258114596', 'yoni_weisser', 5, 'Great app for tracking calories/bulking', 'This summer I wanted to bulk up, and I downloaded Cronometer thinking it would be a pain to log my food everyday. But surprisingly it was very easy and extremely user-friendly to a complete beginner. 10/10 would recommend to anyone who wants to be serious about their diet.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-03T07:12:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14256439358', 'grizzlygaranimal', 5, 'FANTASTIC tracker', 'Easy to use. So much data. Far better than any alternative. Incredible value for the price.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T21:10:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14256317298', 'reno dirty boy fan', 5, 'Great app', 'This is one of the most useful apps for your health. I lost 60 lbs in part because I got serious about tracking my nutrition and this app was indispensable for that.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T20:24:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14255580521', 'waressy', 1, 'Ruined by Ads', 'I switched to this app a long time ago when MFP ran ads and I enjoyed the run. Started using it again recently and every time I feel productive about adding my foods, it shows an ad and KILLS my productivity.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T15:52:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14253883110', 'Avemariajoy', 5, 'Very helpful', 'I can weigh my food or even the bar code. Works great', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T07:07:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14253646079', 'tedoni', 5, 'Big success', 'I have used several apps and paper. None can compare to the easy accuracy of Cronometer. The flexibility is why I keep using it and why I’m hitting my goals', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T06:03:15-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14253084833', 'lee0000032', 1, 'Doesn’t sync weight from Apple health', 'Basic feature that doesn’t work, bad look for a supposed premium app', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-02T03:05:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14251386289', 'VenomousSVT', 2, 'App refresh issues and lack of restaurant data.', 'I made it almost a day and a half before cancelling my subscription. I hate it cost me $11 to try and hate the app. When changing days the app has annoying tick where it slides up a menu from the bottom that is blank and slides it back down. It does this every time you swipe out to another app and come back or when changing days in diary. It was annoying enough that I just can’t deal with it. Combine that with the lack of restaurants I’ve had to manually add my meals and it has made switching into my diet even more annoying.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-01T16:12:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14250089807', 'Clark balsamic', 5, '.', 'This is the best cal tracking app but change it back to the apple!', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-01T09:08:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14249554054', 'Sarah HTX', 5, 'The best by far', 'Already has a majority of my favorite speciality foods and supplements already in the database. I’ve used others, and none have had as comprehensive of a database, making it so much easier to stay accurate and on track. I’m only using the free version, and it’s plenty good for my goals.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-01T06:45:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14249357160', 'goncalvesarianna', 5, 'BEST APP', 'this is the best calorie tracking app and they don’t completely deprive you of features if you don’t pay premium unlike fitness pal and other apps !!!!', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-07-01T05:51:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14247562364', 'Regulus black is back', 5, 'great app all together', 'this app is really great , it has a lot of foods and the scanning barcode feature is really nice, obviously its a little annoying that theres features you have to pay for, but i love that the app is still completely functional without the bought things.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T18:59:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14247178361', 'Chesezinc', 1, 'They took a good app, and broke it in a single update', 'The new update is a really worse version. The font size is now so large, I can’t see all of my items at once. How can I either revert to the old version, or adjust the font size back to the old size? As a daily user, you’ve basically made this unusable in one single change', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T16:47:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14246071659', 'curmudgeon567', 2, 'Poor', 'Best use is to get nutrition info. Useless got tracking. All foods havr to be added to dairy.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T10:38:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14245721207', 'Barb Turner', 4, 'Great except stuck commercials', 'I really enjoy the app and loved how many foods come up accurately when scanned. However the commercials are terrible. I don''t mind sitting through them because I chose not to pay but many times they are very difficult to exit out of and get back to the app.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-30T09:02:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14243640880', 'Kneeling Warrior', 2, 'Please allow users to change the colors', 'I have benefited from this app all year, however, the latest change in colors makes it extremely difficult to read. Please allow users to set their own color choices rather than forcing them to use one set of colors. If this will not be changed, I will be forced to move on to another app which I can read more easily.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T21:36:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14243503757', 'NetnKiva', 5, 'The Best!', 'Easy to use. Keeps me on track!', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T20:42:29-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14242775440', 'Ineverrewiew', 2, 'Deleted right after I got it', 'So basically I downloaded the app thinking it was going to be free but immediately subscriptions popped up to be a part of the gold member which gives you cases to everything so if you don’t pay for it you don’t get like anything that it says will give with the app. You can’t use the scan or picture thing if you don’t have it so you have to search up every single thing you eat and weigh it yourself. Would definitely not recommend unless you’re willing to pay.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T16:07:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14242716284', 'Yallymac', 5, 'Stop logging me out', 'App logs me out every few days and it’s incredibly annoying. Edit: they fixed it a while ago. I still use this app.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T15:44:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14242382634', 'RamonF16', 5, 'Annual Fee Required', 'App description in App Store does Not Disclose this fee nor allow a Free Trial period. 👺😔', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T13:39:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14241508502', 'Oakgrove', 5, 'The best', 'Easy to use, lots of information, comprehensive food list, scanner, really enjoy this food app', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-29T09:07:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14239232880', 'BradenLouden', 2, 'Fell off', 'When I first started using Cronometer it was amazing. Super easy to find the food I wanted to track, everything loaded super fast, and barely any ads. I would recommend it to so many people. Everything I liked about it is gone. First Cronometer turned up the ads. It wasn’t annoying at first, but it’s gotten to the point where the free version is actually unusable. Then I noticed it started to function slower. Everything that used to load quickly doesn’t anymore. And then as a final kick to the balls, the search feature recently was changed, making it much harder to find what I need. For example, now if I look up something like “Banana” instead of the top option being a banana, I get random bs like banana bread. I’m disappointed to say the least. I thought Cronometer was something I would be using for life, but I’d rather use anything else now.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-28T20:00:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14237095110', 'Scotty.O.', 5, 'Love it!', 'I absolutely love this app! I used to use Myfitnesspal but I find this one to be far superior. I love being able to scan the barcode so there is no searching for the food. It is exactly what I am eating. I haven’t found a barcode the app didn’t recognize. It is easy to understand. I highly recommend it!', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-28T07:34:22-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14237063613', 'cdav117', 2, 'What happened to this app?', 'This app has gotten unusable. Intrusive ads slow everything down. Things disappear from the recents now and when I try to type them in the app is completely confused. Iced coffee that used to show up as 9% of my water intake now shows as 74%. The 2% milk I drink everyday is now gone from my recents and when I try adding it manually it pulls in things that are totally off base like almonds but it doesn’t show the milk. It’s become more annoying than its worth now', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-28T07:25:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14235292755', 'NiteDread', 5, 'Great app for both free and paid features', 'I used to use MyFitnessPal for a while until they locked a lot of their free, previously useable features behind a paywall. I found this app after some research and have been using it ever since. It has great free features and the subscription has great features as well, especially if you want to help support the app. You can design which macros you want to focus on which I find to be the most useful tool. I wanted to focus more on how much saturated fat I was consuming and I was able to add it to my screen so I could see it. It’s a great app with great free and paid features. Highly recommend!', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-27T20:36:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14235175569', 'alexwayen', 5, 'Great for micronutrients and photo recognition', 'I’ve tried a lot of other apps, and this one is excellent for tracking micronutrients and supplements. The AI photo analysis works surprisingly well, especially for estimating portion sizes. I also really appreciate that there’s a web version, and I use it regularly. I just wish the web app also supported photo uploads. The UX can feel a bit clunky at times, and some information is occasionally missing. For example, when using AI photo recognition, it would be helpful to see the total calorie count more clearly.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-27T19:52:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14235048706', 'R2KBA2A', 5, 'Fantastic app', 'Easy to use, intuitive UI. Free barcode scanning makes data entry frictionless. Highly recommended.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-27T19:06:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14233661402', 'Kdswq', 5, 'Great dietary t racking tool', 'Very easy to use to track daily dietary intake: food; water; minerals; vitamins water; etc…', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-27T10:39:50-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14230451342', 'Food@home', 4, 'Chronometer review', 'Overall a good app that has an amazing free version just wish that it gave you food recommendations based on what it sees you consistently buying in order to make sure you h it all your nutrient needs', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-26T15:59:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14229572765', 'Gregarious GG', 5, 'Love this App❤️', 'The features are incredible! It is very easy to use. The information I gain about my nutrition is very valuable. Thank you!', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-26T10:49:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14227037846', 'Ilovebookslol', 5, 'Very decent', 'Hi sorry I''m writing this super late so I''m not sure it will be readble but: I downloaded this app expecting to have to pay for all the good stuff and I didn''t! It''s very much free and they make it so easy to track protein and fiber and hit all your goals. I have not one complaint for this app it works the way it''s supposed to and I respect it. Goodnight', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-25T20:18:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14226953038', 'Vanelle!', 1, 'have to put in info to try it', 'i''ll come back and give a higher rating if i actually end up liking this app. but it just pisses me off that i have to verify my email when i don''t know how i like the app yet. just so annoying and such a red flag for apps. other nutrition trackers i''ve used don''t make you do that.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-25T19:44:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14226777087', 'Rj_rae', 5, 'Great', 'Only nutrition tracker that I’ve experienced where you can turn off how the calories are shown, which helps if you don’t want to calorie count. Great free app', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-25T18:36:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14224582487', 'R̶i̶l̶e̶y̶ D̶r̶y̶e̶r̶', 5, 'So easy!!', 'Finally committed to tracking my Marcos using an app rather than eye balling it and this app has made it beyond easy!! The bar code scanner is a cheat code forsure and it’s relatively easy to build and create new meals if you are meal prepping.', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-25T06:19:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14223652804', 'LeeroyJenkins35', 5, 'Perfect for tracking nutrients', 'This app is perfect for tracking micro nutrients and macros. The only issue I have is the recently selected items no longer appear at the top of the search bar when you look them up. You have to scroll through all sorts of individualized items to find generic items, please change this search function back to the way it used to be!', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-25T00:39:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14222822876', 'YMISFT', 5, 'great', 'it’s pretty great! this app helped me lose weight and helped me stay aware of my nutrition intake', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-24T18:47:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14222677667', 'external_screams', 5, 'Even the free version is amazing', 'You don’t have to buy the premium for it to be a good functioning app. Very easy to use, simple instructions, love it', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-24T17:53:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14222137578', 'paige coker', 5, 'great app! and you don’t have to have a subscription!!!', 'one of my biggest things while looking for a new app is if it had a paid subscription, i looked for a lot of different ones and this one does have a subscription, BUT you can completely use this app forever without the subscription, it has like every food product like ever made already on there so you don’t have to look at your packaging or guesstimate to track calories, it also helps you to set a reasonable goal based off of your weight and you’re weight goal and how active you are! it also connects to your apple watch and tracks allllllll if your stuff! I LOVE THIS APP!', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-24T14:25:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14219427496', 'Rome Iheanaju', 5, 'Free version is good', 'Does what I need and easily customizable', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-23T22:47:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1145935738'), '14217717939', 'cjsusername', 3, 'THIS APP IS THE 🐐', 'I’ve used this app for ~6 years with varied consistency, different goals, diets, and hrt. It’s probably the MOST comprehensive and customizable FREE fitness+nutrition tracker. What initially stood out to me was micronutrient tracking which idk any free app that does (or even paid!). But it’s so so important. I feel FANTASTIC when I’m hitting at least 40/50% RDI on micros. I would’ve never known or had the motivation to meticulously track them. The # and quality of features on the free version has never made me feel like I *needed* premium + ads aren’t annoying, which I REALLY respect. But I’m probably going to get premium to finally check out the other features and support a great company! I really just love the overall meticulousness of this app, it scratches my brain and gives me peace of mind about my health, everyyyything is counted 😅', '4.57.0', 'us', '2026-06-23T11:37:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '14168242674', 'georgiehart88', 2, 'Doesn’t sync energy data', 'It’s cute, but language is annoying. Mostly it does not write data to apple fitness about energy, just time, unless you have an Apple Watch.', '5.12.6', 'us', '2026-06-10T18:59:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '14160224968', 'Boinicotti', 1, 'Delete delete', 'I wanted to like this app. I even gave it several days to accumulate my health data. Then I realized it’s just a cash grab. Once your data populates, it’s instantly hidden behind a paywall and you get bombarded with adds to upgrade to a subscription. There is nothing “freemium” about Gentler Streak! It’s just an attempt to get installed on your phone so it can pester you with subscription offers. All the data is useless because they won’t let you see it until you pay. I wish I could see what the app is like without all the paywalls, so I could decide if it’s worth paying for!?!? But no, you have to sign up for a subscription (and it auto renews if you don’t remember to cancel the “free” trial). Hard pass.', '5.12.6', 'us', '2026-06-08T16:56:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '14132111846', 'La mas consentida de Dios', 5, 'Gisell fit', 'Abundante, exitosa,bendecida ❤️ atraigo siempre cosas buenas', '5.12.4', 'us', '2026-06-01T10:54:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '14116950800', 'Heads I win, Tails you lose', 3, 'App works, but lies about real fitness levels', 'The app works. However, it tells me that I have to keep taking 3 day breaks. I’m a healthy persons with no issues, but when I do a workout, like a 30 min easy walk, it complains that I am overreaching and demands I take three days off. That’s not healthy…that’s messed up. If the heart rate stays below 110, it’s safe to walk everyday, but this app feels differently. I’m thinking of canceling my subscription because I refuse to pay for a service that is basically lying to me.', '5.12.4', 'us', '2026-05-28T13:27:15-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '14098484191', 'zombi3g', 2, 'Watch app is broken', 'Watch app never stays in sync, making this useless. Watch app usually says “Ready to raise the bar” or “Great day to push”. Phone app says” Do what feels good” or “You’re pushing too hard”. It’s a shame because this used to be a great app. No more subscription from me.', '5.12.4', 'us', '2026-05-23T16:08:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '14077805127', 'Blitz quietly', 2, 'So far a waste of money', 'It keeps promising to reveal something special eventually. 12 days in and there is nothing that I could not see on the Apple Health App.', '5.12.4', 'us', '2026-05-18T02:34:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '14071221028', 'Renee1$', 2, 'Bad app', 'It tells you the same things over and over and over. It does not track accurately one minute to tell you that you’re over exceeding, then the next day you need to work out like you’ve never worked out in your entire life. It use to be better, but with all the “upgrades” it has become awful. I have had this app for several years and I am now going to get rid of it.', '5.12.4', 'us', '2026-05-16T07:41:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '14045352089', 'ArtyATL', 3, 'Non social...', 'Supports Bluesky but not X...? I guess that''s good for the six or so people on Bluesky. Hopefully this is not some sort of political decision. You shouldn''t punish your users for politics.', '5.12.3', 'us', '2026-05-09T07:19:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '14010892347', 'Jesus Calling', 5, 'Gentler Streak Workout Tracker', 'Gentler Streak Workout Tracker', '5.12.2', 'us', '2026-04-29T16:42:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13996101031', 'ghlatta3', 1, 'Unable to edit', 'At first glance, this appears to be a good app to summarize activities. Unfortunately, I quickly found out that you are unable to edit or delete activities that may be duplicates or other related options. I also noticed that there’s no place for putting in your weight?!? They have age and height as part of your metrics, why not weight? As such, cancelled my subscription within a week - what a waste of money!', '5.12.1', 'us', '2026-04-25T10:03:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13968751562', 'R B 169', 1, 'Don’t know what this is for or about, but would like to cancel or stopped!', 'Thanks', '5.12.1', 'us', '2026-04-17T14:27:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13964884261', 'Leatherjuice', 5, 'Wonderfully human!', 'So much praise for the Customer Support team; they were SO responsive to my question and I see how consistent that is across all their community platforms. 💕 I’m also loving the adjustable suggestions for active recovery - great visual for understanding balance in movement and rest.', '5.12.1', 'us', '2026-04-16T12:13:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13943008336', 'go 1740', 5, 'Locking up', 'Update: did an outdoor walk with sound turned on in settings and everything work. No lock ups. Thank you very much. Great App. Having trouble when doing a dog walk my watch locks up and have to reboot my watch. That did not fix it. Had to take gentler streak off of watch to stop it. Have apple watch ultra 3. Just renewed app and not happy about spending the money. This is not the first time it has done this. Update: Found out this is a bug. Waiting for the fix.', '5.12.1', 'us', '2026-04-10T07:26:29-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13875480600', 'Apple Reviews 1234', 1, 'No way to see if this is the right fit for you without paying up front', 'Be weary of apps like this that don’t let you test a premium version with a trial. This app wants your money up front so you can’t see if it’s a good fit without giving them money up front. And you only receive the 50% off discount for 24 hours after downloading the app. I primarily use iPhone widgets and my Apple Watch complications for viewing my data at a glance. I can’t test the accuracy of this app without premium off the bat. Don’t waste your money on a chance to see if this works for you.', '5.11.3', 'us', '2026-03-22T08:37:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13863444013', 'Dmuakk', 4, 'The', 'The', '5.11.3', 'us', '2026-03-18T22:16:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13851917285', '4cvvxfsy', 5, 'Love this app!', 'This app has been so handy and useful since I have downloaded it. It told me the day that I pushed myself too hard, and I felt that in my body. I’ve learned how to listen to my body and take rest days when needed because of Gentler Streak.', '5.11.3', 'us', '2026-03-15T12:53:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13831746340', 'ThatOtterDude', 5, 'Good app', 'It’s one of my favorite apps, I like it. The only is the sub’s price is too expensive 🥹', '5.11.3', 'us', '2026-03-09T16:34:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13816539748', '"Paiger"', 4, 'Highly Recommended', 'The most positive thing about Gentler Streak is that I make the choice to use Gentler Streak because I spend my day doing different types of exercises from not long after I wake up in the morning, until I go to bed at night. And it allows me to record them because it has a good selection of different types of workouts. And syncs with my Apple Watch & iPhone. Basically, the most important thing I''m asking for is that rather than having to touch the "HOLD TO END" button, being able to just be able to scroll over to view a screen to switch over to ANOTHER workout without stopping! And sadly the negative thing about Gentler Streak is that it doesn''t do well outside of my home. So as soon as I leave the house I have to switch over to using Apple Fitness Tracker instead. The first reason is that if I am using Gentler to record my "Daily Chores", working on some of them as my Wonderful Hubby is driving me somewhere, Gentler Streak will first send me a message that I''m not active! If I don''t look at my watch to see the message it will stop my "Daily Chores"! If they haven''t been stopped, and we''re getting ready to arrive where I''m going to get out and walk, I can''t wait until we actually arrive there! Because after I push the "HOLD TO END" it takes a very long time before it actually stops! And lets me start my "Walking-Indoor"! My Wonderful Hubby doesn''t want to stand there & wait for me to start walking! So I''ve been using my Fitness Tracker for anything done outside of the home. Unless we go to a hotel. I start using Gentler Streak inside the hotel.', '5.11.3', 'us', '2026-03-05T07:22:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13799471120', 'Mastertow', 3, 'Surgery', 'There is no way to say that you have had surgery so of course it affects your daily exercise etc', '5.11.3', 'us', '2026-02-28T10:27:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13793951742', 'Cjmota', 1, 'Corrupt', 'Bought the membership and was unhappy with the product. Unsubscribed and instantly lost access to the app while still paying for the year.', '5.11.3', 'us', '2026-02-26T23:23:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13793529437', 'Cali-swanky', 5, 'One year review of Gentler Streak', 'The app continues to be essential for me. It provides tracking & monitoring of activities. The advice is on point; gentle—yes and a motivator. I will renew and maybe even upgrade to Premium.', '5.11.3', 'us', '2026-02-26T19:58:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13774017584', 'FartyBoy415', 3, 'The obvious issues are puzzling', 'I do want to love the app, I truly do. I am so puzzled by very obvious issues 1. The app on the watch doesn’t does not lock when you swim. I just finished swimming and paused the workout by pushing side buttons, got home and what a surprise! the time and laps were back on, so the whole workout is totally ruined. Default apple app works flawlessly. 2. Watch compilation sometimes does not update for days. Even reinstall did not fix it. What’s the point?', '5.11.3', 'us', '2026-02-21T09:44:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13766892452', 'bronxred', 4, 'Love it! Please add Shortcuts!', 'This app has made a huge difference in my own self care. While Apple’s rings feel like high pressure and lead to feelings of failure, Gentler Streaks feels encouraging and keeps me exercising. The only problem is a complete lack of Shortcuts support. It would double my usage of the app if I could trigger workout recording or more easily add standard workouts that I didn’t record live. Even the simplest Shortcuts would help. Thanks!', '5.11.3', 'us', '2026-02-19T09:50:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13744989156', 'cabruen', 5, 'Use daily', 'Fantastic app. One of the few apps that I open and use daily, and even out a widget on my Home Screen. My life and activity have improved by using this app.', '5.11.2', 'us', '2026-02-13T07:32:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13735384629', 'aThalassophile', 5, 'Work Smarter Not Harder', 'Game changer! Incorporating rest and suggesting both tough and easier workouts takes the guess work out. And the graphics! Adorable.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-02-10T13:27:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13725636328', 'la musica es divertida', 5, 'Muy excelente', 'Gracias muy excelente para saber de la salud', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-02-07T21:27:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13720588213', 'MikeKZen', 5, 'Fantastic', 'Aggregating sleep, step count, workout and key biometric markers provides a dashboard for sustainable activity with snapshots of readiness and progress daily. Outstanding!', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-02-06T12:56:58-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13717093540', 'DMHS81', 5, 'Love it!', 'I know I shouldn’t need the app to validate that I need rest, but it really does help me back off when I am torn between pushing too hard and resting. I also love the fitness path so that I can gauge the potential impact of my actions.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-02-05T13:59:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13715662740', 'Mommodan32', 5, 'Great app', 'I’ve been using Gentler Streak for several years but really is all it’s hyped to be. The activity path really is a motivator!', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-02-05T05:47:50-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13715607415', 'Moon catcher 85', 5, 'Exceptional', 'The app is filled with features that are very useful. For those who are on a health journey it’s definitely worth checking it out and definitely recommend.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-02-05T05:30:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13708221467', 'Fiebert', 5, 'Great app for workouts', 'Gentler Streaks is an excellent app. Works great with Apple Watch', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-02-03T05:13:50-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13704280411', 'KembaCat', 5, 'Best app on my phone!', 'I am motivated by positivity so this is the first app I open every morning to check out my sleep metrics and workout suggestions. I LOVE that this app always encourages balance and self-awareness above just pushing through to some arbitrary goal.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-02-02T03:29:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13702070216', 'galaxymychild', 5, 'Recommended by a psychologist!', 'I’m a psychologist who preaches healthy habit forming so it’s exciting to see an app that supports moving with compassion. I love that the developers use concepts from behavioral science! Great work!!', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-02-01T11:39:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13699004090', 'Stp5up', 5, 'Balance', 'Love the activity path graphic which helps me modulate my exercise and fitness activities. Not always go for more but find a balance with time to rest and recoup based on past days and sleep and vitals. Well done', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-31T17:31:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13697189783', 'fletch48', 5, 'Love this app', 'I use this in conjunction with Apple Fitness to “gently” guide my activity and exercise goals. At almost 66 years old it’s nice to have the data and the suggestions to keep me from overdoing some days and not doing it at all on others. I am really enjoying it.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-31T07:15:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13691337113', 'TechDaniel', 5, 'Found my soulmate wellness app', 'Found my soulmate wellness app! Gentler Streak actually gets what it means to be human. It doesn''t give me a red ''X'' or break my multi-day streak because I''m tired and need rest. Instead, it says: "Rest is part of the plan. See you tomorrow!" It uses a beautiful, rolling "mountain path" to visualize my activity cycle, showing me clearly that active peaks and restful valleys together paint the complete picture of my health. Both are respected. In a wellness tech space that often worships "no days off" and can feel like self-shaming, Gentler Streak offers a precious permission slip—to fluctuate, to listen to my body, and to pursue well-being without self-judgment. If you''re also tired of being held hostage by numbers and want a more flexible, kinder way to accompany yourself, you must try this. Health isn''t a boot camp for your body; it''s a journey you take with your body. Thank you, Gentler Streak, for finally putting me on that path. 🧡', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-29T18:49:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13691314215', 'Elin Key', 5, 'Perfect for long-term habits', 'I’ve used Gentler Streak for six months, and I honestly love it. I’m someone who always wants to be more active, but it’s really hard to set strict workout goals and keep up with them. This app doesn’t pressure you. It gives gentle reminders and encouragement, and it keeps reminding you that you don’t have to be strict with your body. I’d recommend it to anyone, especially women who want an active lifestyle without being pushed too hard. It’s perfect for long-term use.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-29T18:39:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13690934733', 'Nanie59', 5, 'Works for everyone!II', 'I’m a “senior citizen” who likes to keep active and love the way this app can accommodate my activity - mainly walking. It is encouraging and when I need a nudge - it is gentle! Thanks much!', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-29T16:06:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13690600872', 'Dignified Beard', 5, 'My favorite health buddy', 'Gentler Streak has been such a great way for me to evaluate my progress and maintain a healthy lifestyle. I appreciate how easy it is to use and understand.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-29T13:49:57-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13690369911', 'Retired Jin', 5, 'Great design/purpose', 'I am a recent retiree who is loving the time/ability to be active. Whether it be active travel, pickleball, or a fitness class - they bring me joy, social connection, and help me maintain my health. I am not looking to become an Olympic athlete (obviously). A key concern for me is to keep my activity level and intensity balanced and safe so it remains sustainable. Gentler Streak echos and enables that philosophy perfectly. Thrilled to have found it!', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-29T12:22:29-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13689573475', 'smarty496', 5, 'Best way to realistically stay active', 'I use my Apple Watch to track workouts and all, and filling the rings in Fitness is fun, but it is terribly unrealistic to fill them every single day. Gentler Streak’s path feature truly helps to keep me on track by letting me evaluate overall fitness, not just for today. It not only gently nudges when my activity is too low, but also provides a reminder when I’m pushing too much. The weekly, monthly, and overviews help me to visualize the bigger picture, too. All of this is way more motivating.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-29T07:59:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13689293334', 'jbetht79', 5, 'Encouraging', 'I really like that this app accounts for life and fitness levels. I didn’t find the free option helpful and the help information seems to be written from the perspective of the paid app. I did upgrade, but I think the information should cover both unpaid and paid. Until I upgraded, my “path “ didn’t show anything like what was in the help. Still, really enjoying the (paid version) app.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-29T06:34:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13689190099', 'Billiam71825', 5, 'Helpful Insights and Forgiving Guidance', 'This has proven to be an excellent app with great insight into the current state of my health and trajectory over time. My favorite feature by far is the active monitoring and warnings when I’m pushing too far. Without it or when I ignore it, I definitely feel worse off the next day, but when I respect it I feel like I’ve made solid progress and still feel well in the coming days.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-29T06:03:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13689139075', 'Rhokev', 5, 'Genial', 'Está es una de las mejores aplicaciones para seguimiento no solo por la data sino por como la muestra la verdad es oasis de conocimientos de datos duros contrastados con la realidad del día a día', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-29T05:48:15-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13688844071', 'RickInIdaho', 5, 'Great app', 'I appreciate the feedback I get from Gentler Streak. Between time at the gym and an active life I get a good sense of where my fitness level is at and where I need to focus.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-29T04:13:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13687555355', 'JSullivan1', 5, 'Super useful', 'This app is great. It looks great. The user interface is great. The information is great. I look at it literally every day. I really enjoy being able to review my sleep and the insights and see how my exercise routines and my sleep affect my overall health. The recommendations helped me to push myself without going too far.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-28T18:49:47-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13687209237', 'Statechamp11', 4, 'Great app but comparison to food needs work', 'I truly appreciate everything this app does and how it encourages me to be the best I can be without making me feel awful for already being perfect. The only thing that gives me pause is the fact that every workout and weekly/monthly summary puts calories burned into the concept of food. I think the idea behind this came from a good place, most people don’t understand what “100 calories” truly is, but this could be dangerous for people with eating disorders, as the app almost implies “you can have an apple now that you worked out”', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-28T16:31:51-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13686785167', 'Aegis3121', 5, 'Genuinely love this app', 'I really do love using Gentler Streak. It’s encouraged me to stay within a band of activity rather than the default rings, such that I don’t feel bad for missing a day or something. It feels like a more healthy reminder for long term trends than daily engagement. The UI is pleasant to use. I really like that the data is all stored locally in Apple Health too such that if I ever did stop using it, I still have all the history, plus I know it’s just staying local.', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-28T13:41:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1576857102'), '13686686130', 'DiRegNurse', 5, 'One of my most used apps!', 'I tend to go at things hard. Push it to the wall hard. Invariably I ended up either sick or injured. This app really helps me to progress without breaking myself. I can see when I need to rein it in AND when I can push to make optimal progress. Rest days used to be so hard for me. Now I take one of the suggestions for an active rest day - whether full rest or gentle exercise that will help me recover faster from the hard stuff. I also love the sleep and vital signs info. And.. the articles are short, science based and informative. Love this app!', '5.11.1', 'us', '2026-01-28T13:05:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14260674467', 'williespillie', 5, 'Not a Camera expert but love this app', 'I love photography - my friend gave me a lengthy speil about why he likes Halide and I took the bait. Something about how they use the iPhone lens to make images more flat and abide by it''s best foundational hardware. Whatever, I went for it. All I can say is I LOVE the photos I take with this app. Love. It''s not a filter thing. The lighting and texture I get is great. For anyone curious I encourage you to try it you!', '3.0.5', 'us', '2026-07-03T21:43:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14254514146', 'iliketorelax', 1, 'Another subscription service', 'Not going to pay for a camera app when I’m already paying adobe products to edit photos for me, just another reason to fork over money for things to look good at minimal effort.', '3.0.5', 'us', '2026-07-02T09:57:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14254123071', 'peppero7', 1, 'Unreliable', 'The quality of the images from this camera are really nice and the presets look so good. However, the app is super unreliable. Idk if it’s just bc Apple doesn’t have great 3rd party camera support, but it crashes frequently, fails to launch the camera, and I’ve run into bugs with disappearing and lost photos. Just skip this app, it’s not worth losing your photos.', '3.0.5', 'us', '2026-07-02T08:10:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14250909422', 'sabbath303', 5, 'it feels like a CHEAT CODE to have this in my pocket all the time!!', 'LOVE this app!! I’m so happy every time I hit the capture button.', '3.0.5', 'us', '2026-07-01T13:18:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14243181075', 'Ggtr27', 1, 'Manual focus doesn’t work', 'The sole reason I wanted this app was so I could set focus to infinity when taking pictures through glass etc. However, when I set focus to infinity (while leaving all other settings on auto), the pictures come out unusably blurry', '3.0.5', 'us', '2026-06-29T18:42:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14239398022', 'Apple Computer Corp', 1, 'No timer', 'No timer', '3.0.5', 'us', '2026-06-28T21:08:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14232171156', 'rmcnees', 3, 'Great photos, great edits, sluggish performance', 'The images are great, and the new editing tools give lovely results. That’s the number one takeaway. But this app has always been sluggish and you need to be prepared for that. You can put up with it if you have the absolute newest pro hardware, but anything from more than a generation ago has been frustrating to use, in my experience. If you want to compose and take one photo it’s fine; snap two or three and it has been hit or miss for me. Many photos that I thought I’d missed were in the recovery queue, but not all of them. Even on an iPhone 17 Pro I am losing photos if I try to snap more than two in quick succession. Set your expectations here: this app is for capturing one or two intentionally composed photos, not for snapping lots of pics.', '3.0.5', 'us', '2026-06-27T02:57:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14231309821', 'funhourmessengers', 1, 'watch out', 'halide 3 incoming. they’re gonna do the rug pull on people that paid outright again lol.', '3.0.5', 'us', '2026-06-26T21:20:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14231258424', 'internet’s bad now', 2, 'Normally great but something broke', 'Ever since a recent update some photos haven’t been saving. Kind of makes the camera unusable if I can’t rely on it to save the photos I take.', '3.0.5', 'us', '2026-06-26T21:00:15-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14225852868', 'TheDailyCoroner', 5, 'Finally!', 'If you have ever wanted your smart phone camera to act like a real SLR camera with its own dark room, this is it and more!', '3.0.5', 'us', '2026-06-25T12:46:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14216739909', 'Erl.Rochester', 2, 'Regularly failing', 'Cannot trust a camera app that doesn’t reliably save the photo. Quality is nice when it works though.', '3.0.4', 'us', '2026-06-23T06:37:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14211068838', 'GG1060', 3, 'Really frustrated by III.', 'I don''t want to use it. I don''t want to open it. Please let me disable it for now.', '3.0.4', 'us', '2026-06-21T17:56:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14206453098', 'MsLabRatLingo', 5, 'Get real. Get gritty.', 'Take back control of your images.', '3.0.4', 'us', '2026-06-20T12:49:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14201770307', 'waldo647', 5, 'Pioneer & Leader', 'Halide continues their pioneering role in the professional and serious cell phone photography space.', '3.0.4', 'us', '2026-06-19T08:48:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14199341257', 'Spaz007', 2, 'Each time I use this I find more ways to crash it.', 'Recent update fixed one bug but keep hitting more. ProRaw edits seem to be the fastest way to break the app. Can’t edit a 48MP (Original frame instead of 4K) photos without it force closing. Kinda feels like it defaults to 4K output to avoid crashing the app.', '3.0.4', 'us', '2026-06-18T17:30:42-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14198146363', 'croth535', 1, 'Subscribe button not functional', 'I cannot use the app or camera because i can’t even subscribe. I’ll fix review once im able to subscribe Love the app and camera otherwise so it’s a shame I can’t use it', '3.0.3', 'us', '2026-06-18T10:20:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14195199146', 'n3rfus', 4, 'Please allow overall customization of film settings!', 'Please, please provide a way for us to change the default "film" settings. It''s insanely annoying having to dial down grain, halation strength, and MTF strength for every single individual picture I take, one by one. I would love to be able to set an overall user default at minimum, or, ideally, a user default override for each look/process.', '3.0.3', 'us', '2026-06-17T15:53:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14193377883', 'Rob in LIC', 1, 'Incorrect advertising', 'It’s frustrating to purchase an app that says “33% off” and to be told that you have a week to try it out on an annual subscription, to find out two days later that neither is true.', '3.0.3', 'us', '2026-06-17T06:10:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14179502128', 'SniperDaShooter', 5, 'Mark 3 is a great update.', 'Mark 3 adds some great quality of life features to Halide. The shutter priority and iso priority are welcome. And the new editing controls are fun. The new color filters seem refined, not to over saturated or gimmicky. And I love the halation feature! If I could make any changes I would work on the shutter lag. Also it would be great if the exposure compensation slider could snap to 0 easily. But otherwise I love this app and think it’s well worth the subscription.', '3.0.2', 'us', '2026-06-13T15:23:51-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14177377044', 'Seltzer Robb', 4, 'Much better than Mark II', 'I purchased Halide several years ago, but never really used it consistently. Felt somewhat cumbersome and frequently crashed. However, I Mark III is really good! The default options are excellent, and the fact that there aren’t TOO MANY looks is the best part. If this app had shipped with 10+ options, I don’t think I’d use it, but because it’s been pruned to specific looks, it works really well.', '3.0.2', 'us', '2026-06-13T03:51:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14175932096', 'Phunky Tech', 5, 'It makes me want to actually use my phone’s camera', 'Halide Mark III, its new looks, and its new editing system has made me actually want to go out and take photos with my phone for the fun of it. And the photos that come out of it look incredible! I’ve gotten some shots that make friends question whether it came out of my phone or a real camera. For me, it’s a hobby, so the price is worth it. The app is incredible and the devs truly care. Give it a go!', '3.0.2', 'us', '2026-06-12T17:52:59-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14172469167', 'WildWild44', 4, 'Why the change?', 'I installed the app. Received the training emails. Thought that the app was great and easy to learn for an amateur photographer like me. All of a sudden the app changed. I didn’t understand that it was a new version. I don’t know if the new version is better, but I will try it more. I am happy that I can revert to the older version.', '3.0.2', 'us', '2026-06-11T21:12:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14166057379', 'ponderda', 1, 'Don’t be Suckered', 'I was just looking at this app with mild interest, when suddenly I realized I had just bought it for a full year. I resent the fact that this app charged me for a full year for something I don’t like and I can’t use. Don’t you be suckered like I was.', '3.0.2', 'us', '2026-06-10T06:29:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14156634588', 'ouhuqdsooqiwd', 5, 'Finally', 'Relief from complex Camera app swipes and ovetdonevprocessing', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-07T18:19:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14156039276', 'Gentry Crafted', 5, 'A great update to a really good camera app', 'The new features and the process zero functionality is awesome when it matters that what you take a photo of is realistic. The only feedback I have with the iPhone pro max 17 is that golden hour photos look grainy. Otherwise, I’m using it takes lot of photos natively but also to edit photos taken from my SLR and through the various photo apps I have for different purposes.', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-07T14:16:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14155567815', 'eric_slc', 5, 'The best camera app', 'The process zero raw capture + new film simulations makes the iPhone fun again', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-07T11:31:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14154105490', 'Fu_K it', 5, 'We think we are the Doctors we are the disease', 'Halide takes good pics I only wish there was video', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-07T03:49:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14147858634', 'Ram050', 5, 'So much fun!', 'The most recent update adding the different looks and the editing tools has turned this into my favorite camera app. Every look is awesome out of the box. I’m very impressed. I rarely need to go into the editor to tweak parameters. That said, I do appreciate all the options in the photo editor, especially the histogram view and the film simulation. I also appreciate the fact that the looks are applied on top of the raw capture. I like being able to shoot without worrying much about the final outcome, and then apply looks in post. Overall, for my style of shooting and editing, this is the best camera app on the AppStore.', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-05T11:57:52-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14147690539', 'nelsonjj1', 5, 'Wonderful edits on raw photos', 'I’m enjoying the new filters and how they interact with new raw files and old ones in my camera roll.', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-05T11:01:47-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14141911277', 'CorndogBandit', 5, 'M3', 'It’s so good. Can’t wait for a few more filters to be added, but everything looks and runs great! Also portrait mode etc', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-03T23:46:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14136780187', 'Ааа12344321', 1, 'Нужно заплатить', 'Скачивается бесплатно, бесполезная программа', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-02T14:50:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14130343306', 'autumn burchhh', 5, 'Lovely photo app', 'As long as you dont mind the $20/yr sub fee, it’s a lovely photo taking app. I personally love the raw look of the photos. If you dont like the look of all the automatic filters used on the iphone camera app i definitely recommend Halide!!', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-06-01T01:08:07-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14125213847', 'MassiveShock', 1, 'Baiting and Misrepresentation', 'Developers and marketers for the app should have a clear and concise iPhone model compatibility with the app. Read the marketing from a link about the Mark III version and proceeded to purchase the $20 charge to test the new version from my iPhone 15 Pro. Photos came back bad and horrible looking. Then I searched from other reviews that the app was not compatible with my phone. Proceeded to cancel the subscription. Do better you filthy Sharks.', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-05-30T16:41:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14124926183', 'Mrd Mhk', 1, 'Not free, paid scam', 'Why call “free app” if not free? I can''t even check how it works without buying a subscription. Just a scam.', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-05-30T14:44:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14124505547', 'jtvl_ca', 5, 'Fantastic replacement for over-processed default camera', 'It’s exactly the app I was looking for so I could have full manual control of photos or by default not have the extreme hdr in ios camera', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-05-30T12:08:44-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14120984840', '331Bleecker', 4, 'I like Mk III but it feels incomplete', '“Batteries included” feels a little bit of an overstatement. I need basic contrast, highlight and shadow controls (at the minimum) if I’m going to be able to stay inside Halide and not have to go to another editor. To me, not yet worth the paid update.', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-05-29T14:41:46-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14119546762', 'EmceW', 1, 'Don’t worked', 'I can''t pay for the app, even though I have the right amount of money on my balance.', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-05-29T06:53:41-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14116959190', 'coffeebean2003', 1, 'Who gave you the right?', 'Who gave you the right to alter the interface to include a link to Halide Mark III. I’m not going to subscribe for a camera app, and I don’t want the link cluttering an interface I’ve already paid for.', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-05-28T13:30:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14116433768', 'Paul Mina', 1, 'i paid too much for this rubbish', 'cannot use luts! stuck with limited effects?bought this app outright. Once I installed it for my wife, your app is prompting her to re-purchase it. however, your app mentions family sharing. don’t be greedy.', '3.0.1', 'us', '2026-05-28T10:30:14-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14113002825', 'Tangerine Beach Resort', 2, 'One time purchase doesn’t include everything', 'Hey, if I make a one time purchase, I expect everything. I hate subscriptions and have very few. Most of the subscriptions I have are free from T-Mobile. I love one time lifetime purchases. Subscription sucks.', '3.0.0', 'us', '2026-05-27T12:37:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14098542827', 'Phukface420', 1, 'Would’ve been 0stars if possible', 'Be real don’t b fake free the download and try free…… trash', '2.27.3', 'us', '2026-05-23T16:32:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14087535647', 'W. Harden', 5, 'A highly effective tool', 'I''ve been getting into underwater macro photography lately and have a iPhone 17 pro. A big challenge is not really being able to see what you''re aiming and not being able to touch the screen. Apple''s camera app isn''t smart enough to know what the subject is and focus onto it. Halide gives you the tools to make this difficult setup work. Although, it''s not perfect. Occasionally submerging or removing the phone is interpreted as a swipe and messes up some setting. Usually it''s faster to restart the app and enter everything again than figure out what went wrong. A "lock settings" feature would be nice for this. But despite these minor grievances, I''d recommend it to anyone getting into macro photography on their phone', '2.27.3', 'us', '2026-05-20T17:41:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14063984604', 'ryrymead', 5, 'Absolutely amazing.', 'Absolutely amazing but it asked me if I wanna test Mark III and now I fear this app will be ruined by removing features. Mark III is a total downgrade from Mark II. Mark II is perfect, so do not take anything away from it. If anything you can add more but if you remove features I will not be using this anymore.', '2.27.3', 'us', '2026-05-14T08:52:54-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14051511393', 'cal9219', 5, 'it took me a while to appreciate this app', 'I''m a professional user. It took me a long time to appreciate this app. At first I thought it was producing low quality files, but this is just due to the way it creates raw/JPEG exports by default. After I adjusted that, I was able to get an amazing experience with this app and I love it! I love the manual focus assist, where it shows a zoomed in view of the central focus region. I''m really starting to get used to the interface as well', '2.27.3', 'us', '2026-05-10T22:31:01-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '14011042822', 'NAQProductions', 1, 'Was good until they forced subscription', 'It’s hard to find zero filter manual setting apps for the iPhone. I had bought this one early when it was still maybe $5, but they have since switched to subscription based and now I can’t access it anymore. No thanks.', '2.27.3', 'us', '2026-04-29T17:47:43-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '13954542599', 'LA TK Teacher', 1, 'Does nothing for 16e; no refunds allowed.', 'I forgot to turn off automatic renewal and was charged after a week. Within 10 minutes of the notification I emailed Apple about a refund. Rejected twice. And Halide’s comic sans terms said no refunds allowed. The app does nothing to help the 16e experience and their no refund policy is bogus.', '2.27.3', 'us', '2026-04-13T11:54:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '13916405361', 'C-Dubs714', 5, 'Best Camera App for iPhone', 'This is by far the best camera app for taking professional-level photos. It basically turns your phone camera into a $1000 professional photographer camera. It is amazing. You can fine-tune every aspect to be perfect, from ISO to shutter speed to focus to white balance. Every tool a professional would have is at your fingertips. It is not good for taking quick, everyday photos of random stuff. It is for when you need to take a photo with your phone and make it look like an expensive camera. And it’s CHEAP! Only 20 dollars a year for the membership or 60 dollars to unlock it infinitely. 10/10 would recommend.', '2.27.3', 'us', '2026-04-02T19:58:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '13905585121', 'Morpheusgrey', 2, 'Difficult to use', 'Not impressed. I purchased it for the manual feature which repeatedly resets to auto no matter how often I select manual. I will make the wanted settings and then work to frame the image and set the magnification only to find it is in auto again and the settings changed. Manual is apparently tied to magnification and focus which is not true manual. If I can get settings to hold the image capture is great but by that time the scene has changed. Also the zoom is not pinch but manual. It is a waste of money.', '2.27.3', 'us', '2026-03-30T20:19:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='885697368'), '13897473903', 'Badappreview101', 1, 'Garbage “professional” app', 'Considers themselves a “professional” camera app yet saves all images as dng or heic? Formats no platform accepts? Get a grip', '2.27.3', 'us', '2026-03-28T13:17:29-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14233492283', 'RPWa', 2, 'Does not preserve preset', 'Having an issue lately where I selected one preset, then go back to the library, go back to the picture, select a new preset , back again to the library, back to the picture and it reverts me back to the 1st preset used. Long description but that’s the best way I can as a step by step. I’ve deleted the app and reinstalled, have the lifetime tier, but can’t seem to correct the problem. Hopefully the developer can suggest a fix.', '7.2.2', 'us', '2026-06-27T09:48:03-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14210175118', 'AFA1389', 5, 'Amazing', 'No critiques, great app', '7.2.2', 'us', '2026-06-21T12:07:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14186776844', 'ballerinashley', 4, 'FOR DEVELOPERS', 'Please include options to change video speed, and also allow to crop video in app I love this app use it daily it’s my trusty go to specifically for the histogram please do not ever get rid of that that’s by far the reason I come to this app and have used it for years love the price it’s worth it but please allow more options for editing the footage rather than just the image quality and such thanks!', '7.2.2', 'us', '2026-06-15T12:17:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14178484936', 'Iniesta big', 5, 'HD HD', 'Ufff', '7.2.1', 'us', '2026-06-13T09:35:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14176664880', 'Wizzle Berry Pi', 3, 'Tone doen the aggerssive upsell', 'It does not do a whole lot, but I like the interface. I just wish it wasn’t a pain in the butt trying to get you to spend WAY too much on it for its insane lack of features.', '7.2.1', 'us', '2026-06-12T22:53:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14176221683', 'No off-line play!', 1, 'Disappointing and Cumbersome', 'Dated and cumbersome. Not worth your time. Upgrades completely not worth it.', '7.2.1', 'us', '2026-06-12T19:44:26-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14173491053', 'jimys', 5, 'Stop asking me to rate this app. I’ve done it several times already!!', 'Just stop!', '7.2.1', 'us', '2026-06-12T04:39:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14136804100', 'Applestorereviewer559', 1, 'Guess my one time fee wasn''t one time', 'Every Iphone App does this, don''t claim a one time fee just to put all new features behind a paywall', '7.2.1', 'us', '2026-06-02T14:59:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14101259222', 'Emankcin 720', 4, 'Mostly good', 'Would be five stars if it would stop asking for a review', '7.2', 'us', '2026-05-24T09:47:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14100768955', 'Bream777', 2, 'Error with exporting', 'It keeps closing when I try to export images and most of the time I can’t even export because it keeps saying error', '7.2', 'us', '2026-05-24T07:21:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14087714425', 'DreadPirateRobert', 5, 'Quick and easy and very capable', 'Great for quick edits or more complicated work.', '7.2', 'us', '2026-05-20T18:54:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14081060403', 'Youngmelkid3', 5, 'Love', 'Live the app', '7.1.7', 'us', '2026-05-18T23:43:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14053062992', 'Landonnodnal', 1, 'Great for a while', 'I used this app for a couple months and at first it was great. It edited the raw photos from my Canon and turned them into beautiful JPGs all for free. But suddenly out the blue, the app just started crashing. It would crash when making edits and I wouldn’t even be able to export my photos. I contacted support around 4 month ago, they said they were working on it but nothing has changed. It could be because I currently have an older iPhone 13 but it seemed like a more global platform when looking online for answers. FIX YOUR APP PLEASE!!', '7.1.7', 'us', '2026-05-11T08:49:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14052031867', 'Redeemer', 1, 'Used to be the Gold Standard 5-Star App; Now Unusable', 'Since December, the app''s histogram has been utterly broken. Any modification - literally ANY - caused the histogram to display a clipping alert. LITERALLY. ANY. This caused me to wonder if there was an actual error in editing, or just the app bugging out. Either way, it made me lose confidence in even bothering editing photos using the app, which is heartbreaking. I haven''t been able to edit photos with full confidence, and will probably cancel my subscription since the bug still exists. I''ve tried holding out for a fix, but it doesn''t seem like it''s a priority, even though I''m sure I can''t be the only one experiencing this major bug. Not sure how others are tolerating it.', '7.1.7', 'us', '2026-05-11T02:54:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14051689362', 'rayzh11790385', 1, 'Does not work anymore with DJI videos', '“Unable to complete export” error message shown on any video taken with DJI.', '7.1.7', 'us', '2026-05-11T00:04:50-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '14046213740', 'Together We Shall Conquer', 5, 'Please don’t forget', 'The only thing that matters', '7.1.7', 'us', '2026-05-09T11:50:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13997349540', 'LeftBigToe🧈', 5, '👍🏻', 'Very nice', '7.1.6', 'us', '2026-04-25T18:31:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13985199179', 'Clams Maloney', 2, '🫤', 'This is the fourth time I''ve had all my custom presets just vanish. I think it''s probably time to move on and find a new editing app.', '7.1.6', 'us', '2026-04-22T06:50:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13961353109', 'Heineken snakes', 5, '❤️INCREDIBLE….DREAM COME TRUE', 'I’ve been doing photography for six years now, and for the longest time the workflow was always the same: take the photos off my camera or iPhone, move them to my computer, edit in Lightroom, Luminar, or another program, then export them again to an SSD or send them back to my iPhone so I could finally share them. That whole process was long, tedious, and honestly took a lot of the fun out of editing. After experiencing Darkroom, everything changed. Being able to edit directly from my camera roll, copy those edits, batch apply them to multiple photos, and have the originals replaced cleanly instead of dealing with extra copies or unnecessary complications feels incredible. It made the workflow simple, fast, and enjoyable again. What used to take multiple steps across different devices can now be done in one smooth process right on my phone. Another huge reason I appreciate this app is that I hate subscriptions. It’s refreshing to see that I can buy lifetime access instead of being locked into another monthly payment. Even better, the lifetime option costs less than the price of Adobe Lightroom, which makes it an easy value comparison for anyone serious about editing. For anyone who values efficiency, quality, and a clean editing experience, this app is a game changer. This is a dream come true. Ten out of ten. Honestly, very happy.', '7.1.4', 'us', '2026-04-15T11:34:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13945839106', 'cjmal', 2, 'So many bugs', 'I can no longer in good conscience recommend Darkroom to my iPhone/photographer friends. So many bugs , glitches and inconsistencies make this software unreliable.', '7.1.3', 'us', '2026-04-11T02:38:30-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13944058120', 'dUdE 7548', 5, 'Great free Option', 'It is very thorough for being free and feel it is one of the better apps to use for editing. It can be slightly confusing when first learning it, but it is a quick learn.', '7.1.1', 'us', '2026-04-10T13:29:24-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13943782704', 'Im not 10 years old', 1, 'Apple', 'Not the greatest will not connect to my phone, will not fix problems with DPP photo editing', '7.1.1', 'us', '2026-04-10T11:44:31-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13933900034', 'Whats 9 10', 3, 'I can’t green screen', 'Ok so where’s the green screen feature? And I can’t export with out the + edition? Bruh', '7.1.1', 'us', '2026-04-07T17:00:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13930289289', 'Gweav1', 1, 'Buggy', 'It’s becoming super buggy. I’ve used this app for years and since recently it’s been so bad.', '7.1.3', 'us', '2026-04-06T16:02:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13912387410', 'TahoeIsGreatGruberIsWrong', 3, 'iOS7 design language?', 'This app went from being num 1 to being num none. This application is the perfect example why subscriptions can and do screw over customers.', '7.1.3', 'us', '2026-04-01T16:51:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13901691634', 'Stevveeennee', 1, 'Perfect flow, but crashes constantly', 'I would really like to use this app, but it crashes every time I do a batch export and batch paste edits', '7.1.2', 'us', '2026-03-29T17:13:46-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13876075701', 'Haji Azim1234', 5, 'The', 'The', '7.1.1', 'us', '2026-03-22T11:55:33-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13870512466', 'Riv96', 5, 'Pleaseee', 'Can’t use the app cause of all the bugs and crashes and it overheats my phone….and I really don’t want to leave it behind it’s my favorite app please update', '7.1.1', 'us', '2026-03-20T23:23:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13852054871', 'Profeta_Hernandez', 5, 'La mejor app', 'Una de las mejores que e probado y solo con la versión gratis tengo lo que necesito', '7.1.1', 'us', '2026-03-15T13:46:00-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13850931617', 'danwguy', 3, 'Wish it continued to work', 'Over the past few months the app freezes and some photos won’t be able to export or save. It happens randomly either still or Live Photos. I am not going to renew my subscription', '7.1.1', 'us', '2026-03-15T07:24:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13837101326', 'wumpusaev', 1, 'what a joke', 'color grading behind paywall? your service is running on borrowed time.', '7.1.1', 'us', '2026-03-11T07:56:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13826872212', 'nal812', 4, 'Great app but crashes too much', 'This is my fav photo editing app in terms of the filters, tools, and interface, but it crashes SO MUCH. Half the time the export fails. I wish they would spend less time making new features/filters and more on just making sure the app doesn’t crash every 3 photo export..', '7.1.1', 'us', '2026-03-08T07:05:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13824244159', 'Easternsun', 1, 'Review from Disappointed A Legacy User/Longtime Supporter', '2010 or 2011 I started using this app. I purchased it at the time for $10. Wrote a great review and gave five stars and recommended it to everyone I knew. Then it was sold and came a the "Legacy User" title and "perks". Fast forward to the present not only did the "perks" started to fade away but I went from paying yearly for the IOS and MacOS apps. Now all of my previous presets that I created GONE with endless back and forth with their Support Team. To now *new* subscription prices of $10 a month and $40 yearly. Putting me a "Legacy User" back to square 1... a new Member!!! Well DarkRoom you will go back to 1 STAR rating and I will say goodbye to you.', '7.1.1', 'us', '2026-03-07T11:34:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13793231004', 'jimys', 5, 'Color Play', 'Love how the smallest adjustments can sometimes change everything. Isn’t that what art is anyway, a mistake that creates a different something brand new? I make a lot of mistakes and like many of them, I do wish life in general was as accepting of mistakes as Art is. Thanks for these tools.', '7.1', 'us', '2026-02-26T17:54:56-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13784828719', 'CokeForSale', 2, 'App keeps crashing when saving edits', 'A very annoying bug where when exporting my saved work the app crash. It also crashes while I’m editing devs need to fix this', '7.1', 'us', '2026-02-24T10:27:18-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13767068910', 'Annabella__', 4, 'Best Editing app', 'Super cool. It gives you different ideas and options with good quality.', '7.0.25', 'us', '2026-02-19T10:54:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13736369716', 'Sajcjfjxb', 1, 'Filled with bugs', 'Past month the videos end up with terrible audio, like an echo. I’ve updates 3 times now. I sent a report many times and it’s still there with the latest updates. I can’t use any of my edited videos because of the audio bug. The app lags, crashes many times, many other bugs as well like flickering screen, sometimes colors will randomly appear over saturated to the max or discolored. For the price I pay per year is not okay! Just updated again and even more useless. Every adjustment I make does not save! I can’t create anything now. Almost ready to cancel subscription', '7.0.24', 'us', '2026-02-10T20:27:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13736188818', 'Kensington Slagger', 5, 'iOS 26.0.2 Fixed', 'I’m happy again. Love this app. Thankfully I’m a legacy customer because I WOULD NEVER paid a monthly/yearly subscription for this app.', '7.0.24', 'us', '2026-02-10T19:06:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13723983680', 'peoplecure', 1, 'Waste of my time', 'I downloaded this to edit video. The do the annoying setup, and the first thing I see in the video editing feature is “Try Free” button hovering over the player controls (I cannot browse through video in any way). Like, what the hell. Don’t be wasting my time. I just needed a simple video editor. I would have just downloaded CapCut if I knew I would face this blockage. It is a waste of my time.', '7.0.22', 'us', '2026-02-07T10:29:37-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13691576925', 'Dee3', 5, 'Tone Mapping Slider for ProRaw', 'Would you please bring this back? Apple ProRAW photos are garbage in many instances. It was nice to to be able to reduce the tone mapping and build the image back up with this very capable editor. Still giving you 5 stars with hope!', '7.0.22', 'us', '2026-01-29T20:31:22-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13686985423', 'Bud1900', 1, 'Leica guy', 'It has no explanation for how to use it.', '7.0.21', 'us', '2026-01-28T15:01:00-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13676634729', 'nonya1985', 1, 'Excellent … when it works', 'This app is so great when it actually works. For the past several months it has had so many bugs especially when trying to export photos. Sadly this makes the app almost unusable. I really hope the developers figure this out soon because it was so good in until then.', '7.0.19', 'us', '2026-01-25T21:07:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13668181654', 'TahoeIsGreatGruberIsWrong', 1, 'Subscriptions are in, and feature updates are out.', 'Anyone considering subscribing, check the release notes first! 40$ a year and all you get are bug fixes. No iOS matching UI redesign.', '7.0.19', 'us', '2026-01-23T16:12:39-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13666649096', 'Mortyfmmfmmfm', 1, 'Simply unusable in is current state', 'I had this app (and have been paying)for over a year now and In the beginning, prior to adding video editing features things ran smoothly for the most part. Crashes here and there and some limited functionality compared to other offerings from adobe and photomator. But as they have added features the bugs have been constant. I am simply trying to edit my raw photos and export then back to the photo app. While editing I often have crashes (I figure Ok I have amini 6 maybe it''s slow or something, I give it a little latitude for some errors) but I CAN NOT EXPORT PHOTOS ANYMORE. This defeats the entire purpose of this app.I paid for the year and now am sick with an app that won''t let me do is basic functions. Avoid until there are consistent positive reviews again and bugs have been delt with. This app is simply unusable in is current state', '7.0.18', 'us', '2026-01-23T07:10:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13661456188', 'buddhist architect', 2, 'Good at some things but missing basic features and is slow', 'Might as well just pay more for Lightroom or maybe there is a better cheap photo editor out there', '7.0.18', 'us', '2026-01-21T20:29:29-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13658319509', 'wuheif', 1, 'they broke it', 'attempting to crop the image causes double vision and blurring on the image. Literally unusable until they fix this', '7.0.18', 'us', '2026-01-21T00:56:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13653620006', 'Goatie82', 5, 'Need a Repair Tool', 'Are you planning on adding a repair tool? I think with that you will rule the universe.', '7.0.16', 'us', '2026-01-19T17:08:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13648850816', 'R3v3r3nd Meat', 1, 'Full of bugs', 'Every update has made this software run more unstable.', '7.0.17', 'us', '2026-01-18T11:08:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='953286746'), '13641035987', 'spaceparade', 1, 'Truly the best', 'Until recently, their latest major update has left the nearly identical app almost unusable between all the random crashes and their now dysfunctional touch controls.', '7.0.16', 'us', '2026-01-16T11:45:46-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14263324899', 'Wilder497', 5, 'Procreate pocket Review', 'Perfect app for drawing really amazing 😍', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-07-04T12:52:19-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14259715491', 'Michael jr .s', 5, 'Bug with reference window and importing images', 'My app freezes every time I try to add an image to my canvas. But other than that, it’s a good app.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-07-03T15:35:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14248301217', '.bnajeiakkf', 4, 'It’s good', 'I’d like to suggest allowing users to see how many artworks they’ve created, like, just there. Instead of having to stack them.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-30T23:36:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14247191496', 'pawberri', 2, '??', 'wheres the undo button.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-30T16:51:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14243904214', 'bellex1', 5, 'YES!', 'I love the app!', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-29T23:25:06-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14242469049', 'olive 🍸', 4, 'buttons suddenly not working', 'like the title says, for some reason when i hit the back to gallery button and the modify button they do not work.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-29T14:10:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14227096332', 'Maggoumac', 4, 'LOVE it but one thing', 'It’s very fun and all but my erase button doesn’t work? Does anyone else have this problem?', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-25T20:42:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14223255346', '𝚋𝚕𝚒𝚣𝚠𝚒𝚗𝚐!', 5, 'fix this', 'It wont let me move my layers without it disappearing this is the 3rd time and even closing the app wont fix it😢😢', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-24T21:42:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14222119847', 'Bailey.j.l.T', 4, 'The layers', 'I absolutely love this app! It has been my main drawing app for years, but I have always noticed the layers. Why aren’t we able to have unlimited layers? I’m always stuck with 18 or less layers because of having to make the canvas bigger for higher quality.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-24T14:18:48-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14202144048', 'kaspillberg', 4, 'Great app-hate the name', 'I love this app. It’s very dynamic and fluid and fun for me. But the name. It’s given me some problems when people have noticed it.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-19T10:42:50-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14196123753', 'Mix3dRic3', 4, 'Another bug', 'When add a drawing into a stack then try to remove it from the stack by dragging it the canvas refuses to move, I can’t even move canvases within a stack, it just doesn’t work and it’s really irritating. Please fix this!!', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-17T22:16:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14182723191', 'randoBOZOishPersoN', 5, 'THIS APP IS MY LIFE', 'I draw SOO MUCH!! Thank you thank you thank YOU FOR MAKING THIS APP!!!!', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-14T11:19:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14179028794', 'Pubertjohnjones', 2, 'Can’t use', 'I can’t import photos anymore. The app just freezes.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-13T12:31:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14178936195', '?JMncf508%#qwnu', 4, 'LOVE IT! But there are some things I don’t like', 'What I love about this app: I made book covers for books! They turned out so good with this app. I don’t like it when you do animation stuff you can’t do layers :/ But I’m making an animation and it’s so good with this app so far! Love this app! 20/20! What I don’t like: sometimes when I do the fill thing. It dose NOT work. But I can undo it so that’s good. In animation part, you can’t do layers. The layer tab is the frames.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-13T12:00:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14174044765', 'Goosygoos', 5, 'Great app for business flyers', 'I’ve been having this app for a couple years now and I can say this is a great app, I do believe that some of these bad reviews is because of user fault. I will say it does take a while to learn the app, but once you learn it, it’s super easy to use. I use it a lot to make flyers for my business and it’s super easy. Best investment ever.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-12T07:24:36-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14164664335', 'Kirby_Fan99_', 5, 'My main drawing app', 'I use this app as a hobby to just draw 10/10 how is this not 5 stars', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-09T20:57:21-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14164390056', 'JulieAK22', 5, 'Best Drawing Tool Ever!', 'This is so easy and fun for all ages! I love the diverse brushes, animation tools, and choices of colors! The only thing I found that needed a little improvement is how when you hold down to straighten lines, let’s say I wanted a perfectly smooth heart, it gives you a weird W. Other than that, best thing I’ve ever tried!', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-09T19:01:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14163669775', 'MaddieRS3', 5, 'My favorite app!', 'Procreate is soooo good! It might be difficult to understand with many choices for professionals instead of simple one click for an easy doodle. Most of the time I use it for my actual drawings since it’s perfect for it. It deserves to have a higher price but I’m glad it’s not too high since it’s high quality. This is my go to app and I love it so much!!!! Also when I try to import photos it doesn’t work?', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-09T14:14:52-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14159183872', 'Blasty the yeah', 5, 'This will always be the best drawing app', 'The app is really neat and nice to use and I’m familiar with it since I had classes using it but when I did get it on mobile, the undo button isn’t really there. But I love everything else about this app. 👍👍', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-08T10:41:14-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14136992571', 'reelyraddude', 2, 'ehhh', 'procreate why can the text box remember the font but not the text size?? i downloaded this to sketch out comics on the go but theres no way to type in a font size or copy style so it’s actually impossible to use it for that. i forgot this was a problem in full procreate but you can type in the text so at least its slightly less annoying. PLEASE fix this. quick menu is awesome though.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-06-02T16:14:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14126332277', 'TechNerd101', 5, 'Absolutely awesome!!!', 'I love painting stuff, especially space scenes, and I made some FIRE paintings. I love the wide range of brushes and tools. The only thing I’d like to suggest, is when selecting which part of the drawing to omit painting from (masking), I would like to have a feature where I can lock the brush to the line of the selected geometry. For example, when painting atmospheric glow, it’s very time consuming without the feature, but if the brush followed the border of the omitted geometry, I can do it within seconds. Otherwise great app!', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-31T00:31:40-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14120739978', 'Charlie_msp', 5, 'Procreate Pocket is the most simple, intuitive app on IOS', 'It’s simply unmatched', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-29T13:10:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14119076499', 'gerard.o', 5, 'Best drawing and editing app 🙌', 'It’s simple but does everything you need for basic editing. Love it!', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-29T04:26:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14116718830', 'Choco336', 5, '2026 Review', 'Been using this app for years I highly recommend this if your a content creator trying to make thumbnails and stuff it’s so easy hmu for tips or tutorials on TikTok @sadoexp', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-28T12:05:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14103391749', 'Mikecole533', 4, 'Not bad', 'This app would be sooooooo much better if it wasn’t pixilated. I very seldom make “in-app” purchases so if there’s an option to buy a vector style drawing tool- this is why I’m ignorant about it because I don’t look to make purchases- I may as well delete this app now and look for an app that doesn’t charge to draw a smooth line, the way any art app should be. Hey developers, can you add the font “DEATH CROW” and make it available as a FREE font? I think TONS of people would love the font. I don’t own the font but I use it a great seal on personable art. Thanks.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-25T00:08:53-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14093895313', 'AidanRI', 1, 'Terrible!', 'I hate the updates! This app has been destroyed! Do not buy', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-22T11:30:02-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14091506777', 'Crisssssp', 5, 'Goood but one thing', 'Procreate is good but I want one thing bones. i’ve also use procreate dreams (only a little bit) and something just came in my mind bones I think it would be way easier for me to animate stuff in procreate or procreate dreams cause I don’t have to animate and draw each individual thing. Although I still like it, I’ll probably keep using this forever', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-21T20:07:08-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14089134336', 'Pettyma4', 1, 'Payments', 'My only issue with this app is that I’m being charged for it when I don’t have it anymore. There is not an active subscription popping up either and this is the 2nd time I’ve been charged. If anyone could help me with that I’d appreciate it cause i think it’s dumb to spend 6.35 on an app I don’t use. Also what am I even being charged for ?', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-21T05:36:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14087046988', 'moodyunicorntwinfan Calvin', 4, 'Love it 😊', 'I am so glad I downloaded this because it so great guys. Even better, I can do it with Art With flo!', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-20T14:19:35-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14075410434', 'Ajlance1234567', 2, 'Missing tons of simple features and not to to par with ipad version', 'It shouldn’t be that hard to make this as great as the ipad version. The fact that there’s not even an undo button and relies on the worst double tap mechanics i’ve ever used plus all the other lack of things and it’s always crashing on me. There needs to be a lot of improvement.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-17T09:40:48-07:00');
INSERT OR IGNORE INTO reviews
  (tracked_app_id, review_id, author, rating, title, body, app_version, region, review_date)
VALUES
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14061775319', 'hhhhhh69797', 4, 'great, but i wish you could add private layers like the iPad version.', 'that''s all really, 10/10 app either way. i''m wondering if the developers will ever add that feature into the pocket version', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-13T17:57:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14050575184', 'Bleeblesheeble', 4, 'I like it!', 'There are a few things that are not as good as they could be though. First off, the main complaints I see are from people confused on where to find certain features or how to use the app properly, and this could be fixed with a simple tutorial given when the app is first downloaded. Not the biggest issue, as you can generally figure things out if you search around and look up online where to find things. More annoyingly for me- zooming out on a drawing. I don’t like how it will zoom out all the way unless you pinch your fingers slowly. Please fix this, who wants their canvas to revert back to normal positioning every time they zoom out a little too fast? And also- the sliders for brush size selection and opacity selection being on the SIDE of the screen instead of the bottom. I’ve multiple times changed my brush size or opacity by mistake when I’m drawing a bit too close to the edge. Having the sliders at the bottom of the screen is much better. I also don’t like how the sliders are so minimal, I like the ones on ibis paint x better- yeah I get that it’s for aesthetic purposes they’re that way but aesthetics shouldn’t matter when they makes your DRAWING app harder to DRAW with. I also wish when you are selecting a custom canvas size, you could actually see a preview of what size rectangle you are making. Overall this is a good app for people looking to draw on the go or for people who do not have iPads to draw with and the complaints I have don’t actually irk me that much lol', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-10T15:19:31-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14049975064', 'Rangerdardar', 5, 'Excelente', '10', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-10T11:35:49-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14045844504', 'Need help ￼', 1, 'I don’t know how to get procreate 54 back', 'I need help getting procreate 5.4 back', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-09T09:47:31-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14044259012', 'AMBERNO-', 3, 'Adding photos to layer', 'The app is fine but it’s hard to add images to different layers. If something could be done to make it easier or help me understand what to do, that would be great!!', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-09T00:22:16-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14039342141', 'Steve the hair harington 777', 4, 'I love the og procreate', 'Pls make the undo stroke feature otherwise it’s great 🙂', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-07T14:15:28-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14037107165', 'PaneLight', 5, 'I LOVE THIS APP', 'If you’re looking for an app as an artist to really dive into artistically this is perfect. It is 100% worth spending money on. Seriously you will find everything you need like.. •Good texture brushes •Brushes in general •Tools that help you with technique •animation ability • tools that correct alignment issues( straightens a line when needed) • corrects shapes • corrects symmetry And probably way more I’m not a bot I love this app, keep up the the good work procreate!!', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-07T00:04:32-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14036208222', 'Diamonempire', 1, 'Objects keep moving out of place.', 'Import from iPad are no good. wasted time and money. Plus it’s difficult to edit on iPhone, maybe make it more user friendly for pocket. It’s not enough overall, iPad app is better.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-06T16:59:09-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14029147051', 'miss the old internet', 1, 'can’t export PNGs', 'as stated, just shows stupid overanimated “Exporting” screen and then freezes there. not sure what’s gone wrong since the last time opening the app.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-04T17:20:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14021911743', 'Eternal sugar fan♥︎♥︎♥︎♥︎', 3, 'Dude... Wtf.', 'I''m sorry but when I first opened this god forsaken app it doesn''t even make any sense. Yes, I can in fact draw but it just felt off and it started to pmo so bad. PLEASE PROVIDE A TUTORIAL BECAUSE PEOPLE WHO BUY THIS PROBABLY DON''T KNOW HOW TO USE IT AT FIRST', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-02T17:21:11-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14017073243', 'пика68', 1, '🤦🏻', 'The money was wasted. PDF files won''t import; this app can''t see them.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-05-01T09:56:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '14014497623', '💚💅✨Piper✨💅💚', 5, 'MY FAV APPPPPPPP', 'So, there is oneeeeeeee problem! I just dont know how to go back when I mess up something instead of erasing it! But otherwise its amazing ( btw im on phone )', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-04-30T17:14:34-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '13996846234', 'Taylor followed', 2, 'Let’s see why I rated it a two…', 'I rated it a two because I have billing problems and I don’t want that, I wish I could’ve known not to download it with my money, and I’m very new to it. I want my money back…', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-04-25T14:47:55-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='916366645'), '13992109238', 'Larnett09', 1, 'Poor controls', 'I’ve used nearly every single drawing app on mobile, and this one is really confusing. I enjoy the features and control of them but the actual controls are extremely sensitive on a touch screen like a phone, “undo” function rarely works (why does this not have its own button, are you guys actually artists?!) or won’t show up….I’ve had to restart soo many canvases because “undo” functionality won’t appear on my screen. I’ve reinstalled the app, cleaned my screen I’m just completely boggled by how ridiculous it is to use this app. In 2014 I’m really upset with this app.', '4.0.16', 'us', '2026-04-24T07:31:33-07:00'),
