((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='588013838'), '14213470713', 'tsuboiishi', 4, 'Fix collage bugs', 'I’ve been using this app for years and love it. I use the collage feature a lot. When I make an edit in the collage I’m working on, then save as a draft, then go back in to edit it again, the most recent changes made are not saved. It’s been like this for years. Super frustrating. Please fix! Feel free to reach out if you want a screen recording.', '461.4.0', 'us', '2026-06-22T09:29:54-07:00'),
