((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='588013838'), '14156698395', 'Halfadozen6', 3, 'Helpful support', 'I updated my review again because the support informed me that plus is still $30 when I thought it was $40 so I went and got my upgrade through the website because my app kept showing me different memberships that were expensive. I’m keeping my review at 3 stars because I wish they didn’t have all these membership tiers and $30 is still on the spendy side when I used to pay $10 and $20 before for this same service. But I’m glad I don’t have to pay $40 so 3 stars it is.', '461.4.0', 'us', '2026-06-07T18:45:01-07:00'),
