((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='896694807'), '14170242900', 'LordBobTheFirst', 5, 'The Most Important App I’ve Ever Owned', 'Working Copy is just a godsend for being able to use git with virtually anything, and use GitHub (or whatever you want) to make your code both available and safely stored. I switch devices. I don’t worry about backups. I can have multiple AIs working in different branches, while I do the same. It all comes together seamlessly because Working Copy just does it all, and does it with a great interface and reliability. More than worth the money.', '6.8.7', 'us', '2026-06-11T08:06:20-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='896694807'), '14152946899', 'BRB_Biz_Nature_AIx', 3, 'Mediocre, secretive', 'i personally had a bad experience, the app was monitoring me and my work', '6.8.7', 'us', '2026-06-06T19:36:33-07:00'),
