((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='896694807'), '14056290608', 'limeytim', 5, 'Great for using Git with Obsidian', 'If you are looking for a way to reliably sync your obsidian vault with a git remote then this is your answer. Don''t try to use iCloud Drive, it is incompatible with git. Just use this app too clone to your iphone storage in the Obsidian folder in Files, and open the vault in the Obsidian app. It''s the only way you will use git and Obsidian without major frustration.', '6.8.5', 'us', '2026-05-12T06:46:31-07:00'),
