((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1405459188'), '12448586959', 'IvanGames12321', 5, 'Great, but needs a MAJOR update.', 'So you now how Scriptable only reads JavaScript, right. If so, then you know what I’m talking about. But I have a big favor to ask of you. Please add support for HTML. That’s like, the ONLY coding language I know. So, once again, please add HTML support. -IvanGames12321', '1.7.19', 'us', '2025-03-21T18:10:12-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1405459188'), '12305346094', 'kenzomenenzo', 5, 'Scriptable is so cool!', 'I have been preparing for a talk at upcoming Claris Engage conference to be held in Austin, TX - I have been using it to fetch FileMaker data and surface that data in different ways. As a small chart or list of top sales, but there are so many possibilities. A big thank you to Simon for making this great tool freely available. Combine this with Siri and shortcuts and there are incredible on demand interactions that we can deliver.', '1.7.19', 'us', '2025-02-13T02:00:45-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1405459188'), '12174991301', 'UglyBeatsBeautiful', 2, 'Worst integration on iOS', 'I really don’t see the point of this app the state it’s in. The documentation explains absolutely nothing. Giving no examples or any reference to the code it’s even using. It’s just a glossary of functions without any explanation at all. It was clearly built for a secret little club that already magically knows how the app works.', '1.7.19', 'us', '2025-01-12T03:22:19-07:00'),
