((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1450936447'), '5789469990', 'https_rainy', 1, 'Loading to Long', 'When I downloaded it it said it wanted to access my data and made me click accept policy so I clicked it and it took HOURS to load the data, and it’s still loading', '1.12', 'us', '2020-04-09T22:59:10-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1450936447'), '5705046648', 'Blow it out Ur nose', 5, 'I', 'Ghost', '1.11.5', 'us', '2020-03-24T01:18:38-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1450936447'), '5639418395', 'NuclearJon', 5, 'Changed how I use Shortcuts', 'The new automation server has changed how I use shortcuts and made parts of my work automatically and invisibly complete on their own. It’s awesome! Definitely worth the price and then some.', '1.11.4', 'us', '2020-03-09T19:36:23-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1450936447'), '5409196360', 'DigitalMJ', 5, 'Automation Server', 'I like the new experimental server option. Running an action without user interaction is quite liberating. Would like to see Apple make it possible to toggle off the restriction that cripples true automation. Right now the only way to execute these automations, is by tapping on a notification. I think we need both options. Love your app.', '1.11', 'us', '2020-01-15T20:37:17-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1450936447'), '5230551263', 'جيهان 🦋', 3, 'البرنامج صعب', 'ماعرفت له', '1.10', 'us', '2019-12-03T18:12:47-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1450936447'), '4838480457', 'frendaddy', 2, 'Mediocre at best', 'At first thought the app was perfect. The webhooks work great! But then you realize its just another get rich quick scheme and requires a SUBSCRIPTION to get any real use out of it. If it would be like 5 dollars and a one time purchase thatd be different. But the fact that you have to subscribe to the service is kind of ridiculous', '1.7', 'us', '2019-09-25T19:43:25-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1450936447'), '4410782291', 'ScottByrns', 1, 'Can’t agree to privacy policy.', 'Uninstalled before I ever tried it. Might be good but I’m not selling my letting my self be tracked where ever I go for a little convenience.', '1.5.1', 'us', '2019-07-04T11:47:05-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1450936447'), '4045550473', 'JRavWasHere', 1, 'Useless', 'They require a subscription for any basic uses of this app. At least we should be able to use the basic features without a subscription. Money should be optional. The devs don''t know the first thing about making a functional subscription service. Edit: last time I checked, the input parameters are blocked without a pro subscription.', '1.0.1', 'us', '2019-04-22T04:21:58-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1450936447'), '4035076988', '99brendanallen', 4, 'Great for only single actions!', 'I know a developer should have limitations when it comes to needing money, but it does everything that I need when it comes to making basic notifications. Only suggestion that I have is that there should be in is a help section. At first, I didn’t know how to push the notification out, but I know how to now from using your site. Please be sure to include a help section for those who don’t know how to instead of either writing a bad review or doing one extra step and have to go to your site to do so. Great app though! Very convenient now so I can automatically backup shortcuts everyday :)', '1.0.1', 'us', '2019-04-19T19:22:13-07:00'),
((SELECT id FROM tracked_apps WHERE apple_id='1450936447'), '4029372645', 'Nosrac', 5, 'This app solves a problem I didn’t know I had', 'Are you a power user who knows what a POST request is? If you use Shortcuts, you need this app!', '1.0', 'us', '2019-04-18T11:39:25-07:00');
